# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c727023b:

    # "I start the next day pretty sedately."
    "Comienzo muy tranquilo el día siguiente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c1c468d5:

    # "It's not like I'm doing anything until tonight, after all."
    "Después de todo, no tengo nada que hacer hasta la noche."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:5
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a1ccb9cd:

    # "I could've gone to school with the others and watched the tennis tourney they had going on today."
    "Pude haber ido a la escuela con los demás y ver el torneo de hoy."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:7
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cf6d3c56:

    # "But the thought of going there to cheer for that bitch Hiroko doesn't exactly appeal to me, even if I could've met Sayori there."
    "Pero la idea de ir a vitorear a la perra de Hiroko no me agrada del todo, ni siquiera con Sayori ahí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:8
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ebead0bb:

    # "Not to mention Nozomi would be waiting for me as well, and after yesterday I think I've had enough of her judgemental gaze for one weekend."
    "Sin mencionar que Nozomi también me estaría esperando, y después de lo de ayer, creo que ya tuve su mirada juzgándome suficiente por un fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:9
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_e609c6bb:

    # "Even if she might have a point about..."
    "A pesar de que tal vez tenga un punto con..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:10
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_46ee825a:

    # "Ugh, no, forget it. I'm not gonna let it get to me."
    "Aj, no, olvídalo. No dejaré que eso se me meta a la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:11
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_fd0c5696:

    # "Maybe I'll talk to Sayori about it at our date... if there's a good time to bring it up."
    "Tal vez lo discuta con Sayori en nuestra cita... si encuentro un buen momento."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:12
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_52f8c188:

    # "But mostly I just want to enjoy a night with a girl just this once. Is that really too much to ask?"
    "Pero, solo por esta vez, lo que quiero es disfrutar de la noche con una chica. ¿Es mucho pedir?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:17
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_11c4c3ad:

    # "It's a long wait until evening, and as I head over to our town's shopping district a bunch of anxieties all hit me at once."
    "La espera a que caiga el sol es larga, y de camino al distrito comercial de nuestra ciudad, un manojo de ansiedades me invade de golpe."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:18
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_40230d04:

    # "Nozomi had all day to talk to Sayori. Could she have brought up the \"[alt_name]\" thing with her?"
    "Nozomi tuvo todo el día para hablar con Sayori. ¿Le habrá mencionado lo de \"[alt_name]\"?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:20
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_b809894d:

    # "But she told me to deal with it. She wouldn't try to carry out her threat to interfere without giving me a chance to fix it, right?"
    "Pero me dijo que me hiciera cargo. No intentaría cumplir con su amenaza de interferir sin antes darme la oportunidad de arreglarlo, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:21
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_0ee56f2d:

    # "... The chance was at the tennis tourney. She was expecting me to be there."
    "... La oportunidad era en el torneo. Esperaba verme ahí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:22
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_89a3eb37:

    # "Fuck. I should've gone. I should've talked to Sayori before now."
    "Mierda. Debí asistir. Debí hablar con Sayori antes."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:23
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cfa2729b:

    # "I could've told her my side of things. But now..."
    "Pude haberle dicho mi versión de la historia. Pero ahora..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:24
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_2b3d0275:

    # "Where is she? She's supposed to meet me here."
    "¿Dónde está? Se supone que nos veamos aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:25
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_61c44503:

    # "Don't tell me Nozomi convinced her to- {w=1.0}{nw}"
