# game/Kyou 7.rpy:359
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_ebbdaabf:

    # s "*sniff* I know. This is a lot for you to take in. I understand."
    s "*snif* Lo sé. Es mucho que procesar. Lo entiendo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:360
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_dc68747e:

    # s alert_laugh "And I suppose I have killed the mood for our date... ahaha." with dissolve
    s alert_laugh "Y supongo que ya arruinamos el ambiente de la cita... jajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:361
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cf942eb0:

    # s alert_smile_right "So I will take my leave. But thank you, Kyou." with dissolve
    s alert_smile_right "Así que me retiro. Pero gracias, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:362
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_24b14fac:

    # s alert_happy "All things considered, I think we had a good time~" with dissolve
    s alert_happy "A pesar de todo, creo que la pasamos bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:364
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_59080ed3:

    # "And... there she goes."
    "Y... allá va."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:365
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_030a339a:

    # "My head is spinning as I stay seated at our table. I mean..."
    "Sentado en nuestra mesa, mi cabeza no deja de dar vueltas. Es que..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:366
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_938feb50:

    # "What the fuck just happened?"
    "¿Qué mierda acaba de pasar?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:418
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ad1a2ca3:

    # "Saturday comes and goes, but the anxious feeling in my chest won't subside."
    "El sábado viene y se va, pero el sentimiento de ansiedad en mi pecho no se apacigua."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:419
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a579e117:

    # "I tried messaging Nozomi online to ask what she did with me while I was hypnotized, but she's still tight-lipped about the whole thing."
    "Intenté preguntarle a Nozomi por mensaje qué fue lo que me hizo mientras estaba hipnotizado, pero sigue con los labios sellados."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:420
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fbedf621:

    # "Then she set her status to \"away\" and stopped replying to me after a while..."
    "Luego cambió su estado a \"ausente\" y dejó de contestarme después de un rato..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:421
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ca83a193:

    # "So now it's Sunday morning and I don't know what to do."
    "Ahora es domingo y no sé qué hacer."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:422
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b63e3d70:

    # "Do I really go there? Or..."
    "¿Debería ir? O..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:424
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a3d5122f:

    # "The sound of my cellphone vibrating from a received message pulls me out of my funk."
    "El sonido de mi teléfono vibrando al haber recibido un mensaje me saca de mi melancolía."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:428
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7c6ed64a:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Are you coming???\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Vas a venir??? \"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:429
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_bb15425d:

    # "I look at the clock on my phone. There's still plenty of time to get to school in time to catch the start of the tournament."
    "Miro la hora en mi teléfono. Aún hay mucho tiempo para llegar a la escuela a tiempo y ver el comienzo del torneo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:430
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f0ab46d6:

    # "Nozomi must be worried I was thinking of bailing, but I think she cut that possibility right out by checking up on me."
    "A Nozomi debe preocuparle que me escape, pero creo que cortó esa posibilidad instantáneamente al preguntarme."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:431
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c465ead7:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Yeah, I'm coming.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Sí, ya voy. \"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:432
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5ef594f9:

    # "Regardless of how I feel, I can't let Nozomi down. Not if I want us to keep seeing each other."
    "Sin importar como me sienta, no puedo defraudar a Nozomi. No si quiero seguir viéndola."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:434
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_049b00b9:

    # "My phone reverberates with another text almost immediately, and it brings a little smile to my face." with vpunch
    "Mi teléfono retumba con otro texto casi inmediatamente, y dibuja una pequeña sonrisa en mi rostro." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:435
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_29a72d09:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"It'll be ok dont worry :)\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Todo estará bien no te preocupes :)\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:437
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_15fa2e91:

    # "I don't really understand her confidence, but it's sweet of her to encourage me like this."
    "No comprendo su confianza, pero es muy dulce de su parte alentarme así. "

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:441
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3d8a9866:

    # "And this is Nozomi we're talking about. She's the kindest person I know."
    "Y es Nozomi de quien estamos hablando. Es la persona más cordial que conozco."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:442
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_232ba7c0:

    # "What reason do I have not to trust her?"
    "¿Qué razón tengo para no confiar en ella?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:445
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ea9e30be:

    # "I arrive at the school sports grounds in good time, as I observe the crowds that have built around the tennis courts."
    "Llego puntualmente a la zona deportiva de la escuela, y observo a la multitud que se ha formado alrededor de las canchas de tenis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:446
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b3c7d65b:

    # "It makes me pause a moment. This is my last chance to back out of what's already promising to be a very stressful day."
    "Me hace detenerme por un momento. Esta es mi última oportunidad de echarme para atrás y huir de lo que parece que será un día muy estresante."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:448
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a71e2c2e:

    # "But no, I've already committed. I'm going to be here for Nozomi and she's going to make it all right."
    "Pero no, tengo un compromiso. Estaré aquí para Nozomi y ella hará que todo esté bien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:451
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4a0060f0:

    # "I stroll over to the courts and scan the small crowd that seems to be made up of people from our school."
    "Merodeo cerca de las canchas y veo a la distancia una pequeña multitud que parece estar hecha de gente de nuestra escuela."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:453
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ab76e029:

    # "I let out a little smile as I pick out Nozomi from the group, and she seems to notice me at the same time as she flags me over." with dissolve
    "Dejo escapara una pequeña sonrisa al ver que Nozomi está en ese grupo, y parece haberme notado también, por lo que me saluda con la mano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:455
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_79ab6895:

    # n "Kyou! Over here~"
    n "¡Kyou! Por aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:456
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_422f74a7:

    # "As I go to join her, I'm painfully conscious of other's eyes upon me."
    "Al aproximarme, estoy dolorosamente consciente que hay otros ojos sobre mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:457
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b2910997:

    # "There's a couple girls I've seen talking to Nozomi in passing before, and at least a couple from our class."
    "Hay un par de chicas a las que he visto hablar con Nozomi antes, y al menos un par de nuestra clase."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:460
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4859e239:

    # "Including..." with dissolve
    "Incluyendo a..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:461
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0ca5a76c:

    # s "Hello, Kyou. Were it not for Nozomi's heads up I would be genuinely surprised to find you here."
    s "Hola, Kyou. De no haber sido por la advertencia de Nozomi, estaría genuinamente sorprendida de encontrarte aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:462
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9372c444:

    # "... Honestly I could say the same thing of you, Sayori. Shouldn't you be studying? I didn't think it being a Sunday would stop you."
    "... Honestamente, podría decirte lo mismo a ti, Sayori. ¿No deberías estar estudiando? No creí que el hecho de que sea domingo te detendría."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:463
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ec2b8b0a:

    # "Of course I don't say that out loud, and I hope my thoughts aren't plastered across my face as I nod to her in acknowledgement."
    "Claro que no lo digo en voz alta y, en vez de eso, le asiento con la cabeza esperando que mis pensamientos no estén plasmados en mi cara."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:464
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5abff55b:

    # s casual_folded smirk_right "Honestly, I had not taken you to be a fan of Miss Homura's." with dissolve
    s casual_folded smirk_right "Para ser franca, no esperaba que fueras fan de la señorita Homura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:465
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7649fbb5:

    # ks casual frown "I'm not!"
    ks casual frown "¡No lo soy!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:466
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3fc8e810:

    # "Ugh, fuck. The day's just started and she's already getting to me."
    "Aj, mierda. El día acaba de empezar y ya me está poniendo de los nervios."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:468
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b50b7b4d:

    # n "Ahaha, it's okay, Kyou~ Sayori's just teasing you." with dissolve
    n "Jajaja, tranquilo, Kyou. Sayori solo te está molestando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:469
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1c843c83:

    # s smile_right "Mhmhm, quite. I actually think it's admirable that you are making an effort to become more involved with your peers, Hiroko aside." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Jejeje, en efecto. En realidad, creo que es admirable que hagas un esfuerzo por involucrarte más con tus compañeros, dejando de lado lo de Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:471
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_dcf658f0:

    # ks neutral "Huh?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:472
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2b09370a:

    # "\"Were it not for Nozomi's heads up I would be genuinely surprised to find you here.\""
    "\"De no haber sido por la advertencia de Nozomi, estaría genuinamente sorprendida de encontrarte aquí.\""

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:473
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_38802184:

    # "What has she been telling them about me?"
    "¿Qué les ha estado diciendo de mí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:476
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_41e560cc:

    # n "Ah, I think they're getting ready to start." with dissolve
    n "Ah, creo que ya van a empezar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:479
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_dfbf945c:

    # "Nozomi draws our attention to the group of girls filing out of the changing rooms." with dissolve
    "Nozomi dirige nuestra atención al grupo de chicas que está saliendo de los vestidores." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:480
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d9289943:

    # "All of them are bedecked in their school's tennis uniforms, which are mostly white but for some allowances to show their affiliation."
    "Todas llevan puestos los uniformes de tenis de sus escuelas, los cuales son en su mayor parte blancos a excepción de algunos detalles para mostrar su afiliación."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:485
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0f3db39c:

    # "Hiroko's, for example, has a green trim to represent our school. I'd know she's supposed to be one of ours even if I wasn't acquainted with that little asshole." with dissolve
    "El de Hiroko, por ejemplo, tiene un corte verde que representa nuestra escuela. Sabría que que es una de las nuestras incluso si no conociera a esa pequeña cabrona." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:486
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f11f318e:

    # "Still, as the lot of them start their warm-up exercises, I have to ask..."
    "Aunque, mientras empiezan con el calentamiento, debo preguntar..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:487
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2edb4a46:

    # ks sigh "So how long is this gonna take?"
    ks sigh "Y ¿cuándo va a durar esto?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:938
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6aae41bd:

    # ns casual surprised "Huh?"
    ns casual surprised "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:489
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_779a6a7b:

    # ks frown "I-I mean, well, there's all these girls out here and they're all playing each other a bunch of times?"
    ks frown "B-bueno, es que, hay muchas chicas ahí afuera ¿y jugarán unas con otras un montón de veces?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:490
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_44e453b6:

    # ks "I thought tennis matches take hours."
    ks "Creí que los partidos de tenis duraban horas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:491
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7bfc7ba0:

    # "Nozomi smiles at my confusion."
    "Nozomi sonríe ante mi confusión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:942
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3e547238:

    # ns smile "It's a one-day tournament, so the matches will be much shorter."
    ns smile "Es un torneo de un día, por lo que los partidos serán mucho más cortos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:943
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_261cd9a1:

    # ss casual neutral "As I understand it, they are playing the early rounds in small groups, under a round robin format."
    ss casual neutral "Por lo que tengo entendido, jugarán las primeras rondas en grupos pequeños, con un formato round robin."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:944
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_209a5935:

    # ss "Each \"match\" is a truncated set, played to four games instead of six, with a tie break if neither has broken serve by then."
    ss "Cada \"partido \" es un set truncado de cuatro juegos en lugar de seis, con un desempate si ninguna ha quebrado un servicio para entonces."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:945
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_d430356d:

    # ns "Right. Then the top two in each group go on to the knockout rounds, where they'll play one full set per match."
    ns "Cierto. Luego, las mejores dos de cada grupo pasan a las rondas eliminatorias, donde jugarán un set completo por partido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:496
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9cd5613a:

    # ks sigh "That still sounds like a lot of tennis."
    ks sigh "Eso aún suena a mucho tenis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:497
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_40c5db53:

    # "Nozomi grins."
    "Nozomi sonríe."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:948
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_4f236721:

    # ns chuckle "It is. But I've known Hiroko to practice on the courts all day long, so I'm sure she can handle this~"
    ns chuckle "Lo es. Pero sé que Hiroko practica todo el día en las canchas, así que estoy segura de que puede con esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:499
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_da5b4ae0:

    # "I meant to imply we'll be stuck here all day, but either she didn't get it or shrugged off my meaning on purpose."
    "Quise insinuar que estaríamos atrapados aquí todo el día, pero o no me entendió o ignoró mi intención apropósito."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:951
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0c930366:

    # ss smile "Speaking of which, it seems they are about to begin." with dissolve
    ss smile "Hablando de eso, parece que están a punto de empezar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:502
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_67964f29:

    # "Sure enough, we see Hiroko assume a hunched position on the baseline as the umpire announces the start of the match..."
    "En efecto, vemos a Hiroko adoptar una posición encorvada en la línea de base cuando el juez anuncia el inicio del partido..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:506
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f73c14a4:

    # "My eyes pretty much glaze over for the next 20-30 minutes, but a raised cheer from Nozomi brings my focus back to the courtside action."
    "Mi mirada se pierde por los siguientes 20 o 30 minutos, pero un fuerte vitoreo de Nozomi devuelve mi atención a la acción que está ocurriendo en la cancha."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:508
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_67160bb2:

    # t "Game, set and match: Miss Homura. By four games to two."
    t "Juego, set y partido: Señorita Homura. Por cuatro juegos a dos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:510
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_74bb7d27:

    # "Hiroko wipes her forehead before shifting to smile in our direction." with dissolve
    "Hiroko se limpia la frente para luego mostrar una sonrisa en nuestra dirección." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:518
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3f34a0d1:

    # "However, as she walks towards us our eyes meet..."
    "Sin embargo, cuando camina hacia nosotros, nuestras miradas se cruzan..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:520
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0369e400:

    # "... And the smile somewhat fades from her face." with dissolve
    "... Y la sonrisa se desvanece de su rostro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:527
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b40e5d88:

    # n "You're doing great, Hiroko! That other girl couldn't handle you~" with dissolve
    n "¡Lo estás haciendo genial, Hiroko! Esa otra chica no pudo contigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:528
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ca05b7b4:

    # h smile_side "H'yeah, I'm a little pissed off I didn't break her in the first game. She ain't shit." with dissolve
    h smile_side "Je. Sí, me causa rabia no haberla destrozado el primer juego. Juega de la mierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:530
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_875773b2:

    # "Nozomi's distraction doesn't last long, as her eyes dart back to me again." with dissolve
    "La distracción de Nozomi no dura mucho, pues sus ojos vuelven a apuntar hacia mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:532
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0ee9437b:

    # h "I thought I saw you there. What's up with that?"
    h "Creí haberte visto. ¿Qué onda con eso?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:533
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_3770117c:

    # "Ugh, I can't tell her to fuck off with Nozomi and everyone else around."
    "Aj, no puedo mandarla al carajo con Nozomi y todos los demás alrededor."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:535
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_2228e294:

    # "S-so what do I..." with dissolve
    "E-entonces ¿qué ha-..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:536
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6f4bee9e:

    # n smile_side "So, um... Kyou and I had a little talk the other day." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pues, em... Kyou y yo tuvimos una pequeña charla el otro día." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:537
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7dfddcb3:

    # h frown_side "Ehh?" with dissolve
    h frown_side "¿Eeeh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:538
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_374b05ac:

    # "Nozomi clears her throat gently as she continues to justify me."
    "Nozomi se aclara la garganta con gentileza y continúa justificándome."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:539
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_f498dd33:

    # n sad_side "You remember when we were cleaning the classroom by ourselves? We sorta buried the hatchet then." with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Recuerdas cuando estábamos limpiando el salón nosotros solos? Digamos que hicimos las paces." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:541
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_57a206a4:

    # n sad_closed "A-and after that I figured it would be nice if I invited him to come to this? Bring him out of his shell a little bit?" with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Y d-después de eso, pensé que sería bueno invitarlo a esto. ¿Sacarlo un poco de su caparazón?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:542
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ec29a429:

    # "Hiroko just blinks at her, and I think I caught Sayori doing the same."
    "Hiroko simplemente le parpadea, y creo que vi a Sayori haciendo lo mismo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:544
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5b5e94a8:

    # "But then she just sighs and shrugs her shoulders." with dissolve
    "Pero luego suspira y se encoje de hombros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:995
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_601d9bc0:

    # h tennis_headhold2 sleeptalk "'Kay, whatever. I don't really have time for this shit." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 sleeptalk "Ta’ bien, como sea. No tengo tiempo para esta mierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:996
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_875c8328:

    # n smile_side "Right. I think they're calling for you." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Cierto. Creo que te están llamando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:547
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9b45a458:

    # h tennis_armup smile_side "Wish me luck~" with dissolve
    h tennis_armup smile_side "Deséenme suerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:552
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ab201045:

    # "As Hiroko goes to ready for her next match, I notice Sayori's eyes on me."
    "Mientras Hiroko se alista para el siguiente partido, noto que Sayori tiene sus ojos en mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1003
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8ba6af4e:

    # ss neutral "You are being characteristically quiet there, Kyou. Any thoughts?"
    ss neutral "Has estado característicamente callado, Kyou. ¿Alguna opinión?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:554
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ab62fc87:

    # ks surprised "H-huh?"
    ks surprised "¿E-eh?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:555
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_74a71c75:

