    # "Hiroko's not normally one for holding back, but she seems to be considering her words this time."
    "Hiroko no suele ser de las que se contienen, pero esta vez parece estar pensando sus palabras."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1102
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6b36026c:

    # h "Gotta admit, there's something different about you tonight, and I ain't just talking about your shitty singing."
    h "Tengo que admitirlo, hoy hay algo diferente en ti, y no solo estoy hablando de tu canto de mierda."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1105
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8ea49137:

    # h neutral "Dunno how I feel about it yet." with dissolve
    h neutral "Aún no sé cómo me siento al respecto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1106
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e9ef7f31:

    # n smile_side "He's not going to change everything in one night, but do you think you can ease off him now? Just a little?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "No va a cambiar por completo en una noche, pero ¿crees que podrías calmarte un poco con él? ¿Solo un poquito?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1109
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_021b844d:

    # "Hiroko shifts her eyes from me to Nozomi's, then lets out a little sigh." with dissolve
    "Hiroko me quita los ojos de encima para mirar a Nozomi, luego suelta un pequeño suspiro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1110
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1febc6be:

    # h sleeptalk "I guess? Shit's weird, is all." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "¿Supongo? Esta mierda es rara, eso es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_7701656f:

    # h smile_side "Anyway, I'm beat." with dissolve
    h smile_side "Como sea, estoy agotada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1112
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_54f8d267:

    # r smug_side "After the weekend you've just had? I'm shocked." with dissolve
    r smug_side "¿Después de un fin de semana así? Estoy impactada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1526
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5b1839e5:

    # h casual_headhold2 happy_closed "H'yeah~ So, I'm outta here." with dissolve
    h casual_headhold2 happy_closed "Seh. Bueno, ya me voy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1115
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_267c3fe0:

    # "Our group say their farewells as Hiroko and the other girls begin to part from us." with dissolve
    "Nuestro grupo se despide y Hiroko y la otra chica comienzan a alejarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1118
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_e66fa62a:

    # r smile_side "Hey, Nozo, thanks for inviting me. I think I needed this." with dissolve
    r smile_side "Ey, Nozo, gracias por invitarme. Creo que necesitaba esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1119
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_42b6d656:

    # n laugh "Aw, it's been a pleasure, Risa~" with dissolve
    n laugh "Oh, fue un placer, Risa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1120
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b7e40213:

    # r smile "And Kyou?" with dissolve
    r smile "¿Y Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1122
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_09214f0b:

    # ks neutral "Hm?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1123
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_824e208b:

    # r grin "It was fun to meet you~ Don't be a stranger, okay?" with dissolve
    r grin "Fue divertido conocerte. No seas un extraño, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1125
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b74e8876:

    # "... Don't complicate how I feel about you, goddammit." with dissolve
    "... No compliques lo que siento por ti, maldita sea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1126
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_45dadc80:

    # r smile_side "Alright, catch you later." with dissolve
    r smile_side "Muy bien, hasta luego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1127
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_080dd1b2:

    # n laugh "Take care, Risa~" with dissolve
    n laugh "Cuídate, Risa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1136
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c14e9605:

    # "As Risa parts ways from us, a hand raised in farewell, I turn to Nozomi as I suddenly realize." with dissolve
    "Mientras Risa se aleja sacudiendo una mano, me doy la vuelta hacia Nozomi, dándome cuanta de repente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1518
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_de900849:

    # n front chuckle "And then there were two." with dissolve
    n front chuckle "Ya nomás me quedan dos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1138
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_55a24b2a:

    # "We're the only ones left."
    "Somos los únicos que quedan."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1139
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5f000086:

    # n laugh "Ahahahahaha~" with dissolve
    n laugh "Jajajajajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1140
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a77aa5c1:

    # ks smile blush "Wh- what's so funny?"
    ks smile blush "¿Qu- qué es tan gracioso?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1141
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5077cce4:

    # "Nozomi just continues to giggle a few moments longer, before shaking her head with a hand to her mouth."
    "Nozomi se ríe un poco más, para luego sacudir la cabeza con una mano cubriendo su boca."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1142
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a1b2719b:

    # n side laugh blush "O-oh, Kyou, hahaha... Did you listen to yourself earlier?" with dissolve
    n side laugh blush "O-oh, Kyou, jajaja... ¿Te escuchaste hace rato?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1143
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_8d5dbf96:

    # ks sigh noblush "Uh, what do you mean by that?"
    ks sigh noblush "¿Eh, a qué te refieres?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1144
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9ec6bd20:

    # "She grins."
    "Me sonríe."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1145
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_186e1fb5:

    # n smile "Back in the karaoke booth? Singing your heart out?" with dissolve
    n smile "¿En la sala de karaoke? ¿Cuando estabas cantando con el corazón?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1146
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_48be0253:

    # "My mind snaps back to those moments, as if I were being pulled back into that booth."
    "Mi mente regresa de golpe a esos momentos, como si me hubieran arrastrado de regreso a ese cuarto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1147
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_294ea362:

    # ks frown "That was so fucking weird."
    ks frown "Ay, mierda, eso estuvo muy raro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1149
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6c7d3dba:

    # "Nozomi beams as she brings her hands together for an excited clap." with dissolve
    "Con su rostro aún irradiando, Nozomi junta sus manos, llena de emoción." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1150
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_66c33e50:

    # n noblush "So while I had you hypnotized the other day, I said you would feel like a GOD of karaoke as soon as you were in a karaoke booth and had a mic in your hands!" with dissolve
    n noblush "¡Pues, cuando te hipnoticé el otro día, te dije que te sentirías como un DIOS del karaoke cuanto estuvieras en la sala y tuvieras el micro en tus manos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1151
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_03cde686:

    # ks surprised "Is that a fact?"
    ks surprised "¿Lo dices en serio?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1152
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b1234cc1:

    # "Still thinking about it, I barely manage to recall any moment when I was actually holding a mic."
    "Ahora que lo pienso, apenas puedo recordar un solo momento en el que estuviera sujetando un micro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1153
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ec8b0322:

    # n side laugh "I told you to be full of confidence and self-belief that you were the greatest karaoke singer the world had ever seen~" with dissolve
    n side laugh "Te dije que te llenaras confianza y que creyeras que eres el cantante de karaoke más grande que el mundo haya visto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1154
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_5d9d3838:

    # n front shocked "And oh my gosh, you absolutely RAN with that suggestion didn't you?" with dissolve
    n front shocked "Y, por Dios, te tomaste MUY en serio esa sugestión, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6d501c32:

    # ks "Y-... Yeah."
    ks "S-... Sí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1156
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_54f9f651:

    # "I ran so much I barely knew where I was going."
    "Me la tomé tan enserio que apenas sabía lo que estaba pasando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1161
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_40df41cf:

    # n "Doesn't all this excite you, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n "¿No te pone ansioso, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1162
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6f31d5d2:

    # "My mind's racing, but Nozomi doesn't wait for me to answer."
    "La cabeza me da vueltas, pero Nozomi no espera a que conteste."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1163
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6a2d546b:

    # n side smile_side "I can make you forget things. I can convince you I'm invisible..." with dissolve
    n side smile_side "Puedo hacerte olvidar cosas. Puedo convencerte de que soy invisible..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1164
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_fac31cea:

    # n laugh "I can make you the BEST at karaoke!" with dissolve
    n laugh "¡Puedo hacerte el MEJOR en karaoke!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1165
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_13b5990b:

    # n sad_side "Um, well... I can make you THINK you're the best. I guess it's important to know there is a limit to my power." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Em, bueno... puedo hacerte CREER que eres el mejor. Supongo que es importante saber que mi poder tiene límites." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1166
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_ba5749ba:

    # n laugh "B-but still, what a RUSH!" with dissolve
    n laugh "P-pero, aun así, ¡qué EMOCIÓN!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1167
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_851e4639:

    # "I feel like I need to say something."
    "Siento que tengo que decir algo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1596
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_af3f136c:

    # n front2 loving "I can't imagine what you must be feeling, Kyou. Being able to absorb hypnotic suggestions as fully as you can." with dissolve
    n front2 loving "No me puedo imaginar lo que debes estar sintiendo, Kyou. Ser capaz de absorber sugestiones hipnóticas tan plenamente como tú." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1169
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_aa75a6a3:

    # n chuckle blush "Honestly... U-um, I almost wish I was in your shoes." with dissolve
    n chuckle blush "Honestamente... E-em, casi desearía estar en tus zapatos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1170
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_823c1a92:

    # n smile "But being able to trance you, and delight in your reactions, is its own reward." with dissolve
    n smile "Pero poder ponerte en trance y deleitarme con tus reacciones es una recompensa en sí misma." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1171
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_78b341bc:

    # "But it's so hard to think straight when Nozomi's getting this excited about hypnotizing me."
    "Pero es difícil pensar con claridad cuando Nozomi está tan emocionada por hipnotizarme."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1172
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_03d14527:

    # n side laugh "Ahahaha, I'm sorry! I'll calm down." with dissolve
    n side laugh "¡Jajajaja, perdón! Ya me calmo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1173
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_786a94bc:

    # "She takes a breath and smiles at me, still glowing."
    "Toma aire y me sonríe, aún brillando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1174
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c5cd47e1:

    # n side smile "I need to get home, but first, I wanted to check in with you." with dissolve
    n side smile "Debo irme a casa, pero primero, quería ver cómo estabas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1175
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6315d60d:

    # "Here. This is my chance to tell her... whatever it is I need to say."
    "Ahora. Esta es mi oportunidad de decirle... lo que sea que necesite decirle."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1176
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_350b1991:

    # n smile_side "I know what we said before, about letting me hypnotize you, but I don't know how you really felt about doing all this with everyone." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Sé lo que dijimos antes sobre dejarme hipnotizarte, pero no sé cómo te sentiste realmente haciendo todo esto con nosotras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1177
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0eae802b:

    # n front concerned "And, to be honest, I know I sort of ambushed you with it the other night." with dissolve
    n front concerned "Y, para ser franca, creo que te embosqué con esto la otra noche." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1178
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_a7c1414a:

    # n sigh "You stepped up, and you really rose to the occasion tonight, but still..." with dissolve
    n sigh "Te armaste de valor y lo hiciste muy bien, pero, aun así..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1179
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_c25f74d4:

    # n concerned "This must have been so out of your comfort zone." with dissolve
    n concerned "Esto debió estar muy fuera de tu zona de confort." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1180
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_b2d4e339:

    # n neutral "I want to do so much more of this with you, but please don't feel pressured or anything." with dissolve
    n neutral "Hay tanto que aún quiero hacer contigo, pero, por favor, no te sientas presionado ni nada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1181
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_dc0f5cad:

    # n side sad "Just... You're really okay with me doing this, aren't you?" with dissolve
    n side sad "Solo... Sí te parece bien que haga esto, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1196
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_9fa8dd5e:

    # "I can't... I can't refuse this woman."
    "No puedo... no puedo reusarme a esta mujer."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1197
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_6d6e1b25:

    # "My thoughts might be muddled, but out of everything one thing still shines clearly."
    "Mis pensamientos serán un embrollo, pero entre todo eso hay una cosa que brilla con claridad."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_96f947c1:

    # "It feels so good to be hypnotized by Nozomi..." with dissolve
    "Se siente muy bien ser hipnotizado por Nozomi..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1199
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_916be38c:

    # "So why would I refuse her?"
    "¿Por qué me reusaría?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1204
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_87b1660b:

    # "And for my answer, Nozomi lets out a squeal and gives me a tight, but quick, hug." with dissolve
    "Y con mi respuesta, Nozomi suelta un chillido y me da un rápido y fuerte abrazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1205
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_1241cf8e:

    # n happy "Okay, I just wanted to make extra sure." with dissolve
    n happy "Muy bien, solo quería estar extra segura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1206
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_664ee910:

    # n side smile "Alright, well, I'll see you in class tomorrow, Kyou!" with dissolve
    n side smile "¡Muy bien, te veo en clase mañana, Kyou!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1207
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_0de2a5a6:

    # n laugh "Have a good night~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    n laugh "Ten una linda noche. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1209
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Reversal_449e162a:

    # "(( To be continued! ))" with dissolve
    "((¡Continuará!))" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1219
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1a5b0cfc:

    # "Today feels like it's going to be a good day."
    "Siento que hoy será un buen día."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1220
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8beab591:

    # "The sun's out, it's a Sunday and I have the house to myself yet again."
    "El sol ha salido, es domingo y, nuevamente, tengo la casa para mí solo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1221
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_60c0ad16:

    # "If only..."
    "Si tan solo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1223
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_370fa1f9:

    # "... What was that? I heard something downstairs."
    "... ¿Qué fue eso? Oí un ruido ahí abajo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1224
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0fab0158:

    # "Dad left the house before I was out of bed. But that definitely came from inside."
    "Papá se fue antes de que me levantara de la cama. Pero eso definitivamente vino de adentro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1226
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3c9405bf:

    # ks casual frown "H... hello?"
    ks casual frown "¿Ho... hola?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1227
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd1f16d4:

    # "Shit, the door's ajar? Did dad somehow forget to close on his way out? What the hell?!"
    "Mierda, ¿la puerta está entreabierta? ¿Papá olvidó cerrarla cuando iba de salida? ¡¿Qué demonios?!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1228
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d9a98441:

    # "... Or maybe someone forced their way in?"
    "... ¿O tal vez alguien entró a la fuerza?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1230
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b5240b2c:

    # "Closing the door, I wheel around as my eyes scan the room."
    "Tras cerrar la puerta, me doy media vuelta, escaneando la habitación."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1231
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3d5bcf33:

    # "Sure feels like someone's watching me right now."
    "Siento que alguien me está observando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1232
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b1c3b923:

    # "... Nah come on, this is no time to panic. Dad just left the door open."
    "... Nah, vamos, que no cunda el pánico. Papá simplemente dejó la puerta abierta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1233
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1264e50b:

    # "I'll just go from room to room and check the corners. Then I can get on with my day."
    "Solo iré de habitación en habitación a revisar las esquinas. Luego podré seguir con mi día."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1235
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_86e7ca84:

    # "See? Not a th..."
    "¿Ves? No hay n..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1236
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_63a2930a:

    # ks casual angry "Hey! Who's there?"
    ks casual angry "¡Ey! ¿Quién anda ahí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1728
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f7913b3f:

    # "I shout into the kitchen. It looked empty at first glance, but I can see a shadow cast by the counter."
    "Le grito al comedor. Parecía vacío a simple vista, pero puedo ver una sombra en la esquina de la cocina."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1238
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_46886630:

    # "I might have written it off as paranoia, but I definitely saw it move as soon as I shouted."
    "Tal vez solo haya sido paranoia, pero definitivamente la vi moverse cuando grité."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1239
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_51688b55:

    # ks "I'm... I'm calling the cops!"
    ks "Lla-... ¡llamaré a la policía!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1243
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_980d8bb5:

    # "Just then a figure jumps out from their hiding place and sprints past me with a quickness I wasn't expecting."
    "De pronto, una figura salta de su escondite y corre con una inesperada velocidad."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1244
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5146181f:

    # ks "H-hey!"
    ks "¡O-oye!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1252
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f8ccbff0:

    # "I double back into the living room in time to cut off their escape towards the front door, and they change direction to instead rush up the stairs."
    "Regreso a la sala a tiempo para bloquearle la puerta principal, pero cambia de dirección y sube por las escaleras."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1254
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a58c44ee:

    # "The adrenaline pumping in me, I give chase as I see them up ahead."
    "La adrenalina corre por mis venas y comienzo a perseguirlo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1255
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f9a5a5c6:

    # "Obviously flustered by my pursuit, they seem to panic as they dash into the first room with an open door..."
    "Obviamente nervioso por mi persecución, parece entrar en pánico y corre a la primera habitación que encuentra con una puerta abierta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1259
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b7fc3a13:

    # "... The bathroom."
    "... El baño."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1260
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ab43759a:

    # ks casual angry "H-hah. What do you think you're doing in my house?"
    ks casual angry "Ajá. ¿Qué crees que estás haciendo en mi casa?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1264
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb2cf764:

    # n "..."
    n "..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1266
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c5d9e873:

    # "It's a girl?"
    "¿Es una chica?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1267
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3a577cb3:

    # n "D- dammit. I thought you were gone."
    n "M-maldición. Creí que te habías ido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1268
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_58315ce6:

    # ks frown "What?"
    ks frown "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1270
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_deaba70d:

    # n side frown "Well... it doesn't matter. You need to let me go." with dissolve
    n side frown "Bueno... eso no importa. Debes dejarme ir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1271
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5eed5c2e:

    # "Shit, it doesn't take a genius to figure out what's going on here."
    "Mierda, no hay que ser un genio para darse cuenta de qué está pasando aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1273
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_75b85dcd:

    # ks "What, you think you can break into our house and rob us? And I'll let you go?"
    ks "¿Qué? ¿Crees que puedes allanar nuestra casa y robarnos? ¿Y que te dejaré ir?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1274
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b4ce5aba:

    # ks "Gimme one reason why I shouldn't call the cops."
    ks "Dame una razón para no llamar a la policía."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1275
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b81354f8:

    # "Our would-be cat burglar just sneers at me."
    "La pequeña rata simplemente se burla."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1276
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3d3276f7:

    # n front frown "Hah, that's a good one. Have you ever dealt with the cops in this town?" with dissolve
    n front frown "Ja, buena esa. ¿Has intentado lidiar con la policía de esta ciudad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1277
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f4d8bcae:

    # n smirk "And besides, do you really think they'll believe you telling them I was here to rob you?" with dissolve
    n smirk "Y además, ¿de verdad piensas que te creerán si les dices que vine a robarles?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1278
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5d3ccba9:

    # ks "Eh? Why wouldn't they?"
    ks "¿Eh? ¿Por qué no?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1695
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2c34519a:

    # n side rolleyes "Oh, let's see..." with dissolve
    n side rolleyes "Oh, veamos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1280
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fc710068:

    # n side frown_side "You idiots left your door open, so there's no forced entry. Who's to say you didn't let me in, huh?" with dissolve
    n side frown_side "Ustedes, idiotas, dejaron la puerta abierta, por lo que no hay entrada forzada. ¿Quién dice que no me dejaron entrar, eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1281
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c9641a07:

    # ks "Uh... me?"
    ks "Eh... ¿yo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1282
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_869c0e26:

    # n smile "Is that right? Well go ahead and call them. We'll see what they say when I tell them what you did." with dissolve
    n smile "¿En serio? Pues adelante, llámalos. Ya veremos qué dicen cuando les cuente lo que hiciste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1283
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_77c80664:

    # ks frown "What... what I did?"
    ks frown "¿Lo que... yo hice?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1284
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ce33720b:

    # n front smirk "If you call them, you'll find out." with dissolve
    n front smirk "Si los llamas, lo averiguarás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1285
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ea624409:

    # "Ugh, this smug bitch. But I know what she's saying: It's her word against mine..."
    "Ay, perra engreída. Pero entiendo lo que dice: Es su palabra contra la mía..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1286
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_056745d6:

    # "She really thinks she can break into my home and no one will punish her."
    "De verdad cree que puede irrumpir en mi hogar y que nadie va a castigarla."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1287
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c211b34a:

    # "And it sounds to me like it's not the first time she's broken and entered."
    "Y me suena a que no es la primera vez que entra."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1288
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_67ef6fe9:

    # "Come to think of it, our neighborhood's had a wave of burglaries recently..."
    "Ahora que lo pienso, nuestro vecindario ha tenido una ola de robos recientemente..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1289
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_742b2956:

    # n chuckle "Now, if you don't mind..." with dissolve
    n chuckle "Ahora, si no te importa..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1295
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a2ef355c:

    # "And now she tries to push past me, thinking she's made her point. But I grab her arm as I notice her bulging handbag." with dissolve
    "Y ahora intenta burlarme, creyendo que dejó claro su punto. Pero la tomo del brazo al darme cuenta de su bolso abultado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1708
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9f09cda5:

    # n determined "Out of my way."
    n determined "Fuera de mi camino."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1709
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_faf1a4c5:

    # ks casual frown "What's in the bag?"
    ks casual frown "¿Qué hay en el bolso?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1300
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5913d9aa:

    # n angry "None of your beeswax! Now move or I'll scream!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡¿Qué te importa?! ¡Ahora muévete o gritaré!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1303
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_08ca57a9:

    # "Keeping hold of her, I glare into her eyes as I pull out a penlight from my pants pocket."
    "Sin soltarla, la miro a los ojos y saco del bolsillo de mi pantalón una pluma linterna."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1304
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_22a983a8:

    # ks "H-how about taking a look at this instead?"
    ks "¿Qu-qué tal si mejor le das un vistazo a esto?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1305
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7e650137:

    # n determined "Uh, what?" with dissolve
    n determined "Eh, ¿qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1309
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_debb4c02:

    # "Maybe this routine's worked for her before when she was caught breaking into other people's homes..."
    "Esa rutina le habrá funcionado antes cuando la atraparon allanando las casas de otros."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1311
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f9dbe7a3:

    # ks "Just look up, that's all I'm asking."
    ks "Solo mira aquí arriba, eso es todo lo que te pido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1312
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4b176073:

    # "But I'm gonna make sure this is the last time she ever pulls this shit."
    "Pero me aseguraré de que esta sea la última vez que hace esta mierda."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1654
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d34435ba:

    # n frown "N-no, just let go of me, or I'll..."
    n frown "N-no, solo déjame ir o voy a..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1315
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3ac5ef1c:

    # "After all..."
    "Después de todo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1317
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f841d2aa:

    # ks "Just look at the light. You might already notice how it catches your attention."
    ks "Solo mira la luz. Tal vez ya te de diste cuenta de cómo atrapa tu atención."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1318
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_640c383a:

    # "She's never dealt with someone like me before..."
    "Nunca se había enfrentado a alguien como yo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1320
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f0cc9d30:

    # ks "Perhaps you're already becoming curious. Maybe you can stay a bit longer after all, huh?"
    ks "Quizá ya te está dando curiosidad. Tal vez puedas quedarte un rato más."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1321
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8934a6cc:

    # "That is to say..."
    "Es decir..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1322
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_969169de:

    # n neutral "What are you..." with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Qué estás..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1324
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe5f55c8:

    # ks "Shh, don't worry about what I'm doing. Just focus on the light now."
    ks "Shh, no te preocupes por qué estoy haciendo. Solo concéntrate en la luz."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1325
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bfdd101f:

    # "A master hypnotist!"
    "¡A un hipnotista maestro!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1327
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a87f1510:

    # ks "Focus, and even if it makes you tired to look up at the light, even if you feel your eyelids weigh down on you..."
    ks "Concéntrate, y aunque estés cansada de mirar la luz, aunque sientas que los párpados te pesan..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1329
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_58dcf611:

    # ks "Keep looking into the light, keep focusing, keep breathing..."
    ks "Sigue mirando la luz, sigue concentrándote, sigue respirando..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1757
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a12a59e8:

    # ks "Breathing nice and relaxed, becoming more and more focused, more and more sleepy..."
    ks "Respira y relájate. Cada vez más concentrada. Cada vez sientes más y más sueño..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1336
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_37fbb428:

    # "My hand moves up from the thief's arm and moves to hold her shoulder as I watch her struggle to stay awake, fascinated by my toy in spite of herself."
    "Mi mano suelta el brazo de la ladronzuela para sujetar su hombro. Puedo ver que le cuesta permanecer despierta, fascinada por mi juguete, quiera o no."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1338
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_92ff6fcd:

    # ks "Feeling so good. So sleepy. So relaxed watching the pretty light there..."
    ks "Se siente muy bien. Sientes tanto sueño. Te sientes tan relajada al mirar esa bonita luz..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1769
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_accc42ca:

    # ks "And if you find your eyes becoming too tired to keep open, then that's alright. It's alright to close them and let yourself go deeper for me."
    ks "Y si tus ojos están muy cansados para abrirlos, está perfectamente bien. Está bien cerrarlos y dejarte llevar, cada vez más profundo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1775
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ceaf7e53:

    # ks "That's right. Deep asleep, drifting deeper, focusing so much on my words now. Letting them take you deeper and deeper."
    ks "Eso es. Profundamente dormida, más y más profundo, muy concentrada en mis palabras. Deja que te lleven más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1346
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_70d70705:

    # "I grin as her head droops, the cat burglar's mind now completely at my mercy."
    "Sonrío al ver su cabeza caer. La mente de esta rata ahora está a mi merced."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1347
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b49e1161:

    # "Now I'll make her sorry she ever set foot in my house."
    "Haré que lamente haber puesto un pie en mi casa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1348
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2ae5e78b:

    # ks "And as you go so deep for me, focusing so much on my words, perhaps you'll subconsciously notice how true my words are for you."
    ks "Y mientras caes tan profundo, prestando mucha atención a mis palabras, quizá notes subconscientemente lo ciertas que son mis palabras."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1349
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8fe55da3:

    # ks "So now I'm going to put to you that stealing is a terrible wrong, and even the mere thought of stealing from another person makes you feel utterly disgusted."
    ks "Y ahora voy a plantearte que robar está terriblemente mal, y la mera idea de robarle a otra persona te repugna."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1350
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_32dc853f:

    # ks "It's so wrong and vile to steal, isn't it?"
    ks "Robar es malo y ruin, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1351
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2006025d:

    # n sleeptalk "Yes... wrong and vile..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Sí... malo y ruin..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1353
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_59a404d8:

    # ks "So very wrong. So if you realized you had something that belonged to me, you would be very committed to righting that wrong, wouldn't you?" with dissolve
    ks "Muy, muy malo. Por lo que, si descubrieras que tienes algo que me pertenece, corregirías ese error de inmediato, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1354
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5ab683f6:

    # n sleeptalk "Yes... very committed." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Sí... de inmediato." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1356
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2b1ab896:

    # "With a smirk, I continue to take her down the path of atonement." with dissolve
    "Con una sonrisa, continúo guiándola por el camino de la expiación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b5acfe65:

    # "I mean, just re-educating a thief isn't enough."
    "Sin embargo, reeducar a una ladrona no es suficiente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7540e490:

    # "She needs to pay for what she's done."
    "Debe pagar por lo que ha hecho."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1358
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_92c485c8:

    # ks smirk "That's right, and accepting this truth can only take you deeper into trance. More focused on my words. More accepting of the truth."
    ks smirk "Eso es, y aceptar estas verdades te hace ir más profundo. Entre más te concentras en mis palabras, más aceptas la verdad."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1359
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_15562a27:

    # ks "So then, I want to suggest to you another truth: Everything that I say is mine, really is mine."
    ks "Y ahora quiero sugerirte otra verdad: Todo lo que diga que es mío, es mío."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1360
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_05cd246d:

    # ks "There's no need to question anything that I claim belongs to me. Because everything that I say is mine, really is mine."
    ks "No hace falta cuestionar nada que reclame como mi pertenencia. Porque todo lo que diga que es mío, es mío."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1361
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5ff511d0:

    # ks "And you know how wrong it is to have anything that belongs to me, don't you?"
    ks "Y sabes lo mal que está tener algo que me pertenezca, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1362
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d16b751e:

    # n sleeptalk "Y... yes..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "S... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1364
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2ae7b15c:

    # ks "So very wrong. Now in a moment we're going to wake you back up again, back to your conscious mind." with dissolve
    ks "Muy, muy mal. Y en un momento te vamos a despertar y estarás consciente de nuevo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1365
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8377e6b8:

    # ks "But even as you wake, you will hold these truths you just heard deep in your subconscious. Knowing how true and right they are."
    ks "Pero, aunque estés despierta, te aferrarás las verdades que escuchaste en lo profundo de tu subconsciente, sabiendo lo ciertas y correctas que son."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1366
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6ab5419c:

    # ks "Understand?"
    ks "¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1367
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_602bebda:

    # n sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1369
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d428ad36:

    # ks "Good, now waking up as I count to three. Becoming more awake and aware and refreshed with each number I count." with dissolve
    ks "Bien, ahora despierta a la cuenta de tres. Estarás más despierta y consciente y fresca con cada número." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_021f718a:

    # ks "One, taking a nice deep breath, becoming more aware."
    ks "Uno, respira hondo, cada vez más consciente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1372
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd67f581:

    # ks "Two, feeling more awake and alert, accepting the truth of my words..."
    ks "Dos, ya te sientes más despierta y alerta, aceptando la verdad de mis palabras..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ca353944:

    # ks "And three, wide awake now!"
    ks "Y tres, ¡despierta ahora!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1377
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b1638b4c:

    # "I release her from my grip and snap my fingers in front of her nose as she jumps in alarm." with vpunch
    "La suelto y chasqueo los dedos delante de su nariz lo cual la hace dar un sobresalto." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1826
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8600de6b:

    # n "W-wh-wh-wait, what's going on?! What did you do to me?"
    n "¡¿Q-qu-qu-e-espera, qué está pasando?! ¿Qué me hiciste?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1379
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dc0daf54:

    # "Having slipped my penlight back in my pocket, I simply smile and shrug at her."
    "Habiendo devuelto mi linterna a mi bolsillo, simplemente me encojo de hombros."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1828
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_854f6262:

    # ks casual smirk "I didn't do anything. But aren't you gonna explain what you're doing in my house?"
    ks casual smirk "Yo no hice nada. Pero ¿no vas a explicar qué estás haciendo en mi casa?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1381
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_023c1fd1:

    # n irritated "No, now like I said you need to get out of my way." with dissolve
    n irritated "No. Ahora, como dije, fuera de mi camino." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1382
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3418d679:

    # ks "Wait a minute. I asked you a question, remember?"
    ks "No tan rápido. Te hice una pregunta, ¿recuerdas?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1383
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3c8280f6:

    # n side frown "And I said it's..." with dissolve
    n side frown "Y yo dije ¿qué te..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1384
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_87ceff9d:

    # n "I- it's..."
    n "T-te..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1386
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_241d0dd9:

    # "Just then her eyes practically pop out of her head as a new realization dawns on her." with dissolve
    "Y entonces sus ojos prácticamente saltan de sus cuencas al darse cuenta de lo que está pasando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1387
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5a6b072d:

    # ks "What's in the bag, you little thief?"
    ks "¿Qué hay en la bolsa, pequeña ladronzuela?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1389
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_db399882:

    # "She whimpers as she frantically pops her handbag open and a portable games console practically bursts out of there." with dissolve
    "Gimotea abriendo frenéticamente su bolso y una consola de videojuegos portátil prácticamente sale disparada de ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1390
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ba93fdbc:

    # "... She must have swiped it from our living room while she was in there, then started looking for more loot before I disturbed her."
    "... Debe haberla tomado de nuestra sala mientras estaba ahí, y luego empezó a buscar más botín antes de que la interrumpiera."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1391
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b2af337f:

    # n "O-o-oh- OH MY GOD WHAT HAVE I DONE!?"
    n "O-o-oh- ¡OH, POR DIOS! ¿¡QUÉ HE HECHO!?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1392
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8fe12f14:

    # "She trembles on the spot and doesn't resist me reaching over and swiping the console from her bag."
    "Se pone a temblar y no se resiste cuando tomo la consola."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_40955922:

    # ks frown "Alright, I'm gonna put this back and then we're gonna have a chat about your kleptomania, okay?"
    ks frown "Muy bien, pondré esto donde estaba y luego tendremos una charla sobre tu cleptomanía, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1397
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1c7bc1b7:

    # "Leading her back downstairs, I can practically feel the guilt dripping off of her."
