translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fb3a0d93:

    # "And off she goes. Leaving me alone with my thoughts yet again."
    "Y allá va. Dejándome solo con mis pensamientos una vez más."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1704
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7e771913:

    # "To be continued."
    "Continuará."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1710
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_634d856b:

    # "A hush descends upon the assembled crowd."
    "El silencio se apodera del público."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1711
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_6fd0951c:

    # "It's been a long day of competitive tennis, but as I suck in a breath I watch what could be the last bit of action."
    "Ha sido un largo día de tenis competitivo, pero, tomando aire, observo lo que podría ser el momento final."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1714
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ab1310f7:

    # "Hiroko Homura, our school's tennis star, is serving for match point." with dissolve
    "Hiroko Homura, la estrella de tenis de nuestra escuela, servirá en busca del punto de juego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1716
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1cfaf310:

    # "She looks calm and collected as she bounces her ball off the floor, eyes locked on her somewhat flustered-looking opponent."
    "Luciendo calmada y serena, rebota la pelota contra el suelo, ojos fijos en su oponente de aspecto nervioso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_6f6b0727:

    # "A moment later, she grips the ball in her hand before tossing it vertically in the air and... {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    "Un momento después, toma la bola en su mano, la arroja verticalmente al aire y... {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1720
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_b63575de:

    # extend "with perfect form hits a booming serve out wide." with vpunch
    extend "con perfecta técnica, dispara un servicio explosivo muy abierto." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1722
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e11550be:

    # "The girl on the other end doesn't return Hiroko's serve so much as parries it, but it's enough to send the ball across court."
    "La chica del otro extremo, más que devolverlo, detiene el servicio de Hiroko, pero es suficiente para mandar la pelota al otro lado de la cancha."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_207adba2:

    # "It's enough to make the assembled onlookers gasp as the ball unexpectedly clips the net and bounces low on Hiroko's side."
    "Es suficiente para hacer a los espectadores exclamar, pues la pelota roza inesperadamente la red y rebota muy al centro del lado de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1727
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_685cfcbc:

    # "But having rushed to the net, she's already in a position to crouch down and half-volley it back."
    "Pero ella, tras haberse abalanzado contra la red, ya se encuentra en posición para agacharse y salvarla."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1729
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_61464a61:

    # "It was all she could do with that, really, and her opponent takes advantage of her rare piece of luck by hitting a lobbed shot that leaves Hiroko stranded."
    "Apenas pudo lograrlo, y su oponente aprovecha su golpe de suerte para dar un potente disparo que deja a Hiroko varada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1732
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_730dd74e:

    # "... Or so we thought."
    "... O eso creímos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1734
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_cc3dc9c3:

    # h "Kyaa!" with vpunch
    h "¡Fuaa!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1735
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_3fe00316:

    # "Hiroko must have known immediately what was coming, and had already started dashing back to the baseline with alarming speed."
    "Hiroko debió saber de inmediato que eso pasaría, y ya había empezado a correr de vuelta a la línea de base con una velocidad alarmante."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_55f9c922:

    # "Her eye on the ball the entire time, she's able to get back and execute an overhead smash on a ball that really should've beaten someone of her height."
    "Sin quitar el ojo de la bola, consigue regresar y ejecutar un fuerte remate que debería ser imposible para alguien de su estatura."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1737
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1b9b1785:

    # "The other girl... well, it's not like she stopped trying, even at the death and staring down the barrel of a humiliating \"bagel\" defeat..."
    "La otra chica... bueno, claro que no dejó de intentarlo, por más que esté al borde de una humillante derrota tipo \"bagel\"..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1833
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_15bdac23:

    # "But she can't take the sting out of Hiroko's powerful return, and her reply sails wildly off court."
    "Pero no puede hacer nada contra la el poderoso tiro de Hiroko, y su respuesta sale volando fuera de la cancha."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1742
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2aa57a8e:

    # t "Out!"
    t "¡Fuera!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1745
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e419caf8:

    # t "Game, set and match: Miss Homura. By six games to love." with dissolve
    t "Juego, set y partido: Señorita Homura. Con seis juegos a cero." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1748
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ba3221a1:

    # "Hiroko breaks into a smile as she turns and waves towards us in victory, before walking to the net to shake hands with her crestfallen opponent."
    "Una sonrisa se dibuja en el rostro de Hiroko, y entonces ella se da la vuelta y nos saluda victoriosa, para luego caminar hacia la red y darle la mano a su cabizbaja oponente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1752
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_189825c5:

    # "With this tournament being held at our school there's a partisan crowd but even so, there's some sympathy to spare for that other girl."
    "Como que el torneo tiene lugar en nuestra escuela, hay una audiencia parcial, pero aun así, hay algo de simpatía por la otra chica."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1753
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_215ea77b:

    # "She played her heart out, but Hiroko just had her number every time. Just like with everyone else she's played today."
    "Jugó con el corazón, pero Hiroko la superó en cada ocasión. Al igual que a todas contra quienes jugó hoy."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1754
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_86a8783d:

    # "This whole tournament has been a procession for her."
    "Este torneo fue una procesión para ella."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1765
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4ebe0075:

    # "Eventually, after the trophy ceremony and some time with her parents, Hiroko's able to get away and reflect on the day with the rest of us."
    "Eventualmente, tras la ceremonia y pasar algo de tiempo con sus padres, Hiroko logra escaparse y reflexionar sobre el día con el resto de nosotros."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1766
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_cdf2fcbb:

    # n laugh "I'll say it again, Hiroko, you were INCREDIBLE!" with dissolve
    n laugh "Lo diré otra vez, Hiroko, ¡estuviste INCREÍBLE!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1767
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_976539b8:

