    # h frown_side "Then I'll give you back your light thingy." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Y te devolveré tu cosa esa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2021
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_66aab9e7:

    # "And with that, we ended up walking back to mine."
    "Y dicho eso, terminamos caminando hasta mi casa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2022
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_10fe015c:

    # ks casual sigh "Did you really have my penlight in your sports bag the entire time?"
    ks casual sigh "¿En serio tenías mi linterna en tu bolso deportivo todo este tiempo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2024
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_3bceb492:

    # h frown_side "Well, yeah. Why?" with dissolve
    h frown_side "Pues sí. ¿Por qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2371
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f9890175:

    # ks confused "It's just... You never even took it out?"
    ks confused "Es que... ¿No la sacaste ni una vez?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2026
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_3bfdbdc2:

    # h angry blush "W-what?! {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    h angry blush "¡¿Qu-qué?! {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2027
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ad2710ed:

    # extend "NO!" with vpunch
    extend "¡NO!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2028
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_96884535:

    # h angry noblush "Why? {w=0.5}You {nw}" with dissolve
    h angry noblush "¿Por qué? {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2029
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_03d3e948:

    # extend "WANTED me to play with it?" with vpunch
    extend "¿QUERÍAS que jugara con ella?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2030
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_728135d9:

    # ks "No, just... nevermind."
    ks "No, es que... olvídalo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2031
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d07ec395:

    # "That didn't sound entirely convincing. Maybe she just took it out to look at it?"
    "Eso no sonó muy convincente. ¿Tal vez solo la sacó para mirarla?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2032
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_68045792:

    # "But it doesn't seem like she was going to use it."
    "Pero al parecer no iba a usarla."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2033
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_a49c3dab:

    # "It's like she was trying to tell me in the park. She may have wanted to do what it took to win, but when it came down to it, she had her limits."
    "Es como intentaba decirme en el parque. Tal vez quería hacer lo que hiciera falta para ganar, pero, al final del día, tenía límites."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2034
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1dd80ceb:

    # h frown_side "Good, 'cuz I got a bigger question for 'ya." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Bien, porque te tengo una pregunta más grande." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2385
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_0890dbfc:

    # h confused "Like, where the fuck are your folks, man?" with dissolve
    h confused "O sea, ¿dónde mierda están tus viejos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2382
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_16546b02:

    # ks "... What?"
    ks "... ¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2387
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_a8869cb3:

    # h tennis_headhold2 "Yeah, I've been at your place a bunch and it's always just you here." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 "Sí, ya estuve un montón de veces en tu casa y siempre estás solo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2386
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_53201acb:

    # ks neutral "Oh, uh... yeah, dad's on a business trip this weekend."
    ks neutral "Oh, eh... sí, papá fue a un viaje de negocios por el fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2041
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7fcca924:

    # h tennis neutral "What about your mom?" with dissolve
    h tennis neutral "¿Y tu mamá?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2042
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_32d08978:

    # ks sigh "She doesn't live here anymore."
    ks sigh "Ya no vive aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2043
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7d0016ce:

    # h sad "Oh. Ouchies, dude..." with dissolve
    h sad "Oh. Auchis, viejo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2390
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c52f9895:

    # ks sad "Yeah, well... Anyway."
    ks sad "Sí, pues... Como sea."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2045
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e8ba9d74:

    # h sleeptalk_concerned "Okay, yeah. So..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk_concerned "Muy bien, sí. Pues..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2046
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_0f01ea21:

    # "Hiroko unzips her sports bag before reaching inside..."
    "Hiroko abre el bolso deportivo y mete la mano..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2049
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_b0c1c804:

    # "And sure enough, she pulls my penlight from out of there, apparently untouched since the last time she used it on me."
    "Y, por supuesto, saca mi linterna, aparentemente intacta desde la última vez que la usó en mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2050
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7169a36c:

    # h frown "So, uh... you want me to hypnotize you again and stop you thinking Nozo's gross?" with dissolve
    h frown "Pues, eh... ¿quieres que vuelva a hipnotizarte para que dejes de pensar que Nozo es asquerosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2051
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_fab5de66:

    # ks frown "Yeah... Just put me back into trance like you did before and tell me your suggestion the other day no longer affects me. So I can think how I want again."
    ks frown "Sí... Solo ponme devuelta en trance y dime que tus sugestiones del otro día ya no me afectan, para que pueda volver a pensar como quiera."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2052
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_04bd5406:

    # h sleeptalk "'Kay, got it. Then you return the favour and tell me I can think how I want on the courts again." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Bien, claro. Luego me devuelves el favor y me dices que puedo pensar como quiera en las canchas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2053
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_480e56b6:

    # h "Just get rid of all that shit you put in my brain."
    h "Solo sácame toda la mierda que pusiste en mi cerebro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2054
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_993a972c:

    # "Not that she seems to be returning to the courts anytime soon, but I nod at her in agreement."
    "No es que vaya a volver pronto a las canchas, pero asiento afirmativamente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2406
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_90912af0:

    # ks neutral "Of course. So let's get this over with." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Por supuesto. Terminemos con esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2057
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_43148c36:

    # "As I sit down on the couch, I can't help but recall what happened before and I hasten to add:"
    "Al sentarme en el sofá, no puedo evitar acordarme de lo que pasó la última vez y me apresuro a añadir:"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2058
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_0bea2968:

    # ks sigh "And be GENTLE about waking me this time!"
    ks sigh "¡Pero sé GENTIL cuando me despiertes esta vez!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2062
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_da537655:

    # "Hiroko gives me a little grin as she sits down opposite to me."
    "Hiroko me sonríe tomando asiento frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2063
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c04444ad:

    # "Not that I'll say anything, but I feel a little happier inside to see a smile back on her face after what happened in the park."
    "No lo diré, pero me siento un poco más feliz de ver una sonrisa de nuevo en su rostro, después de lo que pasó en el parque."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2064
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_b579b1c8:

    # h "Yeah, yeah. I got this. You ready?"
    h "Sí, sí. Lo tengo. ¿Listo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2065
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e076689d:

    # "I breathe through my nose as I settle down on the couch, and Hiroko waits for me to nod my head before turning the lit penlight towards me."
    "Respiro por la nariz acomodándome en el sofá, y Hiroko espera a que asienta antes encender la linterna sobre mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2068
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_304e4e0b:

    # h "'Kay here we go. So uh, you wanna look up here again."
    h "Bien, aquí vamos. Pues, eh, quieres mirar aquí otra vez."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2070
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7e239562:

    # h "Yeah, that's right."
    h "Sí, eso es."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2072
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_a737d129:

    # h "Just looking up like before."
    h "Solo mira acá arriba, igual que la otra vez."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2074
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7975192f:

    # h "Watching that pretty light back and forth, back and forth."
    h "Mira esa bonita luz que va de lado a lado, de lado a lado."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2076
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_077113cf:

    # h "Wanting to look more and more."
    h "Cada vez de dan más ganas de mirar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2078
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2a4e8cdc:

    # h "Even though it's so hard. 'Cuz of how sleepy it's making you."
    h "Aunque sea difícil, porque te da mucho sueño."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2083
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_336fb00d:

    # h "Ehehe... You look funny when you're sleepy."
    h "Jejeje... Te ves chistoso cuando tienes sueño."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2085
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_caad72a6:

    # h "Shh, nah, it's okay. Just let 'em close."
    h "Shh, nah, está bien. Deja que se cierren."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2088
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c4712d5e:

    # h "That's right. Relax and let 'em close."
    h "Eso es. Relájate y deja que se cierren."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2089
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_48e774c3:

    # h "Feelin' so nice and relaxed and ready to drop asleep."
    h "Te sientes tan bien, tan relajado y listo para quedarte dormido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2090
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_83a38412:

    # h "So drop, Kyou."
    h "Así que haz eso, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2091
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_690a324a:

    # h "Drop asleep."
    h "Duérmete."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2098
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_a4fe417c:

    # h "Hey, wake up! You with me?"
    h "¡Ey, despierta! ¿Estás ahí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2099
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2778ff9c:

    # ks casual sigh "Urrrgh..."
    ks casual sigh "Ayyy..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2101
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_19143c75:

    # "My eyelids start to pull apart as I rouse myself back to the world of the waking."
    "Mis párpados comienzan a levantarse y regreso al mundo de la consciencia."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2102
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_66ff27ea:

    # "I don't think she woke me up properly this time either, but at least I only felt her fingers gently tapping my cheek instead of an all-out slap."
    "Creo que esta vez tampoco me despertó apropiadamente, pero al menos solo sentí sus dedos tocando mi mejilla en vez de una bofetada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2103
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d341858f:

    # "Guess she's learning in her own way."
    "Supongo que está aprendiendo a su manera."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2105
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_bee8911c:

    # h "Cool. Well, you can see Nozo's pretty again. If you want." with dissolve
    h "Genial. Ya puedes ver a Nozo bonita otra vez. Si quieres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2467
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_529e36c8:

    # ks confused "U-Uh, I can?! You're sure?"
    ks confused "¡¿E-eh, puedo?! ¿Estás segura?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2108
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_fcc7d6b9:

    # h "'Course I'm sure!" with dissolve
    h "¡Claro que estoy segura!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2109
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4a0351bf:

    # "Guess I'm just gonna have to take her word for now."
    "Supongo que tendré que confiar en su palabra por ahora."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2110
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_046c0f7a:

    # "Nozomi... I can't wait to see your true form again."
    "Nozomi... no puedo esperar a ver tu verdadera forma otra vez."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2111
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_190537b7:

    # "But anyway, I'm brought back to the present as I find the penlight thrust in my face."
    "Pero, en fin, regreso al presente me doy cuenta de que tengo la linterna en la cara."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2112
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7c8c754a:

    # h "You takin' it or what?"
    h "¿Vas a tomarla o qué?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2113
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_285db06b:

    # ks surprised "Huh? O-Oh, yeah, of course."
    ks surprised "¿Eh? O-Oh, sí, por supuesto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2114
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d26dc44c:

    # "It feels like an age, but I crack a smile as my penlight is safely back in my hands."
    "Siento que fue una era, pero sonrío al ver que mi linterna volvió sana y salva a mis manos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2116
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_5d36dbee:

    # h "Sooo.... Yeah, you gotta do me now." with dissolve
    h "Pueees... Sí, ahora házmelo a mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2117
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_19f0b987:

    # "My smile fades as I look to her."
    "Mi sonrisa se desvanece."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2483
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_3bfc7ba9:

    # ks neutral "And you're sure you want to do this?"
    ks neutral "¿Estás segura de querer hacer esto?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2120
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_702a5da9:

    # h "You listen to a thing I said back there? 'Course I'm sure!" with dissolve
    h "¿Escuchaste algo de lo que dije hace rato? ¡Claro que estoy segura!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2122
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_8d62f066:

    # "I nodded, we swapped seats, and I wearily took her back into trance."
    "Asentí, intercambiamos asientos y, fatigado, la puse de vuelta en trance."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2123
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_848466fc:

    # "It's not that I don't understand her reasoning but still, it's hard not to feel down about everything."
    "No es que no entienda sus razones, pero, aun así, es difícil no desanimarme con todo esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2124
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_6b1c9b2f:

    # "Despite doing all I could to prevent it, I'm right back where I started."
    "A pesar de hacer todo para evitarlo, volví a donde comencé."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2128
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f9b6816f:

    # ks casual "... Four, testing your eyelids now, feeling all your senses return..."
    ks casual "... Cuatro, tus párpados comienzan a moverse; sientes tus sentidos regresar..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2131
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_f67a57b0:

    # "All this really has been a waste of everyone's time."
    "Todo esto sí fue una pérdida del tiempo de todos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2132
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d547b319:

    # ks "And five, wide awake now, Hiroko."
    ks "Y cinco, despierta, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2134
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_b8764f32:

    # h "Urrgh..." with dissolve
    h "Ayyy..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2135
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_bdc52c33:

    # ks sigh "Alright, it's done. Anything you think or do on a tennis court is all up to you again."
    ks sigh "Muy bien, está hecho. Todo lo que pienses o hagas en una cancha de tenis depende de ti una vez más."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2137
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_e6c65c48:

    # "It takes her a moment to register what I just said, but when she does, she gives me a sleepy nod of her head." with dissolve
    "Le toma un momento entender lo que dije, pero cuando lo hace, asiente adormecida con la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2139
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2b8d7f3c:

    # h "'Kay..." with dissolve
    h "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_af6c39de:

    # "She then looks to me, and I'm not sure what to do." with dissolve
    "Luego me mira, y no estoy seguro de qué hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2142
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_fd865950:

    # "I mean, now that we're finished with the penlight, what else is keeping us together?"
    "Digo, ahora que terminamos con la linterna, ¿qué otra razón tenemos para estar juntos?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2144
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ad9eb996:

    # h "So, uh... I gotta ask something else." with dissolve
    h "Y, eh... Hay otra cosa que debo preguntar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2145
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_19efb262:

    # ks neutral "What's that?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2147
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c03bb16b:

    # h "What's the deal with that light thingy?" with dissolve
    h "¿Qué con la linterna esa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2562
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4fb2c091:

    # ks confused "My penlight? What about it?"
    ks confused "¿Mi linterna? ¿Qué hay con ella?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2202
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_48f9fab1:

    # h "I can't stop thinking about that thing." with dissolve
    h "No puedo dejar de pensar en esa cosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2204
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_03ace9d8:

    # h "I mean, it ain't something you buy at a store, is it?" with dissolve
    h "Digo, no la comprase en una tienda, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2205
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_dd87a0d2:

    # "She folds her arms and scowls in thought for a moment."
    "Se cruza de brazos y frunce el ceño pensando por un momento."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2206
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ba11913b:

    # h "Like... It's some kinda special hypnotist's light?"
    h "O sea... ¿es alguna clase de linterna especial para hipnotistas?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2207
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_8031ef10:

    # "That gets a chuckle out of me. But I guess I never told her where the penlight came from."
    "Eso me hace reír. Pero supongo que nuca le dije de dónde salió la linterna."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2208
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_54ae1bbb:

    # ks smile "I guess you're right."
    ks smile "Supongo que tienes razón."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2209
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_7e89c28f:

    # ks "It's a basic penlight that I bought off the internet, but it IS special."
    ks "Es una pluma linterna común y corriente que compré por internet, pero SÍ es especial."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2212
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_eccae642:

    # h "Yeah? Special how?" with dissolve
    h "¿Sí? ¿Especial cómo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2213
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_add6d5af:

    # ks "I took it apart and made some modifications so the light would be more eye-catching."
    ks "La desmantelé y le hice algunas modificaciones para que la luz fuera más atractiva."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2214
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_bc84eabb:

    # ks "So I guess you really could call it a \"hypnotist's light\" because that's what I designed it for."
    ks "Supongo que sí puedes llamarla \"linterna para hipnotistas\", porque para eso la diseñé."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2216
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_4392f081:

    # h "What? Seriously, you MADE that thing?" with dissolve
    h "¿Qué? ¿En serio tú HICISTE esa cosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2217
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_dbd796e3:

    # h "Like... How? Why?"
    h "O sea... ¿Cómo? ¿Por qué?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2218
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_aab9b6e9:

    # "... Honestly, it feels kinda nice to be able to talk freely with someone about this stuff."
    "... Honestamente, es agradable poder hablar libremente de esto con alguien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2219
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_c299eb13:

    # "Not that I expected Hiroko of all people to understand me, but after everything that's happened, she does seem genuinely curious."
    "No esperaba que Hiroko me entendiera, pero después de todo lo que pasó, en serio parece tener curiosidad."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2220
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_970dabc5:

    # "I can't help but indulge her."
    "No puedo evitar complacerla."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2222
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1a970080:

    # ks "Well, I always liked tinkering with things, and I'd just gotten into learning hypnosis so I thought to myself \"Why not do both?\"" with dissolve
    ks "Bueno, siempre me gustó retocar cosas, y recién empecé a aprender hipnosis, así que me dije: \"¿Por qué no ambos?\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2223
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_d08f77c7:

    # ks "I think it helped motivate me to have something to do with my hands while I learned how to hypnotize people."
