    h sleeptalk_concerned "Por favor..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2371
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_79f6c323:

    # "I don't say anything as she hastily puts her shoes back on and darts out of the house."
    "No digo nada al verla ponerse vacilantemente sus zapatos y salir corriendo de la casa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2372
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_51af8b96:

    # "But that look on her face as she left. Was she..."
    "Pero esa mirada en su rostro cuando se fue. Me..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2373
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_0598cadf:

    # "Was she seriously that scared of me?"
    "¿En serio me tenía miedo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2429
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_8a9a2549:

    # "What an impossible little woman..."
    "Esa mujercita es imposible..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2431
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_87094806:

    # "Where does she get off thinking I'll actually use this thing like that?"
    "¿De dónde saca la idea de que usaré esta cosa así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2432
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_748e01e1:

    # "Because yeah, I know what she was getting at: It's dangerous to use this thing on people. As if I didn't fucking know?"
    "Porque, sí, sé adónde quería llegar: Es peligroso usarla en la gente. Como si no lo supiera, carajo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2433
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_76e8563e:

    # "But I can't just break it because she told me to. She doesn't get to do that, and besides, I want to know more about it."
    "Pero no puedo solo romperla porque ella dice. Ella no puede hacer eso, y además, quiero saber más de esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2434
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_2607e02b:

    # "Why does it have the effect on people that it does? Isn't that worth figuring out?"
    "¿Por qué tiene este efecto en la gente? ¿No vale la pena averiguarlo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2435
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_a20b9f46:

    # "I'm not going to use it to brainwash Nozomi, or whatever perv shit she thinks I'll do with it."
    "No la usaré para lavarle el cerebro a Nozomi, o ninguna mierda pervertida que esté pensando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2436
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_753a8b79:

    # "But if she really thinks that of me... What is she going to do tomorrow?"
    "Pero si eso es lo que piensa de mí... ¿Qué hará mañana?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2437
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_ef0da39f:

    # "Will she shoot her mouth off about me to anyone who'll listen? Tell Nozomi I mean to use this on her and make her think she's my girlfriend or something?"
    "¿Hablará sobre mí con cualquiera que la escuche? ¿Le dirá a Nozomi que pienso usar esto en ella para hacerla creer que es mi novia o algo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2438
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_1b3d67a3:

    # "I've passed on the chance to hypnotize Hiroko before so she wouldn't cause any mischief, and she hasn't so far, but maybe this time..."
    "Dejé pasar la oportunidad de hipnotizar a Hiroko antes de que me hiciera una jugarreta, y hasta ahora no lo ha hecho, pero esta vez..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2440
translate spanish Day7_Con_Hiroko_Penlight_07372fa4:

    # "Maybe this time she really can't be trusted..."
    "Tal vez esta vez no se puede confiar en ella..."

