    # "As I make my own way towards the courts, there is an applause from the assembled onlookers."
    "Al abrirme camino hacia las gradas, hay un aplauso por parte de los conglomerados espectadores."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3161
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_cd031a6a:

    # "It seems the players have just started leaving the changing rooms to begin their warm ups."
    "Parece que las jugadoras acaban de salir de los vestidores y comienzan a calentar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3164
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e075ff46:

    # "And there, at last, is Hiroko; clad in our school's tennis uniform as she strides calmly to assume her position on one of the courts." with dissolve
    "Y ahí, al último, está Hiroko; vistiendo el uniforme de tenis de nuestra escuela y tomando su posición en una de las canchas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3165
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4e0ca755:

    # "I think I hear Nozomi call out to her, but if so Hiroko's completely unfazed as she does a few stretches ahead of her first game."
    "Creo que oí a Nozomi aclamarla, pero Hiroko se mantiene completamente impasible, haciendo un par de estiramientos antes de su primer juego."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3166
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_bdf8a713:

    # "Picking a spot on the opposite side of the court to Nozomi, I settle in as Hiroko finishes her warm ups and the umpire signals the start of the match..."
    "Tomando un lugar del lado opuesto de las gradas al de Nozomi, tomo asiento mientras Hiroko termina sus calentamientos y el juez anuncia el inicio del partido..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3168
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3ee42d12:

    # "The next 20 minutes or so pass in a blur, as we all watch our school's tennis ace show us what she's capable of."
    "Los siguientes 20 minutos pasan en un abrir y cerrar de ojos, y todos vemos a nuestro as del tenis demostrar de lo que es capaz."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3169
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_80b3d61e:

    # "Her serves come down fast and precise. Her footwork around the court is sharp and quick and her volleyed returns leave her opponent flailing at thin air almost every time."
    "Sus servicios son rápidos y precisos. Su juego de piernas sobre la cancha es agudo y veloz, y sus devoluciones dejan a su oponente golpeando el aire en casi cada ocasión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3176
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_47ddd7f6:

    # t "Game, set and match: Miss Homura. By four games to love."
    t "Juego, set y partido: Señorita Homura. Por cuatro juegos a cero."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3177
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a762410a:

    # "I think we all just witnessed a murder."
    "Creo que acabamos de presenciar un asesinato."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3179
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9f26491a:

    # "Hiroko wipes her brow with her armband and turns to walk off court while I notice a delighted-looking Nozomi cheering and waving her over." with dissolve
    "Hiroko se limpia la frente con su brazalete y se da la vuelta para salir de la cancha, mientas que noto a Nozomi vitoreándola encantada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3180
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a601b750:

    # "After how worried she was about her friend, seeing Hiroko destroy her first opponent with such focused professionalism must have been a massive relief."
    "Con lo preocupada que estaba por su amiga, ver a Hiroko destruir a su primera oponente con tan enfocado profesionalismo debió ser un inmenso alivio."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3181
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_94cf1af6:

    # "... So focused in fact, it takes Hiroko a while to notice Nozomi waving at her."
    "... Tan enfocado, de hecho, que a Hiroko le toma un rato darse cuenta de que Nozomi la está llamando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3182
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_132d7a11:

    # "She stops to exchange a few words, but she doesn't hang around before walking away to tend to her equipment."
    "Se detiene para intercambiar algunas palabras, pero no se queda y se va a recoger su equipo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3183
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_eaacb388:

    # "That girl's been a picture of focused calm from the moment I saw her today."
    "Esa chica ha sido la viva imagen de la calma y la concentración desde el momento en que la vi hoy."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3184
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6cd5af4a:

    # "Like winning every match she plays is the only single thing on her mind..."
    "Como si ganar cada partido que juega fuera lo único en su mente..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3186
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0e765b26:

    # r "Hey, ball boy. I wondered what happened to you." with dissolve
    r "¿Qué hay, recogepelotas? Me preguntaba qué te había pasado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3187
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_113e8c27:

    # "I, on the other hand, seem to have no end of things to think about."
    "Yo, por otro lado, tengo toda clase de cosas en que pensar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3188
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_86981acb:

    # ks casual frown "It's Kyou."
    ks casual frown "Es Kyou."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3189
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_135646a3:

    # r tennis wristband_left grin "Sure it is~ Anyway, how's our girl doing?" with dissolve
    r tennis wristband_left grin "Sí que sí. Como sea, ¿cómo le va a nuestra chica?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3190
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5dcb1568:

    # ks "Who, Hiroko? She just won."
    ks "¿Quién, Hiroko? Acaba de ganar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3191
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_72852505:

    # r smile "Heh, no doubt. But, uhh..." with dissolve
    r smile "Je, de eso no hay duda. Pero, emm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3192
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2aef5217:

    # ks neutral "What?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3194
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0ccf9a90:

    # "Risa puts a hand to her chin and sighs deliberatively." with dissolve
    "Risa se lleva una mano a la barbilla y suspira deliberadamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3195
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c9f57b54:

    # r "Well, how do I put this..."
    r "Pues, ¿cómo decirlo?..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3199
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1da3a3dd:

    # h "Hey, 'Ris." with dissolve
    h "Hola, 'Ris." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3201
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_912c70eb:

    # r "Hey, there she is~ Me and your boyfriend were just talking about you." with dissolve
    r "Ey, allí está. Tu novio y yo estábamos hablando de ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3202
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_05715888:

    # "Wait, \"boyfriend\"?"
    "Espera, ¿\"novio\"?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3203
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_33dd5417:

    # "Does Risa know about what we've been doing? How..."
    "¿Risa sabe de lo que hemos estado haciendo? ¿Cómo...?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3205
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fc29f160:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah, I don't care, I'm jus' passing through. My next game's about to start." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Seh, me da igual, solo vengo de paso. Mi próximo juego está por empezar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3206
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_07fc8e58:

    # h neutral_side "See ya." with dissolve
    h neutral_side "Nos vemos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3209
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a9720b90:

    # "And just as soon as she appears by us, Hiroko's gone again as she paces over to the next court over where I'm sure her next match is supposed to be." with dissolve
    "Y tan pronto como se apareció ante nosotros, Hiroko se va, camino a la cancha de al lado donde, estoy seguro, será su siguiente partido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3210
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8b00b506:

    # r frown "Aaaand, that's what I'm talking about." with dissolve
    r frown "Yyy eso es a lo que me refiero." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3211
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9d22f426:

    # ks "Huh?"
    ks "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3212
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d0f4b382:

    # "Risa looks across to the next court, where Hiroko has already taken up a position by the net as she waits for her next opponent."
    "Risa mira las canchas contiguas, donde Hiroko ya asumió su posición junto a la red, esperando a su próxima oponente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3213
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_90c326c2:

    # "Pretty sure there's still a few minutes before the next round of matches start."
    "Estoy seguro de que aún quedan unos minutos antes de que dé inicio la siguiente ronda."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-03-12 22:02

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3029
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_edf511c0:

    # n sad "S-soo... are you here to cheer for our school too, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n sad "E-esteee... ¿también vienes a apoyar a nuestra escuela, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e1ae1a83:

    # n sigh "I know... I'm just so worried about her. Especially after- {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    n sigh "Lo sé... Es que estoy preocupada por ella. Sobre todo después de-{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3119
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ada360a9:

    # "Risa looks across to the next court, where Hiroko has already taken up a position by the net as she waits for her next opponent." with dissolve
    "Risa mira las canchas contiguas, donde Hiroko ya asumió su posición junto a la red, esperando a su próxima oponente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3121
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_20f8f37e:

    # r concerned "I just can't figure her out at all, you know? Especially after that weird narcoleptic episode I heard about." with dissolve
    r concerned "Es que no la entiendo, ¿sabes? Sobre todo después de ese episodio narcoléptico del que escuché." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3122
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5d2013db:

    # "She looks at me as if she's expecting a reply..."
    "Me mira como si estuviera esperando una respuesta..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3123
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c669b5bc:

    # "I just want her to leave me alone."
    "Yo solo quiero que me deje solo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3124
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_50ecda8e:

    # ks sigh "Man, don't look at me. You've got the wrong idea if you think I'm her boyfriend or whatever. I'm just here to watch."
    ks sigh "Cielos, no me mires a mí. Te equivocas si crees que soy su novio o algo así. Yo solo vine a mirar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3126
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_43e1ebae:

    # "Risa frowns at me for a moment." with dissolve
    "Risa me frunce el ceño por un momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3127
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1bf9689b:

    # r "Just her biggest fan, huh? Bought her a premium tennis racket out of the goodness of your heart, okay ball boy."
    r "Nada más que su mayor admirador, ¿eh? Le compraste una raqueta de tenis de primera por pura buena voluntad, ¿cierto, recogepelotas?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3128
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_072cf4f3:

    # ks frown "Kyou."
    ks frown "Kyou."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3130
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b15cd7b2:

    # "She takes a breath and sighs." with dissolve
    "Toma aire y suspira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3131
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5efd15f0:

    # r "Look, I get it. Not my business. It's just weird that she's like this."
    r "Mira, entiendo. No es mi problema. Es solo que es raro que esté así."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3132
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fe064d22:

    # "With a sigh of my own, I realise I'd better try and reassure her or something."
    "Con un suspiro de mi parte, me doy cuenta de que será mejor intentar tranquilizarla o algo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3134
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_89546f3b:

    # ks neutral "Hiroko's dead set on winning this thing, isn't she? Maybe she's... just so dedicated that she's blanking everything else and staying 100%% focused." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Hiroko está determinada a ganar, ¿no? Tal vez está... tan dedicada que ignora todo lo demás y está 100%% enfocada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3135
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3ee2868d:

    # r neutral_side "Hmm..." with dissolve
    r neutral_side "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3136
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7adfdf5e:

    # ks "It's what she's passionate about, after all."
    ks "Es lo que le apasiona, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3137
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ed50f7a8:

    # r frown_side "Passion, huh..." with dissolve
    r frown_side "Pasión, ¿eh?..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3138
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8c06462a:

    # "She sucks a breath, as the umpires around us start calling for the players to get back on the courts for their next matches."
    "Toma aire, mientras los jueces a nuestro alrededor comienzan a llamar a las jugadoras para que vuelvan a las canchas para los siguientes partidos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3139
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c51ce829:

    # r tennis "Yeah, that's the thing. There isn't any." with dissolve
    r tennis "Sí, esa es la cosa. Ya no hay." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3140
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_47447833:

    # r concerned_side "Nothing gets to her now. Nothing makes her happy. She's just, like... there." with dissolve
    r concerned_side "Nada la molesta ahora. Nada la hace feliz. Está, pues... ahí nada más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3141
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_498e8b4b:

    # ks sigh "Yeah, so? She just wants to win, that's all she cares about."
    ks sigh "Sí, ¿y? Solo quiere ganar, es lo único que le importa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3143
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a01803d6:

    # r frown "No, Kyou. It isn't." with dissolve
    r frown "No, Kyou. No lo es." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5e6a7fc7:

    # "Risa obviously wants to argue some more, but she's out of time, frustratedly swinging her racket back and forth as she steps onto the court beside us." with dissolve
    "Es evidente que Risa quiere discutir más, pero se le acaba al tiempo, así que camina a la cancha junto a nosotros, sacudiendo frustrada su raqueta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3146
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2c8f3f2c:

    # "Meanwhile, I think to slip away for a bit. Just so I don't get into a conversation like that again..."
    "Mientras tanto, yo decido escabullirme. Solo para no volver a meterme en una conversación así..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3148
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f9bda938:

    # "I saw what I wanted to see from Hiroko. It seemed all she needed was that winning mentality after all."
    "Vi lo que quería ver de Hiroko. Parece que todo lo que necesitaba era esa mentalidad ganadora, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3149
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0a40fcaa:

    # "So the final's scheduled for the early evening. I should come back then..."
    "La final será en la tarde. Regresaré entonces..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3196
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9c3525b4:

    # "... I return to find everyone crowded around a single court."
    "... Cuando vuelvo veo que todos están reunidos alrededor de una sola cancha."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3197
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e4391652:

    # "As I approach, I find a little gap in the audience where I can insert myself and get a look at who's playing..."
    "Al aproximarme, encuentro una pequeña abertura en la audiencia por la cual puedo adentrarme y ver quién está jugando..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3204
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_73205f0a:

    # "... And I smile at what I see." with dissolve
    "... Y lo que veo dibuja una sonrisa en mi rostro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3205
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_947f054e:

    # t "Deuce."
    t "Deuce."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3207
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9e13186e:

    # "Hiroko made the final. Of course she did!"
    "Hiroko llegó a la final. ¡Por supuesto que sí!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3208
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f640f6ad:

    # "But what's the score? Who's winning?"
    "Pero ¿cuál es el marcador? ¿Quién está ganando?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3209
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_778fe7a1:

    # t "I can't believe she's still holding on!"
    t "¡No puedo creer que siga de pie!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3210
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a5ce7d0c:

    # "And who's that guy talking about?"
    "¿Y de quién está hablando ese chico?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3212
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b683be67:

    # "Just then my thoughts are interrupted by the popping sound of a ball being served, as Hiroko's opponent sends it shooting down the line."
    "De pronto mis pensamientos son interrumpidos por el sonido de una pelota siendo servida, enviada por la oponente de Hiroko con un tiro paralelo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3214
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_229a76a4:

    # h tennis_armup frown_side "Ahh!" with dissolve
    h tennis_armup frown_side "¡Aah!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3215
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_40191db4:

    # "Hiroko takes a step to her side and, gripping her racket tightly with both hands, makes a back-handed return across court."
    "Hiroko da un paso hacia su costado y, sujetando firmemente la raqueta con ambas manos, hace una devolución de revés cruzada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3217
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c43a895f:

    # "It sails towards the other girl, who stayed back on her line, and she hits the ball solidly to Hiroko's right."
    "Vuela hacia la otra chica, quien se mantuvo en su línea, y ella golpea la bola sólidamente hacia la derecha de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3218
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5a52c862:

    # h sleeptalk "Urrh..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Arrg..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3222
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_49e34783:

    # "Hiroko gasps as she dashes across the baseline and smacks her return across court once again."
    "Hiroko jadea mientras corre hasta la línea de base y azota su devolución, nuevamente cruzada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3225
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b6e1e21e:

    # "The other girl grunts and slices it back, only to find the net and the crowd roars delightedly."
    "La otra chica la envía de regreso con un gruñido, pero se encuentra con la red, y la multitud ruje maravillada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3227
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3fe75109:

    # "And that's when, as I cast my eyes back to our school's tennis star, I notice how uncomfortably sweaty she looks." with dissolve
    "Y es entonces que, al volver mi mirada a la estrella del tenis de nuestra escuela, me doy cuenta de lo incómodamente sudorosa que luce." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3231
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_20862bb1:

    # t "Advantage, Miss Homura." with dissolve
    t "Ventaja, Señorita Homura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3232
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_eb78dc92:

    # n "{size=16}Oh my god, I can't watch this!{/size}"
    n "{size=16}¡Ay, Dios, no puedo ver esto!{/size}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3233
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d7e5a75d:

    # "As the people around me mutter excitedly, I see Hiroko's chest heaving as she struggles to draw breath back into her lungs."
    "Mientras la gente a mi alrededor murmura con emoción, veo cómo el pecho de Hiroko lucha por regresar el aliento a sus pulmones."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3236
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_04452ad4:

    # t "Match point."
    t "Punto de juego."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3238
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5fdae661:

    # "And as Hiroko goes to assume her position to receive serve once again... wait, was that a limp?" with dissolve
    "Y Hiroko asume su posición para recibir una vez más... espera, ¿acaba de cojear?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3240
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1b8aec12:

    # "The umpire takes a moment to hush the crowd before play continues, and the more I look at Hiroko, the more exhausted she looks."
    "El juez de línea espera a que la multitud guarde silencio antes de continuar, y entre más miro a Hiroko, más exhausta se ve."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3241
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9e4c9c12:

    # "There's a nasty-looking bruise on her leg where she must have gone to ground at some point."
    "Hay un moretón muy feo en su pierna sobre la cual seguramente se cayó en algún momento."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3242
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2aef477e:

    # "And the way her racket wobbles in her hands; like she can barely keep it lifted from the ground..."
    "Y la forma en que su raqueta se tambalea en sus manos; como si apenas pudiera levantarla del suelo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3243
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c0b42290:

    # "Yet her determined eyes gaze unwaveringly across to the other finalist."
    "Y sin embargo, sus determinados ojos miran inquebrantablemente a la otra finalista."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3244
