    # ks "Maybe you won't admit it right now. Not to yourself and definitely not to me, but I got a feeling you like the experience of being hypnotized."
    ks "No lo admitirás ahora. No a ti misma, y definitivamente no a mí, pero me da la sensación de que te gusta la experiencia de ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3440
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d40687e0:

    # ks "You secretly like the idea of being \"made\" to do stuff that's weird or embarrassing. And by none other than yours truly." with dissolve
    ks "En secreto de gusta la idea de ser \"obligada\" a hacer cosas raras y embarazosas. Y por nadie más que tu servidor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3441
