# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2964
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8d4580dd:

    # r tennis wristband_right "Yeah, that's what's bugging me. There isn't any." with dissolve
    r tennis wristband_right "Eso es lo que me extraña. No hay." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3140
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0dd8e26b:

    # r concerned_side "Nothing's getting to her. Nothing makes her happy. She's just, like... going through the motions." with dissolve
    r concerned_side "Nada le molesta. Nada la hace feliz. Solo está... haciendo las cosas y ya." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6a1cd919:

    # "Risa obviously wants to argue some more, but she's out of time as she can see her match is about to start."
    "Risa obviamente quiere discutir más, pero se le acaba el tiempo, pues su partido está a punto de empezar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2932
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a38e1185:

    # "Frustratedly swinging her racket back and forth, Risa steps onto the court beside us as she tries to turn her focus to the game at hand. At least for now."
    "Sacudiendo frustrada su raqueta, camina a la cancha que está junto a nosotros e intenta concentrarte en el juego."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3357
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_29fa1d3a:

    # "It briefly crossed my mind to wait for Hiroko and walk home with her, but I don't want to run into Risa and Sayori again today."
    "Se me cruzó por la mente le idea de esperar a Hiroko y caminar a casa con ella, pero no quiero toparme con Risa y Sayori otra vez."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3362
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4810aa16:

    # "In any case, I know I won't have to wait long. I can trust Hiroko to honour the deal we made."
    "En todo caso, sé que no tendré que esperar mucho. Puedo confiar en que Hiroko cumplirá con el trato que hicimos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3363
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c970ff96:

    # "After all, I imagine the thought of coming here to assist in my warm-up show is now all she can think about..."
    "Después de todo, imagino que la idea de venir a ayudarme en mi acto de calentamiento es ahora lo único en lo que puede pensar..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3393
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a3b5997e:

    # h angry vein "H'yeah, your \"winning mentality\" nearly wrecked me, so kiss my ass." with dissolve
    h angry vein "Seh, tu \"mentalidad ganadora\" casi me parte en dos, así que bésame el culo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3394
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f4725fa2:

    # h casual_armup irritated "Ugh, as it is I'm gonna be sore for days..." with dissolve
    h casual_armup irritated "Ay, voy a estar días adolorida..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3395
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2f72c733:

    # "Hiroko offers nothing else but for a low growl while she quivers in place."
