translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5f7a808c:

    # "Her reaction succeeds in making me chuckle, as I take my penlight out of my pocket."
    "Su reacción logra hacerme reír un poco, y saco la linterna de mi bolsillo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3490
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1c738b47:

    # h surprised novein "A-ahh..." with dissolve
    h surprised novein "A-aah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3497
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e777cf06:

    # ks "I shine the light, and you look. There's no need for you to spend any conscious effort thinking about it."
    ks "Enciendo la luz, y tú observas. No hace falta que hagas ningún esfuerzo consciente en pensarlo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3562
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_37d07e78:

    # "Yeah, yeah, you think she's cute. I thought so too the first time I met her."
    "Seh, seh, creen que es linda. Yo también lo pensé la primera vez que la vi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3563
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_831db254:

    # "But you guys don't know her like I do..."
    "Pero ustedes no la conocen como yo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3708
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4984d315:

    # "I stay with her a moment to make sure she keeps upright, then walk back to my viewers one last time."
    "Me quedo con ella por un momento para asegurarme de que no se caiga, luego regreso con los espectadores una última vez."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3709
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_eb39d9c1:

    # "The feeling of pride must be written all over my face as I look towards the camera. I'm sure everyone watching the stream would comment if I allowed them to see it."
    "Debo tener el sentimiento de orgullo escrito en toda la cara cuando miro en dirección a la cámara. Seguro todos los que ven la transmisión me lo dirían si les dejara verla..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3711
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6819f71d:

    # "The chat explodes once again as people rush to compliment the pair of us."
    "El chat nuevamente explota y la gente no para de elogiarnos a ambos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3712
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_396bfa2d:

    # "While they didn't see me performing the induction of my assistant, they were satisfied by my use of hypnotic language during the performance that I knew what I was doing."
    "Si bien no me vieron llevar a cabo la inducción en mi asistente, mi uso de lenguaje hipnótico durante la presentación los convenció de que sabía lo que hacía."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3713
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5a616987:

    # "And as for \"[stagename]\"... yeah, it'd be hard for her to react the way she has unless she were pretty deeply hypnotized and trusting of my commands."
    "Y en cuanto a \"[stagename]\"... sí, sería difícil que reaccionara así a no ser que estuviera muy profundamente hipnotizada y atenta a mis órdenes."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3714
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e4ddaefe:

    # "They know she's the real deal."
    "Saben que esto es real."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3717
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1c88047a:

    # "Anyway, it's then that I decide to wrap up our streaming show."
    "En fin, es entonces que decido dar cierre a la transmisión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3718
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4c2aecee:

    # "People were suggesting other things for \"[stagename]\" to do in front of the camera, but I know better than to push my luck any further tonight."
    "La gente estaba sugiriendo otras cosas para que \"[stagename]\" hiciera, pero mejor no tiento más mi suerte esta noche."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3719
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4353476e:

    # "The last thing I'd want is for Hiroko to collapse on camera or finally break out of her entranced state out of sheer desperation at her situation."
    "Lo último que quiero es que Hiroko colapse frente a la cámara o que finalmente escape de su estado de trance en desesperación por su situación."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3720
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9f4431c5:

    # "This was a warm-up show, just like I told her it was going to be."
    "Esto fue un calentamiento, como le dije que sería."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3721
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_80a867b8:

    # "So I return to Hiroko's side once more and place a hand gently on her shoulder."
    "Así que vuelvo al lado de Hiroko una vez más y coloco mi mano suavemente sobre su hombro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3722
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3cd9d7d3:

    # "She looks so peaceful right now; focused entirely on staying in hypnotic trance just as I told her."
    "Luce tan pacífica en este momento; enteramente concentrada en permanecer en trance hipnótico como le dije."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3723
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_442c52b1:

    # ks smile "Very good, Hiroko. You're so good at being hypnotized. So good at staying hypnotized."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Hiroko. Eres muy buena siendo hipnotizada. Muy buena quedándote hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3725
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d9b19090:

    # ks "But in a few moments it'll be time to leave this blissful state of hypnosis. You'll be waking up fully refreshed and mindful of what we've done together."
    ks "Pero en unos momentos será hora de salir de este dichoso estado de hipnosis. Despertarás fresca y consciente de lo que hemos hecho juntos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3726
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_595c167f:

    # ks "Waking up as I count to five, Hiroko..."
    ks "Despierta a la cuenta de cinco, Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3610
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1eb79d1f:

    # ks "One, two... taking deep breath in and out, allowing the rest of the world to come back to you."
    ks "Uno, dos... inhala y exhala profundamente, dejando que el resto del mundo vuelva a ti."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3728
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_95ed9f0c:

    # ks "Three, feeling your whole body become lighter as your consciousness returns..."
    ks "Tres, siente cómo tu cuerpo se vuelve más ligero y tu consciencia regresa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3729
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7726af0c:

    # ks "Four, testing those eyelids of yours. Becoming more conscious. Less asleep."
    ks "Cuatro, comienza a mover tus párpados. Más consciente. Menos dormida."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3730
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a4c988d3:

    # ks "And five, Hiroko. Wide awake, now."
    ks "Y cinco, Hiroko. Despierta ahora."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3761
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0525817f:

    # "As Hiroko starts to rouse herself, I take my hand off her shoulder and wait."
    "Una vez Hiroko comienza a reaccionar, retiro mi mano de su hombro y espero."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3764
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f700ad3a:

    # "Her eyelids seem to heave themselves up to uncover her sleepy green eyes, as the rest of her body barely stirs from its rigid position on my bed."
