# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3382
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_acf7d0d0:

    # "{color=#FFFFFF}\"Well we're about to do a live hypno show. DM me if you want to watch and I'll send you an invite, we're starting in five minutes.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#FFFFFF}\"Bueno, estamos a punto de hacer un espectáculo de hipnosis en vivo. Envíenme un mensaje directo si quieren ver, empezamos en cinco minutos.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3415
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fddc59b0:

    # "And with that I leave them watching as I step over towards the bed and rejoin \"[stagename]\", standing to her side while keeping just out of sight of the camera."
    " Y con eso, los dejo mirando para acércame a la cama y reunirme con \"[stagename]\", parándome a su lado, justo fuera de la vista de la cámara."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3458
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d6fdcefb:

    # "As her hand gently floats back down to rest on the bedsheets, I think briefly about what I've planned for our main event."
    "Viendo su mano bajar suavemente para posarse sobre la sábana, pienso brevemente en lo que planeé para el evento principal."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3467
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0bb90b9b:

    # "With a grin I step briefly in front of her, keeping my back to the camera, as I slide my penlight against the palm of her left hand."
    "Con una sonrisa, me pongo brevemente frente a ella, manteniendo mi espalda hacia la cámara, y deslizo mi linterna contra su palma izquierda."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3793
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_504100c0:

    # "Maybe even too easy. Like goddamn, is there even anything that I can suggest that she'll refuse?" with dissolve
    "Tal vez demasiado fácil. Maldita sea, ¿siquiera hay algo que pueda decir que ella rechazaría?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3818
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_bdc97eca:

    # "Yeah. It's true that I started messing with Hiroko out of a sense of justice, but I can't ignore the once-in-a-lifetime opportunity that she presents me."
    "Sí, es cierto que le he estado haciendo esto a Hiroko en busca de justicia, pero no puedo ignorar la oportunidad única en la vida que me está brindando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3819
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ffe7fcce:

    # "With such a surprisingly creative mind hiding beneath that punky exterior, coupled with her adorable naiveté... I can't just stop now."
    "Con una mente tan sorprendentemente creativa ocultándose bajo ese agresivo exterior, acompañada con su adorable ingenuidad... no puedo detenerme así como así."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3820
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ddb9a472:

    # "I can test the limits of the human imagination and truly sharpen my skills as a hypnotist and... hell, I can truly bring out her full potential as a human being."
    "Puedo poner a prueba los límites de la imaginación humana y perfeccionar mis habilidades como hipnotista y... diablos, puedo sacar a la luz todo su potencial como ser humano."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3822
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a3f32b7b:

    # "So no, Hiroko. I won't let you go. I held up my side of our deal."
    "Así que no, Hiroko. No te dejaré ir. Cumplí mi parte del trato."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3823
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0f4d60ed:

    # "I'll keep ensuring that you hold up to yours."
    "Y me aseguraré de que tú sigas cumpliendo la tuya."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3820
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_47928c05:

    # ks casual neutral "That's right, Hiroko. Just breathe in, breathe out, and relax. Returning to this deep, deep state of hypnotic trance."
    ks casual neutral "Eso es, Hiroko. Solo inhala, exhala, y relájate. Volviendo a este muy, muy profundo estado de trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3825
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c1535975:

    # ks "But I want to remind you again as you experience all of this, that you are always in control of yourself."
    ks "Pero quiero recordarte una vez más mientras experimentas esto, que tú siempre tienes el control de ti misma."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3826
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_56c08a42:

    # ks "Everything you think and feel is always a choice, and that choice is always yours."
    ks "Todo lo que pienses y sientas es siempre tu elección, y esa elección siempre es tuya."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3827
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_cad31fdc:

    # ks "So knowing all of this, I want you to try coming out of hypnosis now."
    ks "Así que, sabiendo eso, quiero que intentes salir de la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3828
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_667310c2:

    # h sleeptalk "Mmrn... t-try...?" with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Mmnn... ¿i-intentar...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3830
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d9840f7b:

    # ks "Yes, Hiroko. Like I said, entering this deep, comfortable state of hypnosis is always a choice. So if you want to, you can attempt to open your eyes now." with dissolve
    ks "Sí, Hiroko. Como dije, entrar a este profundo y cómodo estado de hipnosis es siempre tu elección. Por lo que, si quieres, puedes tratar de abrir los ojos ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3831
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7fb96b83:

    # ks "Just for a little while, try to pull those heavy, leaden eyelids open and come out of hypnosis all by yourself; just to see if that's what you really want."
    ks "Solo por unos momentos, trata de levantar esos párpados pesados como plomo y salir de este estado de hipnosis por tu cuenta; solo para ver si eso es lo que realmente quieres."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3832
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fb5c9242:

    # "Yeah. So I'm asking her to rouse herself from trance, but I wonder if she realizes she's being tricked again."
    "Sí. Le estoy pidiendo que se despierte del trance, pero me pregunto si se da cuenta de que de nuevo está siendo engañada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3833
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1bde8d4f:

    # h sleep_concerned "Mmmn... mmmrrrnnn..." with dissolve
    h sleep_concerned "Mmmn... mmmñññnnn..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3834
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0c098852:

    # "Because even if it seems I'm encouraging her to escape, I know I'm setting her up to fail. And knowing what I know about Hiroko, she's surely going to fall for it."
    "Porque si bien parece que la estoy alentando a escapar, mi intención es que fracase. Y sabiendo lo que sé de Hiroko, no tengo duda de que caerá."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3835
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_54676ea3:

    # ks "But I want you to know it's okay if you can't. It's okay if your eyelids struggle to open..."
    ks "Pero quiero que sepas que está bien si no puedes. Está bien si a tus párpados les cuesta abrirse..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3836
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ad1c606d:

    # "I watch as her eyelids flicker and start to peel back, almost like she's succeeding in the test I've set her."
    "Veo cómo sus párpados tiemblan y comienzan a elevarse, casi como si estuviera pasando la prueba que le puse en frente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3838
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_302e8549:

    # "But her body is so completely wrecked. The temptation to give up and rest again must be immense, and I'm hardly encouraging her mind to fight it. Far from it, in fact."
    "Pero su cuerpo está hecho trizas. La tentación de rendirse y descansar debe ser inmensa, y poco estoy haciendo por alentar a su mente a luchar. Todo lo contrario, de hecho."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3839
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0e787947:

    # ks "And it's completely fine if your eyelids remain so heavy that you find it hard to keep them open. Completely okay if you want to give up and let them close again."
    ks "Y está completamente bien si tus párpados siguen tan pesados que te es difícil mantenerlos abiertos. Si te quieres rendir y dejar que se cierren."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3840
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a1689045:

    # "So she can try to escape her trance. She can struggle to break free."
    "Así que puede intentar escapar del trance. Puede luchar por liberarse."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3841
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_23f7bfc1:

    # ks "Nothing bad will happen if they close, Hiroko. All it means is that you've chosen to stay in this nice, comfortable state of hypnosis for me."
    ks "Nada malo pasará si se cierran, Hiroko. Solo significa que elegiste quedarte en este agradable y cómodo estado de hipnosis para mí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3842
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7a53e78c:

    # "But she WILL fail. And when she does, she'll totally believe her failure was hers to decide."
    "Pero VA a fracasar. Y cuando lo haga, estará convencida de que ese fracaso fue su decisión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3843
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ae7163b1:

    # ks "And when they do close, you will find yourself dropping deeper into trance. Even deeper into that comfortable, relaxing state of hypnosis."
    ks "Y cuando se cierren, caerás más profundo en trance. Más profundo en ese cómodo y relajante estado de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3845
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3ef1a0b3:

    # h sleeptalk "Uurh... ahhh..."
    h sleeptalk "Eeh... aaah..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3845
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_795d8eaf:

    # "You really are a lot of fun to mess with, Hiroko. But don't worry, I think you'll start to lighten up about this stuff from now on."
    "Sí que es muy divertido jugar contigo, Hiroko. Pero no te preocupes, creo que tu actitud comenzará a mejorar a partir de ahora."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3846
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d55e115e:

    # ks "That's alright, Hiroko, you don't have to struggle anymore if you don't want to. Simply relax and go deeper now."
    ks "Muy bien, Hiroko, ya no tienes que esforzarte más si no quieres. Simplemente relájate y cae más profundo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3848
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3fed623e:

    # ks "All this means is that you've chosen to be hypnotized. Because remember, only you have this power to remain so deeply hypnotized. My words can only ever guide you." with dissolve
    ks "Esto solo significa que elegiste ser hipnotizada. Porque recuerda, solo tú tienes el poder de permanecer tan profundo en trance. Mis palabras solo pueden guiarte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3849
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_dae3d960:

    # ks "Nobody is forcing you to do anything, Hiroko. You never had to perform in front of a camera, just as you never had to yawn in class when your phone went off."
    ks "Nadie te está obligando a hacer nada, Hiroko. Tú no tenías que actuar frente a la cámara, y no tenías que bostezar en clase cuando tu teléfono vibraba."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3850
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0c72a23f:

    # ks "You're relaxed because you want to relax. You're hypnotized, because you want to be hypnotized."
    ks "Estás relajada porque quieres estar relajada. Estás hipnotizada porque quieres estar hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3851
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2a5a28fa:

    # ks "And you're listening to me now... because you want to listen."
    ks "Y estás escuchándome ahora... porque quieres escucharme."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3852
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_23d28632:

    # ks "So now it's time you admitted this to me, and most importantly to yourself..."
    ks "Y ahora es momento de que lo admitas, no solo para mí sino para ti misma."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3853
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5b89d75d:

    # ks "You want to be hypnotized. Don't you, Hiroko."
    ks "Tú quieres ser hipnotizada. ¿No es así, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3854
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0c0a7b95:

    # h sleeptalk "Mrrn... I..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Mmmn... qu-..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3858
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_98de1332:

    # h "I want to be hypnotized... y-yeah..." with dissolve
    h "Quiero ser hipnotizada... s-sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3857
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b0e4d287:

    # ks "You feel comfortable about being hypnotized by me. Don't you." with dissolve
    ks "Te agrada ser hipnotizada por mí. ¿No es así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3858
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_921e7014:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah... comfortable." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Sí... me agrada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3860
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_dd96b7d1:

    # ks "All that rage you've been expressing. All that anger and fear and embarrassment over being hypnotized by me..." with dissolve
    ks "Toda esa furia que has estado expresando. Toda esa ira y miedo y vergüenza por ser hipnotizada por mí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3861
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b15b02ac:

    # ks "It was all because you didn't want to accept the truth of your own feelings, wasn't it?"
    ks "Todo era porque no querías aceptar la verdad y admitir lo que sentías, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3862
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c745bcca:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah... didn't wanna... didn't wanna accept... the truth..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Sí... no quería... no quería aceptar... la verdad..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3864
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e0253fa0:

    # ks "But now that you've been honest about your feelings with me... don't you think you can accept it now?" with dissolve
    ks "Pero ahora que has sido honesta conmigo sobre tus sentimientos... ¿no crees que ahora puedes aceptarlos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3865
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_46c324b7:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3867
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4ff4feae:

    # ks "That's good, Hiroko. It always feels good to be honest about what you feel." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, Hiroko. Siempre se siente bien ser honesta con lo que sientes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3868
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_de3b5d73:

    # ks "You enjoy being hypnotized. It makes you feel good when I hypnotize you, and you like following my directions under hypnosis."
    ks "Disfrutas ser hipnotizada. Te hace sentir bien que yo te hipnotice, y te gusta seguir mi dirección bajo hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3869
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8ac28375:

    # ks "And besides, you really want to honor the deal you made with me, don't you?"
    ks "Y además, quieres honrar el trato que hiciste conmigo, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3870
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d4ffaede:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah... 'course I do..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Sí... claro que sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3872
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a5721691:

    # ks "That's exactly right. So when I next wake you from this state of trance, you'll awaken happy and refreshed, and fully aware of this conversation we've just had." with dissolve
    ks "Exactamente. Así que, cuando despiertes de este estado de trance, te sentirás fresca y alegre, y completamente consciente de la conversación que acabamos de tener." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3873
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8246d4cd:

    # ks "And you'll be completely comfortable and willing to honor your commitment to be my hypnotized assistant for my next show. Isn't that right?"
    ks "Y te sentirás completamente cómoda y dispuesta a honrar tu compromiso de ser mi asistente hipnotizada en mi próximo espectáculo. ¿No es así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3876
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_de275909:

    # ks "Wonderful, Hiroko. Feeling so incredibly hypnotized. Feeling so incredibly easy to hypnotize." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso, Hiroko. Te sientes increíblemente hipnotizada. Te sientes increíblemente fácil de hipnotizar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3878
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5dfb41fc:

    # ks "So now, waking up slowly as I count up to five."
    ks "Y ahora, despierta lentamente mientras cuento hasta cinco."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3880
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2ad9f18c:

    # ks "One, two... breathing nice and slow, feeling good."
    ks "Uno, dos... respira hondo, sintiéndote muy bien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3882
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fb779f84:

    # ks "Three... four... eyes opening, conscious thought returning..."
    ks "Tres... cuatro... tus ojos se abren, tu consciencia regresa..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3884
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3b1f728d:

    # ks "{cps=15}And... {w=0.5}{/cps}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=15}Y... {w=0.5}{/cps}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3886
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_79404a26:

    # extend "five, wide awake."
    extend "cinco, despierta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3888
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7a712c70:

    # h sleepy "..." with dissolve
    h sleepy "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3889
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b27a5ca1:

    # "I watch quietly as Hiroko's tired eyes slowly flicker open."
    "Observo en silencio cómo los ojos de Hiroko se abren suavemente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3890
