# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4104
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_10509093:

    # "I barely got enough sleep last night."
    "Apenas pude dormir anoche."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4106
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_dabd97d2:

    # "Not because I turned in late. Nozomi has an early start, so we headed home shortly after we wrapped up at karaoke."
    "No porque haya regresado tarde. Nozomi debía levantarse temprano hoy, por lo que nos fuimos a casa poco después de salir del karaoke."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4107
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cfb6fe85:

    # "But I wasn't upset. Not least because we promised each other that we'd meet again today; make the absolute best of our weekend."
    "Pero eso no me molestó. Ni un poquito, pues prometimos que volveríamos a vernos hoy; aprovechar al máximo nuestro fin de semana."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4108
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5a3fb036:

    # "And although I turned in early myself, I could hardly stop thinking about my perfect girlfriend. My Nozomi."
    "Y si bien yo también me fui a la cama temprano, apenas pude dejar de pensar en mi perfecta novia. Mi Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4109
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_8b0db6e0:

    # "She really has it all now. The looks, the personality..."
    "Ahora de verdad lo tiene todo. La apariencia, la personalidad..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4110
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_272adf10:

    # "I couldn't have slept in today if I tried."
    "No podría dormir hasta tarde hoy, aunque lo intentara."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4112
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_1eacf993:

    # "So I get up at the crack of dawn, shower, and do the last thing I ever expected to do."
    "Así que me levanto al amanecer, me ducho, y hago lo último que jamás esperé hacer."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4113
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3558c0dd:

    # "Head to school on a freaking Sunday!"
    "¡Ir a la escuela un maldito domingo!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4115
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bc7883c4:

    # "I arrive at the school sports field in good time."
    "Llego a buen tiempo a los campos deportivos de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4116
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_353cc669:

    # "She told me there's a big event here today, and although there's a couple of people milling around, I don't see much evidence of that yet."
    "Me dijo que hoy hay un gran evento aquí, y si bien hay unas cuantas personas rondando por ahí, aún no veo mucha evidencia de ello."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4117
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e2b74083:

    # "Hell, I don't even know what sport is going on. I never actually thought to ask her about that."
    "Caray, ni siquiera sé de qué deporte se trata. Nunca se me ocurrió preguntarle nada de eso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4119
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_eec89d22:

    # "... Why does that bother me all of a sudden?"
    "... ¿Por qué eso empieza a molestarme de repente?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4121
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_28d6892a:

    # a "Kyou! You made it!"
    a "¡Kyou! ¡Llegaste!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4122
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_60213fb1:

    # "Fortunately, the enticing sound of my new girlfriend calling out to me distracts me from such cares before I have another moment to dwell on them."
    "Afortunadamente, la cautivadora voz de mi novia llamándome me distrae de esas preocupaciones antes de que pueda pasar otro momento pensando en ellas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4125
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e99e1c49:

    # "Everything feels right when she's with me." with dissolve
    "Todo se siente en su lugar cuando ella está conmigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4126
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_64cb958c:

    # ks casual smile "N-Nozomi! You're here!"
    ks casual smile "¡N-Nozomi! ¡Aquí estás!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4127
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ea5c1dad:

    # a giggle "Hehe, and so are you! Gosh, you even got here before me, you eager-beaver~" with dissolve
    a giggle "Jeje, ¡y tú también! Dios, incluso llegaste antes que yo, come-ansias." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4128
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a4f11adc:

    # ks blush "Damn right I am. As if I'm ever gonna skip out on spending time with you."
    ks blush "Pero claro que sí. Como si fuera a dejar ir una oportunidad de pasar tiempo contigo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4130
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f541a1f0:

    # "Nozomi giggles as she wraps her arms around me for a quick embrace as she plants a sweet peck on my cheek." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me envuelve en sus brazos con una risita, dándome un beso en la mejilla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4131
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_438fe5f7:

    # a "That's so sweet."
    a "Qué dulce."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4132
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_abb6b02b:

    # "As we pull away, I have to notice she's still wearing the clothes I bought her yesterday, and she quickly catches my glance."
    "Una vez termina el abrazo, me doy cuenta de que aún lleva la ropa que le compré ayer, y ella rápidamente nota mi mirada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4135
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_fc0da195:

    # a shy blush "Although I have to say, I do feel a little sheepish about wearing this out here. I guess it's not exactly work appropriate?" with dissolve
    a shy blush "Aunque debo decir que me da algo de pena llevar esta ropa aquí. ¿Supongo que no es exactamente apta para el trabajo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4136
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e7f7d132:

    # ks "Maybe not. But I love that you did, Nozomi."
    ks "Tal vez no. Pero me encanta que la hayas traído, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4137
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_22e32d62:

    # a happy "Mm! Besides, what else was I going to wear?" with dissolve
    a happy "¡Mm! Además, ¿qué otra cosa iba a usar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4139
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ab82dece:

    # a smile "It's okay to wear this today, right?" with dissolve
    a smile "Está bien usarla hoy, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4140
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_24d4c05a:

    # ks "Of course it is. I want you to enjoy it, Nozomi."
    ks "Por supuesto que sí. Quiero que la disfrutes, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4141
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c841f2b8:

    # a happy "Mm, and I do~ " with dissolve
    a happy "Mm, y sí que la disfruto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4142
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_93b13178:

    # a smile -blush "I was looking through my wardrobe, but so little seems to appeal any more, you know?" with dissolve
    a smile -blush "Busqué entre mi guardarropa, pero ahora muy poco me llama la atención, ¿sabes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4143
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bc4448c0:

    # ks "Yeah, I get it. This outfit's gonna be hard to top."
    ks "Sí, lo entiendo. Este atuendo será difícil de superar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4146
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_05b417b4:

    # "We smile at each other, enjoying this moment of bliss in each other's company." with dissolve
    "Nos miramos con una sonrisa, disfrutando este momento de alegría en compañía del otro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4147
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_8b397f2e:

    # "If I only I could take her away from here; go on another date. The fact I can't is so immensely frustrating to me right now."
    "Si tan solo pudiera sacarla de aquí; ir a otra cita. No poder en este momento me parece tan frustrante."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4148
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_dc97fbe5:

    # ks -blush "So what's the plan for today? We ARE going to have time for each other later, right?"
    ks -blush "Entonces, ¿cuál es el plan? SÍ vamos a tener tiempo para pasar juntos después, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4150
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_94da79dd:

    # a happy "Oh, of course! I can surely catch some time between setting things up to hang out with you during the day, you'll see~" with dissolve
    a happy "¡Oh, por supuesto! Estoy segura de que encontraré algo de tiempo que compartir contigo entre preparativos, ya verás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4151
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_889aeb82:

    # a shy "And once we're all done here, maybe we can go out and do something for the evening. How does that sound?" with dissolve
    a shy "Y una vez todo esté listo por aquí, tal vez podamos salir a hacer algo en la tarde. ¿Qué tal suena eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4153
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0cc7bc7b:

    # ks "Yeah, that'll work. So uh, what needs doing exactly?"
    ks "Sí, eso funcionará. Entonces, eh, ¿qué es lo que tiene que hacerse?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4155
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e0c4cb77:

    # a "Right, well, we just need to put up some signage, set up the nets and register the players as they arrive." with dissolve
    a "Claro, pues, solo tenemos que poner algunos señalamientos, preparar las redes y registrar a las jugadoras cuando lleguen." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4156
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_41a80d12:

    # a smile_side "Then we're on duty handing out refreshments, updating scorecards... some of us even volunteered to be ball girls and boys for the games." with dissolve
    a smile_side "Luego nos toca repartir refrigerios, actualizar las tarjetas de puntuación... algunos de nosotros incluso se ofrecieron a ser recogepelotas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4158
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_08213bd1:

    # "\"Nets\"? \"Ball boys and...\""
    "¿\"Redes\"? \"Recogepelotas\", \"jugadoras\"..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4159
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_74d4e4df:

    # ks confused "You did?"
    ks confused "¿En serio?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4160
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_294ce5b1:

    # "This is..."
    "Esto es..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4161
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4fbb98a8:

    # a happy "Well, not me personally. But yes, the only officials are the umpires and some outside observers?" with dissolve
    a happy "Bueno, no yo personalmente. Pero sí, los únicos oficiales son los jueces de línea y algunos observadores externos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4162
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0b6c5d3e:

    # a smile "And the tennis club can't handle it themselves since obviously a lot of them are playing today." with dissolve
    a smile "Y las del club de tenis no pueden hacerlo ellas mismas, ya que obviamente muchas de ellas van a jugar hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4163
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b563c89b:

    # "... a tennis tournament. Then that means..."
    "... un torneo de tenis femenil. Eso significa..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4165
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6d123ebb:

    # h "Oh fuck me, what is this?" with dissolve
    h "Su puta madre, ¿qué es eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4170
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_446a97bb:

    # "... Hiroko." with dissolve
    "... Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4171
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_25ba791f:

    # "She comes to a stop as she's about to pass us by, her eyes fixed on my girlfriend as she seems to take in her new look with a puzzled expression."
    "Se detiene mientras pasaba junto a nosotros, quedando sus ojos fijos en mi novia, al parecer observando su nueva imagen con una perpleja expresión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4172
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_25e0878e:

    # a happy "Ah, good morning, Hiroko. I hope you have a great tournament today!" with dissolve
    a happy "Ah, buenos días, Hiroko. ¡Espero que tengas un buen torneo hoy!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4173
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bac083c6:

    # h frown_side "Uh... h'yeah, sure. But what's going on with you? What's with that getup?" with dissolve
    h frown_side "Eh... sí, claro. Pero ¿qué onda contigo? ¿Qué te hiciste o qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4174
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_60cc33be:

    # "But she's not going to spoil our day. I won't let her."
    "Pero no va a arruinar nuestro día. No lo permitiré."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4175
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2b0c59f1:

    # ks frown "Is there a problem, Hiroko?"
    ks frown "¿Algún problema, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4177
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_7d5ac770:

    # h angry "An' you!{w=0.5}{nw} What the fuck are " with dissolve
    h angry "¡Y tú!{w=0.5}{nw} ¿Qué carajos haces " with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4178
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_fcf621ee:

    # extend "YOU doing here?" with vpunch
    extend "TÚ aquí?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4179
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6f3e2e44:

    # "Hiroko wheels round to face me, a finger thrust at my chest like she's about to go off on another of her screaming tirades."
    "Hiroko se da la vuelta para encararme, poniéndome un dedo en el pecho como si estuviera a punto de iniciar otra ronda de gritos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4182
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b57c32b6:

    # h "I... nope, fuck off. I don't have time for this shit. Not today!" with dissolve
    h "Te... nop, a al carajo. No tengo tiempo para esta mierda. ¡Hoy no!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4183
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3c6ce04c:

    # "But she mercifully cuts herself short, instead angrily turning from us both as she storms away towards the tennis courts."
    "Pero se detiene misericordiosamente, y en vez de eso se da la vuelta y se aleja de nosotros en dirección a las canchas de tenis."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4185
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_7213dac8:

    # h angry_side "Not fuckin' today. Just FUCK off, the pair of ya..." with dissolve
    h angry_side "Hoy no estoy para estas pendejadas. Solo váyanse a CAGAR ustedes dos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4186
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_75ba3418:

    # a sad "Oh my. I think I might have set her off somehow." with dissolve
    a sad "Oh, vaya. Creo que de algún modo la hice enojar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4187
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f2d74c36:

    # ks sigh "It's not your fault. She's just like that."
    ks sigh "No es culpa tuya. Así es ella."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4188
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d2715eda:

    # a sigh "I know. I just thought... well..." with dissolve
    a sigh "Lo sé. Solo pensé que... bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4189
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_968f8ece:

    # "I wait a moment for her to finish what she was going to say, but she only goes on to shake her head."
    "Espero un momento a que termine lo que estaba a punto de decir, pero únicamente sacude la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4190
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_888298e6:

    # a neutral "No, it's nothing; just Hiroko being Hiroko, that's all." with dissolve
    a neutral "No, no es nada; es solo Hiroko siendo Hiroko, eso es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4192
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5fe06944:

    # "And in no time at all that heavenly smile re-appears on her beautiful face." with dissolve
    "Y en un instante esa sonrisa celestial reaparece en su bello rostro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4193
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2284c6dc:

    # a "Besides, I need to get to it. But I was wondering..."
    a "Además, tengo que ponerme a trabajar. Pero me estaba preguntando..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4194
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_983ed070:

    # a giggle blush "... Do you think you might want to help me out?" with dissolve
    a giggle blush "... ¿Te gustaría ayudarme?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4195
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a85def66:

    # "I have to chuckle at that, and I flash her a grin."
    "No puedo evitar soltar una pequeña risa, y le ofrezco una sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4196
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_9c65dca9:

    # ks smirk "Was this your plan all along, Nozomi? Bringing me out here to do your dirty work?"
    ks smirk "¿Este fue tu plan desde el comienzo, Nozomi? ¿Traerme acá a hacer tu trabajo sucio?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4197
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_280fbe07:

    # a embarrassed "Ehehehe~ W-well, we might be a little short-staffed again; we often are at these things." with dissolve
    a embarrassed "Ejejeje. B-bueno, puede que estemos algo cortos de personal otra vez; suele pasar en esta clase de cosas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4198
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_77616aad:

    # a shy "But at least this way we can be around each other more during the day, right?" with dissolve
    a shy "Pero al menos así podemos pasar más tiempo juntos durante el día, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4199
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_baf834a4:

    # "To be honest, I'm not exactly relishing spending my time running around doing chores for these people on my day off. But she does make a good point."
    "Para ser honesto, no me emociona precisamente pasar parte de mi día libre corriendo de un lado a otro haciendo tareas por estas personas. Pero ella tiene un buen punto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4200
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_89d20df1:

    # ks smile "Alright, Nozomi, you got me. Lead on."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Nozomi, tú ganas. Dime qué hay que hacer."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4202
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c05a8903:

    # "Besides, there's no way I'm gonna just hang around here by myself. She's literally the only reason I'm here at all."
    "Además, no pienso quedarme por ahí solo sin hacer nada. Ella es la única razón por la que estoy aquí, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4204
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a0bbab47:

    # "So I spent the next hour helping to set up the tennis courts, putting signs out front for the general public, and some other busywork."
    "Así que paso la siguiente hora ayudándola a preparar las canchas de tenis, poniendo señalamientos para el público general, y otras tareas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4206
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d0d81840:

    # "Nozomi was right about being short-staffed. Most of the student council were no-shows, and at least some of those here seemed happy for my unexpected assistance."
    "Nozomi tenía razón con lo del corto personal. Casi nadie del consejo estudiantil se apareció, y algunos aquí parecían estar felices de que yo participara."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4208
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e1f7db52:

    # "And I for one was appreciative of the fact Nozomi was by my side for most of our work." with dissolve
    "Y yo aprecio el hecho de que Nozomi estuvo a mi lado durante la mayor parte de nuestro trabajo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4209
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3cdd9867:

    # "Although I couldn't help but observe the looks everyone was giving her when they didn't think she'd notice."
    "Aunque no pude evitar notar las miradas que todos le estaban dando cuando creían que no se daría cuenta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4210
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_7f5ceeeb:

    # "And she's trying not to let it show. I always see her smiling when I look her way as we work together..."
    "Y ella intenta que no se note. Siempre la veo sonreír cuando volteo en su dirección mientras trabajamos juntos..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4212
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_fcd8c234:

    # "... But the longer the hour drags on, the less that smile seems to stay on her face." with dissolve
    "... Pero entre más avanza la hora, menos parece quedarse esa sonrisa en su rostro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4213
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_af3ad85e:

    # ks casual neutral "Hey... Nozomi?"
    ks casual neutral "Oye... ¿Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4214
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4a537579:

    # a neutral "{cps=15}Hm...? {w=1.0}{/cps}{nw}" with dissolve
    a neutral "{cps=15}¿Mm...? {w=1.0}{/cps}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4217
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_aa651d23:

    # extend "Oh hey, Kyou. What's on your mind?"
    extend "Oh, ¿qué pasa, Kyou? ¿En qué estás pensando?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4218
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_7cc12c81:

    # ks smile "I'm still thinking about how beautitful you look today. Just thought you should know that in case you forgot."
    ks smile "Sigo pensando en lo hermosa que te ves hoy. Solo pensé que debías saberlo en caso de que se te haya olvidado."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4219
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_579f9a5b:

    # a happy blush "Mhmhmhmhmhm~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a happy blush "Jijijijiji. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4220
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_25e2709c:

    # "Nozomi pauses what she's doing for a moment to self-consciously run a hand through her hair as she giggles."
    "Nozomi pausa lo que está haciendo un momento, luciendo autoconsciente al pasar una mano por su cabello con una risita."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4221
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2da1f7c7:

    # a smile "Guess I looked like I needed cheering up, huh?" with dissolve
    a smile "Supongo que parece que necesito algo de ánimo, ¿eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4222
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_aa32e0db:

    # ks "I mean, kinda? None of these guys seem to be talking to us much."
    ks "Pues, ¿un poco? Ninguno de estos sujetos parece hablarnos mucho."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4223
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_73aca094:

    # a confused -blush "O-oh well, it's not like I'm in charge today anyway. And we all know what we need to do." with dissolve
    a confused -blush "O-oh, bueno, no es como si hoy estuviera a cargo ni nada. Y todos sabemos lo que tenemos que hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4224
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_fa8ef3ac:

    # "She says as we set up the last of the water bottles down on a table made for the players, before we turn around to inspect the courts."
    "Dice ella mientras colocamos la última botella de agua en una mesa para las jugadoras, para luego darse la vuelta e inspeccionar las canchas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4226
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_01e21c7c:

    # "Pretty much everything is organized for the event now, and right on schedule as we notice the first members of the public filter through the school gates in the distance." with dissolve
    "Básicamente ya todo está organizado para el evento, y justo a tiempo, viendo a lo lejos a los primeros miembros del público entrar por las puertas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4227
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_273f1b11:

    # a "I... I don't mind all that much, really."
    a "No... no me molesta, de verás."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4228
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c7197396:

    # a neutral "Besides, I'd be a fool if I thought things were going to go any different. To think anyone might actually be happy for me." with dissolve
    a neutral "Además, sería una tonta en pensar que las cosas serían diferentes. Pensar que alguien estaría feliz por mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4229
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_9e42a75f:

    # "My head is shaking before I even realize I'm doing it."
    "Mi cabeza se sacude antes de que siquiera lo note."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4230
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c7e97133:

    # a confused "You really don't think so?" with dissolve
    a confused "¿De verdad no lo crees?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4231
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_49e4bd71:

    # ks neutral "Nozomi, you're not a fool. Everything you're doing, you know I support you one-hundred percent, right?"
    ks neutral "Nozomi, no eres una tonta. Lo que sea que hagas, sabes que te apoyaré al cien por ciento, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4232
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_83e5de1a:

    # a neutral "I know. You're even still calling me \"Nozomi\", even now that we're here amongst everyone." with dissolve
    a neutral "Lo sé. Hasta sigues llamándome \"Nozomi\", incluso ahora que estamos entre todos los demás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4233
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_79c244b2:

    # ks "I've been careful not to let them hear it. Besides, isn't that what you want to be called?"
    ks "He tenido cuidado de que no me escuchen. Además, ¿qué no es así como quieres que te llame?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4235
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f1165cf7:

    # a "I-I'm not saying I don't enjoy it, but..." with dissolve
    a "N-no estoy diciendo que no lo disfrute, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4236
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e783d849:

    # ks frown "You know they don't give a damn about you, so who cares what they think any more? Those guys were never gonna accept you anyway, no matter what you do."
    ks frown "Ya sabes que no les importas, entonces ¿qué más da lo que opinen? Esas personas nunca te iban a aceptar te dodos modos, sin importar lo que hicieras."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4237
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a503bded:

    # ks "If they can't see you for the kind, beautiful soul that you've become, then it's their loss isn't it?"
    ks "Si no pueden verte como la cordial y hermosa alma que te has vuelto, entonces es su problema, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4238
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_14704a63:

    # a drowsy "Kyou..." with dissolve
    a drowsy "Kyou..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4239
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a5115183:

    # ks "So stop worrying about what anyone else thinks. So long as we have each other, we'll be all right. You'll be all right."
    ks "Así que deja de preocuparte por lo que otros piensen. Siempre y cuando nos tengamos el uno al otro, todo estará bien. Tú estarás bien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4240
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e02ea1d6:

    # "I reach out to take her hand, and she makes no move to stop me as I try to emulate that kindly smile of hers."
    "Tomo su mano, y ella no hace intento alguno por detenerme, mientras intento emular su gentil sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4242
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_47110663:

    # ks smile "I'll never let you go, Nozomi. No matter what, I'll never leave your side, okay?" with dissolve
    ks smile "Nunca te dejaré ir, Nozomi. Sin importar qué, nunca me apartaré de tu lado, ¿está bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4244
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_524be5d5:

    # n "... Akiko?"
    n "... ¿Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4246
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bb41a457:

    # n "I-is that...?" with dissolve
    n "¿E-eres tú...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4251
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_08b6e3a5:

    # n "W-w-why do you look like... what..." with dissolve
    n "¿P-p-por qué te vez como... qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4252
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_234b1340:

    # n shocked_side "Wh- w-what is going ON?!" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡¿Qu- q-qué está PASANDO?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4253
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a39869d8:

    # "My heart stops cold as I slowly turn my head to register a voice I now wish wasn't so familiar to me."
    "Mi corazón se detiene mientras giro lentamente la cabeza, siguiendo la voz que ahora desearía que no me fuera tan familiar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4255
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c64c4e3a:

    # a "You don't... Don't you like it, Nozomi? I thought at least you would..." with dissolve
    a "¿No te... no te gusta, Nozomi? Pensé que al menos a ti te gustaría..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4256
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0894c5ca:

    # "The commotion around the tennis courts feel as if they've been afflicted by a deathly silence while I see standing before us a woman staring open-mouthed."
    "Pareciera que la conmoción en las canchas de tenis se hubiera sumido en un mortal silencio mientras veo de pie frente a nosotros a una mujer boquiabierta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4257
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_779b5953:

    # "Her face seems fixed in an expression of abject terror, before she begins to speak in a trembling tone."
    "Su rostro parece congelarse en una expresión de abyecto terror, y posteriormente comienza hablar con un tono temblante."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4258
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_005521c0:

    # n sad_side "L-like it? What have... what have you done to yourself, Akiko?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿G-gustarme? ¿Qué te... qué es lo que te has hecho, Akiko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4259
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cb378530:

    # "SHE'S here? Today?!"
    "¿ELLA está aquí? ¡¿Hoy?!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4260
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ba8cb747:

    # n sad_closed "Your hair, those glasses, I... I thought I was being paranoid the other day, but now?" with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Tu cabello, esos anteojos, pensé... pensé que estaba paranoica el toro día, pero ¿ahora?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4261
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_485b95c9:

    # n sad_side "What in the world could've possessed you to make yourself up to look like me?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Qué rayos fue lo que te impulsó a hacerte lucir como yo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4262
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b0805f91:

    # a sad_side2 "I-I... I...." with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "E-este... pues..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4263
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_86cdefd5:

    # "What do I do? What do I even say to the girl I used to love in front of my... my true love?"
    "¿Qué hago? ¿Qué le digo a la mujer que solía amar delante de mi... verdadero amor?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4271
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_8ee3825f:

    # n shocked_side "Why would you think I'd like this? You can't possibly think I'd enjoy seeing you like this! Why would anyone?" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¿Qué te hizo creer que me gustaría esto? ¡¿Por qué pensarías que me agradaría verte así?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4272
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_89c98c5c:

    # "I can only stand by as all of this plays out helplessly before my eyes."
    "Solo puedo quedarme de pie viendo cómo esto se desarrolla frente a mis ojos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4273
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_412ba9aa:

    # n "This isn't you at all!"
    n "¡Esta no eres tú!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4275
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_03cf4b61:

    # a "I can't be me any more, Nozomi. But if I can even come close to the person you are? Wouldn't that be incredible?" with dissolve
    a "Ya no puedo ser yo, Nozomi. Pero si puedo al menos acercarme a la persona que tú eres... ¿No sería eso increíble?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4276
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_53624d7f:

    # n sad_side "The person I am? Why on earth..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿La persona que yo soy? Pero ¿por qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4277
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bb2894a2:

    # a surprised_side "Because you're PERFECT, Nozomi! Don't you know that?" with dissolve
    a surprised_side "¡Porque tú eres PERFECTA, Nozomi!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4278
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ec86eb72:

    # n neutral_side "I... Akiko, you're not making any sense." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "¿Soy...? Akiko, ¿de qué estás hablando?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4279
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2ff74bfd:

    # a sad_side2 "Nozomi you're such an all-round lovely person, and you're so... so beautiful. So beautiful it hurts." with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "Nozomi, eres una persona tan polifacética y encantadora, y eres tan... tan hermosa. Tan hermosa que duele." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4280
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_119235a0:

    # a sad_closed2 "It's just like you to not even realize how wonderful you really are. Not even know why you'd inspire someone as lowly as me." with dissolve
    a sad_closed2 "Veo que no te das cuenta de lo maravillosa que eres. Ni siquiera sabes por qué inspirarías a alguien tan inferior como yo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4281
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d2ab6948:

    # n sad_side "As lowly as... what are you even saying?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Tan inferior como... ¿qué es lo que estás diciendo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4282
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a9ef5e1c:

    # a sad_side "But don't you see, Nozomi? That's how much I respect you! That's why I want to be everything that you are!" with dissolve
    a sad_side "Pero ¿no lo ves, Nozomi? ¡Esto es muestra de mi respeto por ti! ¡Es por eso que quiero ser todo lo que tú eres!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4283
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cd840f0a:

    # a surprised_side "You understand now, right? Please tell me you understand, I... I-I need you to understand!" with dissolve
    a surprised_side "Lo entiendes ahora, ¿verdad? Por favor, dime que lo entiendes, ne-... ¡n-necesito que lo entiendas!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4284
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0d2678d7:

    # n sad_closed "I don't. Akiko, I don't understand you at all..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "No, Akiko, no lo entiendo para nada..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4287
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_8eecd44f:

    # "I observe that as Nozomi speaks those words, her gaze suddenly shifts towards me." with dissolve
    "Observo cómo, al decir esas palabras, Nozomi torna su mirada repentinamente hacia mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4288
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_02bedcf8:

    # n frown "But when I think about what I do understand..." with dissolve
    n frown "Pero cuando pienso en lo que sí entiendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4289
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a637aa07:

    # s "... Akiko?"
    s "... ¿Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4290
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_805a49c1:

    # "Those round, brown eyes seem to bore into my soul, even as another voice ineffectively attempts to cut the tension."
    "Esos redondos ojos marrones parecen perforar mi alma, incluso mientras otra voz intenta infructuosamente cortar la tensión."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4293
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e757cf2e:

    # s "My word, it IS you, isn't it?" with dissolve
    s "Santo cielo, SÍ eres tú, ¿o me equivoco?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4294
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d4dcef28:

    # "And I watch as my girlfriend visibly seems to wither before the sight of the latest gawker; her shoulders sagging, her head lowering."
    "Y observo cómo mi novia parece marchitarse al ver a la nueva espectadora; sus hombros se aflojan, su cabeza decae."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4296
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6c757cd3:

    # a "Yes, Sayori it's... it's just me." with dissolve
    a "Sí, Sayori, soy... soy solo yo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4297
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3c1419da:

    # "Like the life's being drained out of her body before my very eyes."
    "Como si la vida estuviera siendo drenada de su cuerpo delante de mis ojos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4299
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cffbc0ea:

    # a sad_side "I'll always just be Akiko, huh." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Siempre seré solo Akiko, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4300
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f71b4ebd:

    # "Surely they notice it too. But they won't let up, will they?"
    "Tienen que notarlo ellas también. Pero no van a retroceder, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4301
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ba3f00a3:

    # s concerned "I knew there was something suspect about your appearance the other day, but to think that this was your goal?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Sabía que había algo sospechoso sobre tu apariencia anteayer, pero ¿pensar que este era tu objetivo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4302
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_568192af:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "I am struggling to comprehend why you would do such a thing." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Me cuesta comprender por qué harías algo como esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4303
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_acfac662:

    # "I should get her out of here, away from these judgmental assholes."
    "Tengo que sacarla de aquí, lejos de estas críticas de mierda."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4305
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d12372e0:

    # a "I just don't understand why no one's getting it." with dissolve
    a "Yo no comprendo por qué nadie lo entiende." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4306
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_da5a4bf0:

    # "But on the other hand, maybe it's good for her to have this experience."
    "Pero, por otro lado, tal vez es bueno que tenga esta experiencia."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4307
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_75697c30:

    # a sad_side "Who would want to be Akiko?" with dissolve
    a sad_side "¿Quién querría ser Akiko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4308
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e246b722:

    # "To have these girls reject her, and give her the will to fully reject her former self in turn."
    "Que estas chicas la rechacen, y le den la voluntad de rechazar por completo a su antigua yo en respuesta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4313
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f4608297:

    # a "Akiko wants to understand people, but she's so nosy and incompetent that she doesn't know when to shut up." with dissolve
    a "Akiko quiere entender a la gente, pero es tan entrometida e incompetente que no sabe cuándo callarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4314
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4194c4b3:

    # "Because yeah, my Nozomi will never want to go back to the plain girl she used to be. Not after this."
    "Porque sí, mi Nozomi nunca querrá regresar a la chica escueta que solía ser. No después de esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4316
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_36028860:

    # s concerned "Akiko..." with dissolve
    s concerned "Akiko..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4317
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_1847317c:

    # "So maybe I don't need to worry myself at all. Maybe I just need to let this play out, painful as it is to hear."
    "Entonces tal vez no tengo ni que preocuparme. Tal vez solo debo dejar que esto se desarrolle, por doloroso que sea escucharlo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4319
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5f454ec9:

    # a sad_closed "She's ugly and graceless, she fails in everything she tries but she keeps trying the same things over and over because she's the very definition of insanity." with dissolve
    a sad_closed "Es fea y sin gracia, fracasa en todo lo que intenta, pero continúa intentando las mismas cosas una y otra vez porque es la definición de la locura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4320
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e7ed4f42:

    # "It'll be alright in the end, my Nozomi."
    "Todo estará bien al final, mi Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4321
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4c6f1177:

    # a cry "She's so stupid, t-to keep trying even though she'll never accomplish anything in her worthless life!" with dissolve
    a cry "¡Es una estúpida que continúa intentando a pesar de que nunca logrará nada en su inservible vida!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4323
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_96feac87:

    # a "All Akiko will ever do is mess up. Her dreams will go unfulfilled and she'll spend her life alone in some dingy apartment with only her cats to keep her company." with dissolve
    a "Lo único que Akiko jamás logrará es meter la pata. Ninguno de sus sueños se cumplirá y pasará su vida sola en un sucio apartamento sin más que sus gatos como compañía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4324
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_364f2aa2:

    # "You'll never have to be that girl ever again, Nozomi. I can promise you that."
    "Nunca tendrás que ser esa chica otra vez, Nozomi. Eso te lo puedo prometer."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4326
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e697c8b2:

    # n sad_closed "Oh my God, Akiko. Please stop; you can't seriously believe those awful things!" with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Oh, por Dios, Akiko. Por favor, detente; ¡no puedes creer esas cosas horribles!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4327
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_94b98a11:

    # a cry_happy "Eheh... o-only her cats will ever love her... But Nozomi?" with dissolve
    a cry_happy "Jeje... s-solo sus gatos la amarán... ¿Pero Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4330
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d8cb63fd:

    # a "Nozomi is everything Akiko dreams of being. She's so perfect in every way, so would it be so bad if there were two of Nozomi? And none of Akiko?" with dissolve
    a "Nozomi es todo lo que Akiko sueña con ser. Es tan perfecta en todo aspecto, entonces, ¿sería tan malo si hubiera dos Nozomis? ¿Y ninguna Akiko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4332
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_db8461f5:

    # a cry_smile "And it's just like they say, isn't it? \"Imitation is the sincerest form of flattery\". That's how much I admire you, Nozomi." with dissolve
    a cry_smile "Y es como dice el dicho, ¿verdad? \"La imitación es la forma más sincera de adulación\". Todo esto es porque te admiro, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4335
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_45d3bf36:

    # a cry "Why can't I honour the best girl at school by trying to be everything you are?" with dissolve
    a cry "¿Por qué no puedo honrar a la mejor chica de la escuela intentando ser todo lo que tú eres?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4336
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a04cb280:

    # n sad_closed "This doesn't... \"honour\" me, Akiko, this is..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Esto no me... \"honra\", Akiko, esto es..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4337
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f19b6d5e:

    # a "Why can't you let Akiko die!"
    a "¡Por qué no puedes dejar que Akiko muera!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4339
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ac493861:

    # s casual_folded irritated "Akiko, that's enough. This is perverse." with dissolve
    s casual_folded irritated "Akiko, ya es suficiente. Esto es perverso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4340
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4f4e3471:

    # s casual_folded sleep_concerned "\"Imitation is the sincerest form of flattery that mediocrity can pay to greatness.\" It pains me to hear you believe yourself sub-par, Akiko." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep_concerned "\"La imitación es la forma más sincera de adulación que la mediocridad le puede rendir a la grandeza.\" Me acongoja oír que te consideres tan mísera, Akiko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4342
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0cefa792:

    # s frown "But why in the blazes do you consider yourself mediocre? No, worse?" with dissolve
    s frown "¿Qué te hace creer que eres mediocre? No, ¿peor?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4343
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ebfb272d:

    # s casual angry "You are the student council president, for heaven's sake!" with dissolve
    s casual angry "¡Eres la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, por el amor de Dios!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4344
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b5466aaa:

    # s frown "You are, or... *were* respected before your needless fraternizing with this worthless cretin by your side. Before all of..." with dissolve
    s frown "Eres, o bien... *eras* respetada previo a tu innecesaria confraternización con este despreciable cretino a tu lado. Antes de todo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4345
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_57fc975d:

    # "Sayori waves her hand angrily up and down over \"Akiko's\" trembling form."
    "Sayori señala con su mano de arriba abajo el cuerpo temblante de \"Akiko\"."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4346
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_dac17596:

    # s angry "This!" with dissolve
    s angry "... ¡esto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4347
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6d2ce8b3:

    # s sleeptalk "Rrrg... Look, I have always known you to be eager to challenge yourself and others and yes, perhaps some of us found you off-putting. But you always had noble intentions." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Grr... Mira, sé que no eres ajena a desafiarte a ti misma y a los demás, y sí, quizá algunos te hallamos algo difícil. Pero siempre tuviste intenciones nobles." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4348
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_54bf69f6:

    # s concerned "You are a good person, Akiko. You were always true to yourself and accepting of your flaws and really, what more could anyone ask of you?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Eres una buena persona, Akiko. Siempre fuiste fiel a ti misma y aceptaste tus defectos. ¿Qué más podía pedir alguien de ti?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4349
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_09792f8e:

    # s casual_handup "Is your self-esteem really so low that you would devote yourself to such an insipidly childish fantasy?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup "¿Es tu autoestima tan baja como para decidir dedicarte a una fantasía tan insípidamente infantil?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4350
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e4dc8dc7:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "How could you possibly conceive that you were not valued before now?" with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "¿Cómo pudiste concebir la idea de que no fueses valorada antes de ahora?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4351
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_27509397:

    # n frown "{cps=15}Oh, I think there's only one explanation here that makes s-{/cps}{nw}" with dissolve
    n frown "{cps=15}Oh, creo que solo hay una explicación aquí que tiene s-{/cps}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4354
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f833654e:

    # a "Why did you leave the student council, Sayori?" with dissolve
    a "¿Por qué abandonaste el consejo estudiantil, Sayori?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4356
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_53d13d52:

    # s concerned "What?" with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4358
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a0231109:

    # a angry_side "Why did you leave me?" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¿Por qué me abandonaste a mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4359
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_9857389a:

    # "Huh, so these two have bad blood?"
    "Eh, ¿o sea que hay animosidad entre estas dos?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4360
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_09297ec6:

    # s surprised "Leave you? Akiko, my priorities took me elsewhere. I told you this, did I not?" with dissolve
    s surprised "¿Abandonarte? Akiko, mis prioridades me llevaron a otro lado. Te lo expliqué, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4361
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cea96466:

    # "This is going even better than I thought."
    "Esto está yendo todavía mejor de lo que pensé."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4363
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5717d3fa:

    # a "You could've stayed if you wanted to! Yes, it's harder for us third years like you thought, but you're no stranger to working hard." with dissolve
    a "¡Pudiste quedarte de haberlo querido! Sí, es más difícil para los de tercero como pensaste, pero tú no eres ajena a trabajar duro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4364
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_76db33c8:

    # a sad_side "And you know I would've been there for you, Sayori. We could've still worked together. Studied together." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Y sabes que yo habría estado ahí para ti, Sayori. Pudimos seguir trabajando juntas. Estudiado juntas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4365
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5979bd62:

    # a sad_closed "You just didn't want to." with dissolve
    a sad_closed "Pero tú simplemente no lo quisiste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4366
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c2dd82a8:

    # s concerned "{cps=15}Akiko, you don't understand-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    s concerned "{cps=15}Akiko, no lo entiendes-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4367
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_684f92b1:

    # a angry_side "The second you left us I may as well have not existed to you! What's so hard to understand about that!" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¡Desde el segundo que nos dejaste es como si hubiera dejado de existir para ti! ¡¿Qué otra cosa hay que entender?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4369
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bd79ce7c:

    # a "You gave up on me, Sayori; Just like everybody else. You saw what a hopeless screw up I am and you took your haughty self as far away from me as you could." with dissolve
    a "Renunciaste a mí, Sayori. Igual que todos los demás. Viste el chasco sin remedio que era y en tu soberbia te alejaste de mí tanto como pudiste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4370
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_5d3dd3f8:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "Akiko... no..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Akiko... no..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4371
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3a0e1d06:

    # a sad_side "I can't even blame you for it. Why would you want to be around me when you have your books and your precious, perfect Nozomi." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Ni siquiera te puedo culpar. ¿Por qué querrías estar cerca de mí cuando tienes tus libros y a tu preciosa y perfecta Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4373
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_58304076:

    # a cry "I can't blame you at all. But damn you for saying you ever respected me." with dissolve
    a cry "De verdad no puedo culparte. Pero maldita seas por decir que alguna vez me respetaste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4375
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f416c4cc:

    # "And then, with shuffled steps, she backs away from those girls and reaches to grip my hand in hers as she looks teary-eyed to me." with dissolve
    "Y luego, a pasos arrastrados, se aleja de esas chicas y me toma de la mano, mirándome con lágrimas en los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4376
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_afa19a30:

    # a cry_smile "Kyou is the only one who saw what I could be. This \"cretin\" is the only one who... who wants me. Who believes in me." with dissolve
    a cry_smile "Kyou es el único que vio lo que podía ser. Este \"cretino\" es el único que... que me quiere. Que cree en mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4377
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_de7cd6a8:

    # "She smiles at me through her tears, and I smile back as I hold her hand tightly to my side. Just as she then flashes another hateful glance at her former friend."
    "Me sonríe entre sus lágrimas, y yo le sonrío, apretando su mano a mi lado. Justo mientras ella le lanza otra mirada de odio a su antigua amiga."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4378
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_887483d8:

    # a frown_side "And you can't even let me have that?" with dissolve
    a frown_side "¿Y ni siquiera puedes dejarme tener eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4380
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ebe106da:

    # a angry_side "Just DAMN you to hell, Sayori!" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¡Entonces puedes irte al INFIERNO, Sayori!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4381
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f91c5315:

    # "Now it seems it's Sayori's turn to wither, as any comeback she might have had seems to die on her lips."
    "Ahora parece que es el turno de Sayori de marchitarse, pues cualquier respuesta que pudiera tener parece perecer en sus labios."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4382
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b7b1de32:

    # "Yeah, now's the time to leave. With my perfect, beautiful Nozomi."
    "Sí, y ahora es el momento idóneo para irnos. Con mi perfecta y hermosa Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4384
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3713c0c3:

    # ks neutral "I think you girls have said your piece. And the tennis club doesn't need you for anything else, right?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "Creo que las dos ya dijeron su parte. Y el club de tenis ya no te necesita para nada más, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4385
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_66aa5560:

    # a smile "Yes, that's right. I could stay to help with the games, but..." with dissolve
    a smile "Sí, es correcto. Podría quedarme a ayudar en los juegos, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4386
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_9ad06898:

    # ks smile "We're leaving now."
    ks smile "Ya nos vamos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4387
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_927b4cca:

    # a shy blush "Yes, please. Take me away from here." with dissolve
    a shy blush "Sí, por favor. Sácame de aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4389
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3d05c5cb:

    # n shocked_side "Akiko, NO! Get away from him!" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡Akiko, NO! ¡Aléjate de él!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4390
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_329a55a0:

    # a surprised_side "N-Nozomi? Whatever for?" with dissolve
    a surprised_side "¿N-Nozomi? ¿Por qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4391
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a167519b:

    # n sad_side "You... Akiko, you said you respect me, right?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Tú... Akiko, dijiste que me respetabas, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4392
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_87fddf94:

    # a sad_side2 "More than anyone in the world. I've tried to tell you!" with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "Más que a nadie en este mundo. ¡Es lo que he intentado decirte!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4393
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e4b5e877:

    # n frown_side "Well, HE doesn't! I don't know what he told you, but you cannot trust him! Please!" with dissolve
    n frown_side "¡Bueno, ÉL no me respeta! ¡No sé qué fue lo que te dijo, pero no puedes confiar en él! ¡Por favor!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4395
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0382b07b:

    # "I look to Nozomi. My Nozomi, as she looks back to me and I see... a wavering expression in her eyes." with dissolve
    "Miro a Nozomi. Mi Nozomi. Y ella me mira y veo... una expresión de indecisión en sus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4396
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e8918cfe:

    # a sad2 "B-but..." with dissolve
    a sad2 "P-pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4398
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_48fcb8ff:

    # "Is she really taking those words seriously?"
    "¿De verdad se está tomando esas palabras en serio?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4399
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cc816727:

    # "Of course she is. Of COURSE she is!"
    "Pero por supuesto que sí. ¡Por SUPUESTO que sí!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4398
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0a9310d6:

    # s surprised "Uh... s-she's right! {w=0.5}{cps=15}His presence and your sudden loss of confidence cannot be a coincidence-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    s surprised "Eh... ¡t-tiene razón! {w=0.5}{cps=15}Su presencia y tu súbita pérdida de confianza no pueden ser una coincidencia-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4399
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ced15eb4:

    # a angry_side "Agh! YOU stay out of this!" with dissolve
    a angry_side "¡Ay! ¡TÚ no te metas en esto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4400
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_00bd05d6:

    # "Nozomi's the only one who can tear us apart! And I grip my girl's hand tightly at the realization."
    "¡Nozomi es la única que puede separarnos! Y yo tomo con fuerza la mano de mi novia al darme cuenta de eso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4402
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_91886ea4:

    # "No more indecision. I need to stop being a bystander and get her out of here. Quickly." with dissolve
    "No más vacilaciones. Tengo que dejar de ser un mero observador y sacarla de aquí. De inmediato." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4403
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cf1683a1:

    # ks frown "Let's go, Nozomi. We don't need to be here any more."
    ks frown "Vámonos, Nozomi. Ya no tenemos que seguir aquí."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4407
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_62dfa596:

    # "I need to... oh." with dissolve
    "Necesito... oh." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4408
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b5d28d95:

    # ks "... Akiko. Akiko, we need to leave!"
    ks "... Akiko. ¡Akiko, tenemos que irnos!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4412
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_de0b0e40:

    # n "That wasn't my ears playing tricks on me, was it?" with dissolve
    n "Mis oídos no me engañaron, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4413
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_f99012c0:

    # s surprised_right "No, Nozomi. No it was not." with dissolve
    s surprised_right "No, Nozomi. Escuchaste bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4414
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_18531253:

    # "This is bad. But what's the worst that could happen, really?"
    "Esto es malo. Pero ¿qué es lo peor que podría pasar?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4415
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cb942a83:

    # ks "Listen, Nozomi. I promised to leave you alone, and I have. But that cuts both ways, doesn't it?"
    ks "Escucha, Nozomi. Prometí que te dejaría en paz, y eso hice. Pero eso va en ambas direcciones, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4416
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_69f653da:

    # ks "So I don't know what you girls think you heard just now, but me and Akiko are leaving now. Don't try and stop us."
    ks "Así que no sé qué es lo que creen que acaban de oír, pero Akiko y yo nos vamos ahora. No intenten detenernos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4418
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_0c754159:

    # n angry "Don't you dare run away with her, you... you SCUM!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡No te atrevas a irte corriendo con ella, pedazo de... de ESCORIA!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4419
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c30a2271:

    # "Nozomi yells, and I think it's stirring the growing crowds into action around us."
    "Nozomi grita, y creo que eso llama la atención de la multitud a nuestro alrededor."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4420
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_c311bb6f:

    # "This is more attention than any of us needs, and I can feel myself tense up for a moment."
    "Esto es más atención de la que necesitamos, y puedo sentir mi cuerpo ponerse tenso por un momento."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4421
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_98eddeda:

    # "But no, I can't stop. And I yank on my girlfriend's hand as I desperately try to pull her away from all those worried-looking faces coming near us."
    "Pero no, no me puedo detener. Y tiro de la mano de mi novia, intentando desesperadamente alejarla de todos esos rostros preocupados que se acercan."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4422
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_09aaea63:

    # a pain -blush "A-ahh! Kyou, you're... hurting me!" with vpunch
    a pain -blush "¡A-aah! ¡Kyou, me estás... lastimando!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4423
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e48d351d:

    # "And especially away from Nozomi. If we stay, there's no telling how my girlfriend will react to her incessant preaching."
    "Y sobre todo lejos de Nozomi. Si nos quedamos, quién sabe cómo reaccionará mi novia a sus incesantes sermones."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4425
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_809f5293:

    # n "Akiko, please! I know he got in your head; he did the same to me, that's why I know!" with dissolve
    n "¡Akiko, por favor! Sé que se metió en tu cabeza; ¡me hizo lo mismo a mí, por eso lo sé!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4427
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b70ebee1:

    # n shocked_side "I know none of this is your fault! But the longer you stay with him, the more he'll hurt you. It's all he'll ever do." with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡Sé que nada de esto es tu culpa! Pero entre más te quedes con él, más te lastimará. Es lo único que hará." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4428
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_328bc595:

    # a sad_side2 "He... he's safe to be around. He is." with dissolve
    a sad_side2 "Es... completamente seguro estar con él. En serio." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4430
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_1c5b846a:

    # ks angry "Akiko, COME ON! Why are you stopping?" with dissolve
    ks angry "¡Akiko, VAMOS! ¿Por qué te detienes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4431
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a70ac2b7:

    # n sad_side "Let me help you, Akiko. I know things seem bleak right now, but I promise you that it'll get better. I'll listen to everything you have to say." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Permíteme ayudarte, Akiko. Sé que todo parece sombrío ahora, pero te prometo que mejorará. Escucharé todo lo que tengas que decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4432
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b3f2f5b2:

    # "Shit. This isn't working. Everyone's... this is too intense."
    "Mierda. Esto no está funcionando. Todos están... esto es demasiado intenso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4433
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_4ad4bfb9:

    # ks "Akiko, PLEASE!"
    ks "¡Akiko, POR FAVOR!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4434
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_831e73d2:

    # n frown_side "And let me tell you something else: I'm not as perfect as he told you. Not by a long shot." with dissolve
    n frown_side "Y déjame decirte algo más: No soy tan perfecta como él te dijo. Ni de cerca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4435
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_123f5db0:

    # "It's no good. With the crowd forming around us, dragging her out of here won't get me very far, not unless I can get her to move with me."
    "No consigo nada. Con esta multitud formándose a nuestro alrededor, arrastrarla fuera de aquí no me llevará muy lejos, no a menos que consiga que se mueva conmigo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4436
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b7f48aa7:

    # "But she's not even looking at me. Not anymore."
    "Pero ni siquiera me está mirando. Ya no."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4437
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_30a45602:

    # a confused_side "What? {w=1.0}N-no, don't say that-{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    a confused_side "¿Qué? {w=1.0}N-no, no digas eso-{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4438
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_47953915:

    # n frown_side "Why would anyone want to be Nozomi? She's a lazy screw-up who still needs her mom to clean up after her, and cook her meals and get her out of bed in the mornings." with dissolve
    n frown_side "¿Por qué alguien querría ser Nozomi? Sigue siendo una torpe perezosa que necesita que su mamá limpie por ella, y cocine sus comidas, y la levante por las mañanas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4439
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3490b3a2:

    # n irritated "She's such a screw-up she doesn't even know what to do when she leaves high school!" with dissolve
    n irritated "¡Es un desastre tan grande que ni siquiera sabe qué hacer cuando salga de preparatoria!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4440
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a7f575d0:

    # s casual_handup concerned "Huh..." with dissolve
    s casual_handup concerned "Vaya..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4443
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_993ed5cf:

    # n neutral_side "And Nozomi isn't kind. Sure she puts a smile on her face, but she barely opens up to anyone; that's why she has so few friends. Never had a boyfriend..." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Y Nozomi no es gentil. Solo pone una sonrisa en su rostro, pero apenas se abre con la gente; por eso tiene tan pocos amigos. Nunca tuvo un novio..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4442
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6c8e42a0:

    # n sad_side "She's just a scared little girl frightened of the world and her place in it. At least Akiko gets an apartment; Nozomi probably won't even get out of her parent's house." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Es solo una temerosa niñita asustada del mundo y de su lugar en él. Al menos Akiko tendrá un apartamento; Nozomi probablemente ni siquiera salga de casa de sus padres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4443
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ba685982:

    # n sad_closed "Oh, and you know this already, but even though Nozomi loves to sing, she can't carry a tune to save her life. You need to hear her someday; it's embarrassing." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Oh, y esto ya lo sabes, pero a pesar de que a Nozomi le encanta cantar, no puede afinar ni aunque su vida dependiera de ello. Tendrías que oírla; da pena." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4444
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_46d4e3d6:

    # n sad_side "No one should want to be Nozomi. Even I don't want to be Nozomi sometimes." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Nadie debería querer ser Nozomi. Incluso yo no quiero ser Nozomi a veces." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4445
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_946a1718:

    # n smile_side "But I couldn't be anyone else. I can only be the best... the best version of Nozomi that I can be." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pero no puedo ser nadie más. Solo puedo ser la mejor... la mejor versión de Nozomi que puedo ser." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4447
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d52db3e0:

    # a "But you're still... s-still Nozomi..." with dissolve
    a "Pero sigues... s-sigues siendo Nozomi..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4448
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_d5535d73:

    # n sad_side "And you're still Akiko. And there's nothing wrong with that." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Y tú sigues siendo Akiko. Y eso no tiene nada de malo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4450
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_e7e2cc5e:

    # "Finally, my girlfriend looks back to me, but I only see the uncertainty in her eyes. I can only feel the tug on my hand as she starts to recoil from me." with dissolve
    "Finalmente, mi novia voltea a verme, pero solo puedo ver la incertidumbre en sus ojos. Solo puedo sentir el tirón en mi mano al intentar apartarse de mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4451
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3c6bf823:

    # n "You don't need to change who you are to be happy. You only need to be the best version of Akiko that you can be. Okay?"
    n "No necesitas cambiar quién eres para ser feliz. Solo necesitas ser la mejor versión de Akiko que puedas ser. ¿Está bien?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4452
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bdb5002d:

    # "I'm losing her... or I've already lost her. And staying here any longer amongst this ever-growing crowd is only making it worse for me."
    "La estoy perdiendo... O ya la perdí. Y quedarme más tiempo entre esta creciente multitud solo empeora las cosas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4453
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_3b694dce:

    # "S-so I need to..."
    "N-necesito..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4459
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2542e6cd:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's where I'm at for now! Please looks forward to the next update, where I intend to write at least one conclusion to this storyline! ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: ¡Y hasta aquí me quedé por ahora! Por favor, esperen con ansias la próxima actualización, ¡en la que pienso escribir al menos una conclusión para esta historia! ))"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4460
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a7f62a4b:

    # "{size=40}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}"
    "{size=40}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 7.rpy:4454
    old "I need to get out of here"
    new "Necesito salir de aquí"

    # game/Kyou 7.rpy:4454
    old "I need to stay by her side"
    new "Necesito quedarme a su lado"
# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-05-21 19:06

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4303
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_31a1600a:

    # "I should get her out of here, away from these judgmental assholes before they make her regress even further."
    "Tengo que sacarla de aquí, lejos de estas críticas de mierda antes de que deshagan mi progreso con ella."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4369
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cb219b1a:

    # a "You gave up on me, Sayori; just like everybody else. You saw what an insufferable fool I am and you took your haughty self as far away from me as you could." with dissolve
    a "Renunciaste a mí, Sayori. Igual que todos los demás. Viste la tonta insufrible que era y en tu soberbia te alejaste de mí tanto como pudiste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4390
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_7b819c5a:

    # "We've barely moved a couple steps before my girlfriend suddenly digs her heels into the ground, bringing us back to a halt as she faces her tormentors once again."
    "Apenas doy un par de pasos cuando mi novia de repente presiona sus talones contra el suelo, deteniéndonos para volver a encarar a sus atormentadoras."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4461
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_852f6554:

    # "I pull my hand back, and it easily comes loose from Akiko's flimsy grip."
    "Retraigo mi mano, y esta escapa fácilmente del endeble agarre de Akiko."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4462
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6ea7ebed:

    # a "The best version of... me?"
    a "¿La mejor versión de... mí?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4464
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_23a3e1be:

    # "And I run, pushing my way past the assorted throng of concerned parents and fellow students as I make my escape."
    "Y entonces corro, y huyo atravesando la diversa multitud de padres y estudiantes preocupados."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4465
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_1097da49:

    # "As I stumble on through I find myself instinctively looking back at the girl I'm leaving behind."
    "Avanzando entre tropiezos, instintivamente volteo a ver a la chica a la que estoy dejando atrás."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4466
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2e23dd7a:

    # "Our eyes meet for one last, fleeting moment. Just long enough to catch the expression written on her face before it's lost in the crowd."
    "Nuestras miradas se cruzan por un último y efímero momento. Justo lo suficiente para ver la mirada dibujada en su rostro antes de que desaparezca entre la gente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4469
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_ccd3a898:

    # "That look of pain in her eyes was unmistakable."
    "Esa mirada de dolor en sus ojos era inconfundible."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4473
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_eb831c17:

    # "I'm so sorry, Ak... Nozomi. But there was nothing I could do, not with all those people. Not while you're hanging on my old crush's every word."
    "Lo siento, Ak... Nozomi. Pero no había nada que pudiera hacer, no con toda esa gente. No cuando es mi palabra contra la de mi antiguo amor."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4474
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_29939c18:

    # "But... I can still save us. I know as much as you're hurting right now, you still trust me. You'll still want to talk to me. After all..."
    "Pero... aún puedo salvarnos. Sé que por mucho dolor que estés sintiendo ahora, aún confías en mí. Aún quieres hablar conmigo. Después de todo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4477
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_33455dfa:

    # "I told you that you enjoy talking to me. I told you I'm safe to be around. And there's nothing anyone can say to convince you otherwise."
    "Te dije que disfrutabas hablar conmigo. Te dije que era seguro estar conmigo. Y no hay nada que nadie pueda decir para convencerte de lo contrario."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4478
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_61cc36b8:

    # "My hypnosis saw to that just as plainly as it's gotten you hanging on Nozomi's every word right now."
    "Mi hipnosis se asegura de ello tanto como se está asegurando ahora de que escuches cada palabra de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4480
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_595fc920:

    # "But she can't be with you forever. She can't always be there, poisoning your mind against me."
    "Pero no puede estar contigo toda la vida. No puede estar siempre ahí, envenenando tu mente para ponerte en mi contra."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4483
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a86011c8:

    # "All we need is a chance to be alone..."
    "Lo único que necesitamos es una oportunidad de estar solos..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4484
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_2c776693:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Hey, call me as soon as you get a moment to yourself. We need to talk.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Oye, llámame tan pronto tengas un momento a solas. Debemos hablar.\"{/color}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4486
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b09e0a2b:

    # "And... sent. Now all I have to do is wait..."
    "Y... enviado. Ahora no me queda más que esperar..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4490
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_91360fea:

    # "Hours pass, and I'm pacing around my room as I stare at my phone screen."
    "Pasan las horas, y doy vueltas en mi habitación mirando la pantalla de mi teléfono."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4491
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_74c5e779:

    # "Still nothing? Is that bitch still not leaving her side? Why else wouldn't she be responding?"
    "¿Aún nada? ¿Qué esa perra no se ha despegado de su lado? ¿Por qué otra razón no respondería?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4530
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_164db35b:

    # "How long does one of those tennis tournaments last anyway? They must be close to wrapping up by now."
    "¿Cuánto tiempo se supone que dura uno de esos torneos de tenis? Ya tendría que estar por acabar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4493
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_b1fae3cd:

    # "They all have to go home sometime..."
    "Tendrán que irse a cada eventualmente..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4497
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_14768231:

    # "She's not answering her texts, she's not answering my calls... What the fuck?"
    "No responde sus textos, no responde mis llamadas... ¿Qué carajos?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4498
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_cf93c2f2:

    # "Dammit. Why didn't I think to ask her where she lives? I could've made a house call instead of being stuck here rooted to my phone like a dumbass."
    "Maldita sea. ¿Cómo no se me ocurrió preguntarle dónde vive? Así podría ir a su casa en lugar de estar aquí pegado a mi teléfono como un pendejo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4499
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_6dbfb61c:

    # "I just... everything about today has been a mistake. But I haven't lost Nozomi. Not yet."
    "Todo... todo ha sido nada más que errores hoy. Pero no he perdido a Nozomi. Aún no."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4500
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_a82ea9d8:

    # "Yeah. There's always tomorrow. Tomorrow will be different..."
    "Sí. Siempre hay un mañana. Mañana será diferente..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4501
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_be964433:

    # "Tomorrow we're back in class, and we'll have the chance to be alone again. And then... we'll fix all of this."
    "Mañana regresaremos a clase, y tendremos otra oportunidad de estar solos. Y luego... puedo arreglar todo esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4502
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_821326ea:

    # "You'll let me hypnotize you again and we'll correct my mistakes together, won't we?"
    "Me dejarás volverte a hipnotizar y corregiremos mis errores juntos, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4505
translate spanish Day7_Villain2_Kyou_bcd69a54:

    # "After tomorrow, you won't idolize that bitch quite so much..."
    "Después de mañana, ya no idolatrarás tanto a esa perra..."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 7.rpy:4456
    old " (disabled)I need to stay by her side"
    new "Necesito quedarme a su lado"

