# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3633
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_634d856b:

    # "A hush descends upon the assembled crowd."
    "El silencio cae sobre la multitud."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3634
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_73002cf5:

    # "It's been a long day of competitive tennis, but as I suck in a breath I watch what must be the match of the tournament."
    "Ha sido un largo día de tenis competitivo, pero sentado en una banca observo lo que debe ser el partido del torneo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3638
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_50c16de3:

    # "Hiroko Homura, our school's tennis star, has put up a good fight in this semi-final, forcing a tie break like this." with dissolve
    "Hiroko Homura, la estrella del tenis de nuestra escuela, ha dado una gran batalla hasta esta semifinal, forzando un desempate así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3639
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2a200bc3:

    # "But I have to say, she looks pretty spent."
    "Pero debo decir que luce muy agotada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3641
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2b1c2b9f:

    # "It's been a scrappy game, and Hiroko lost her cool more than once during the match."
    "Ha sido un juego con errores, y Hiroko perdió la compostura un par de veces durante el partido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3642
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_fc9483ee:

    # "And as her opponent tosses the ball in the air to serve for match point, I can't help but think..."
    "Y mientras su oponente lanza la pelota en el aire para servir el punto de juego, no puedo evitar pensar que..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3645
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e04526d7:

    # h "Haah! {nw}" with vpunch
    h "¡Aah! {nw}" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3648
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2f35c5db:

    # extend "{w=2.0}{nw}"
    extend "{w=2.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3651
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0c25d06d:

    # extend "Ahhh, nuts."
    extend "Aaah, rayos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3654
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_cbae15c6:

    # t "Game, set and match: Miss Tanikawa."
    t "Juego, set y partido: Señorita Tanikawa."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3655
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_bbb9af5b:

    # "... It seems she rejected my hypnotic suggestions after all."
    "... Parece que rechazó mis sugestiones hipnóticas después de todo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3667
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e7d3f4e2:

    # r "Man, that was a nail-biter, wasn't it? You almost had her, Hiro."
    r "Cielos, estuvo para comerse las uñas, ¿no? Casi le ganas, Hiro."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3669
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a2c594eb:

    # "While that girl from the other school takes the plaudits, I followed Hiroko to watch from a discreet distance as she's consoled by her friends."
    "Mientras esa chica de la otra escuela se lleva los aplausos, sigo a Hiroko para mirar desde una distancia discreta mientras la consuelan sus amigas."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3670
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a2eb70ef:

    # h pain "Those fuckin' passing shots! I didn't have the reach to get to 'em and she knew it." with dissolve
    h pain "¡Esos passing shots de mierda! ¡No tenía el alcance para atraparlos y ella lo sabía!" with dissolve

    # game/Kyou 7.rpy:3628
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7c8aa22d:

    # s casual_handup sleeptalk "Tanikawa did seem to get the measure of you as the match progressed. Your numerous unforced errors didn't help either." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleeptalk "Tanikawa ciertamente parece haber medido tus capacidades adecuadamente conforme progresaba el partido. Los numerosos errores no forzados tampoco fueron de ayuda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3674
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0c9b5906:

    # s concerned "Still, if you had converted that break point in the second game you probably would have beaten her." with dissolve
    s concerned "No obstante, si hubieses cubierto ese punto de quiebre en el segundo juego, es probable que la hubieses vencido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3677
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7d65bfc6:

    # n smile_side "Yeah, but what's more important is that you showed everyone watching how much this sport means to you, Hiroko." with dissolve
