# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3905
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2e889336:

    # "I shot Nozomi a puzzled look, but it didn't take long for me to realize what she was up to."
    "Le doy a Nozomi una confusa mirada, pero no me toma mucho darme cuenta de lo que tiene en mente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3906
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_f16741d8:

    # "So I found what she wanted, while I heard Nozomi telling Hiroko to make herself comfortable on my couch..."
    "Por lo que fui a buscar lo que quería, mientras escuchaba a Nozomi decirle a Hiroko que se pusiera cómoda en mi sofá..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3910
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e9150544:

    # ns casual smile "So? How are we feeling?"
    ns casual smile "¿Y bien? ¿Cómo te sientes?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3912
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_c982889a:

    # "I watch as Hiroko shifts a little on the couch and lets out an indifferent grunt."
    "Observo cómo Hiroko ajusta un poco su posición en el sofá y suelta un gruñido indiferente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3914
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8a1d5d18:

    # h "Erh, I can't decide if it's more or less weird that my bestie's gonna hypnotize me this time." with dissolve
    h "Em, no me decido si es más o menos raro que sea mi mejor amiga quien me va hipnotizar esta vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3915
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0756df35:

    # ns chuckle "Ehehe, try not to think about that. Just relax and leave everything else to me, okay?"
    ns chuckle "Ejeje, trata de no pensar en eso. Solo relájate y déjame el resto a mí, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3917
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_1282b72a:

    # h "... Sure." with dissolve
    h "... Claro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3918
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_67e97ced:

    # ns smile "And you really are fine with this? With what we talked about?"
    ns smile "¿Y de verdad estás de acuerdo con esto? ¿Con lo que discutimos?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3920
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_6df661f7:

    # h "Uhh... I said I was, right? 'Sides, after all the crazy shit Kyou was doing on me, this sounds like hypno kindergarten." with dissolve
    h "Eeh... Ya dije que sí, ¿verdad? Además, luego de tanta puta locura que Kyou me estuvo haciendo, esto suena a hipno jardín de niños." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3921
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_eba9edc0:

    # ks casual sigh "And how crazy do you think this all looks to me? Watching the pair of you have your own hypnosis session in my house?"
    ks casual sigh "¿Y qué tan loco crees que esto luce para mí? ¿Verlas a las dos tener su propia sesión de hipnosis en mi casa?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3923
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2d4a36d0:

    # "Hiroko just scoffs at me as she looks my way." with dissolve
    "Hiroko voltea a verme, mofándose." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3924
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4f75ae3a:

    # h "H'yeah, well for one thing this ain't YOUR house; it's your old man's. And you don't have to watch us if it bothers you so much."
    h "Seh, pues primero que nada, esta no es TU casa; es de tu viejo. Y segundo que nada, no nos tienes que mirar si tanto de molesta."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3926
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ef79cb3c:

    # "And Nozomi shoots me a frown as she settles down beside the couch." with dissolve
    "Y Nozomi me frunce el ceño mientras se acomoda a un lado del sofá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3927
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_42ca1867:

    # n "You should at least move out of her peripheral vision, Kyou. You'll only distract her."
    n "Deberías al menos salir de su visión periférica, Kyou. Solo la distraerás."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3928
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_f6742b8d:

    # ks frown "Oh... Right."
    ks frown "Oh... Cierto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3929
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_77397295:

    # "Fair point, I guess. Although I can't resist making an observation about Nozomi's first time hypnotizing someone..."
    "Buen punto, supongo. Aunque, no puedo resistir hacerle una observación a la primera vez que Nozomi hipnotizará a alguien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3930
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_21cf14b8:

    # ks confused "Shouldn't *you* be in front of her, though? How are you going to gauge her reaction to what you're doing if you can't see her face properly?"
    ks confused "Pero ¿no deberías *tú* estar frente a ella? ¿Cómo vas a juzgar su reacción a lo que estás haciendo si no puedes ver bien su rostro?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3931
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_110a00ca:

    # n "Oh... shush. Just move out of her way, will you?"
    n "Oh... chitón. Solo hazte a un lado, ¿quieres?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3932
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_32df46f6:

    # "With a shrug, I do as she says and step aside."
    "Encogiéndome de hombros, hago lo que dice y me alejo de en frente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3934
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_bee88107:

    # "And as soon as I do, Nozomi reaches above her friend before letting a coin drop in front of her face where it dangles from a piece of borrowed string." with dissolve
    "Y en cuanto lo hago, Nozomi alza su mano sobre su amiga para después dejar caer una moneda delante de su rostro, donde cuelga de un hilo que tomó prestado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3936
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_956ce466:

    # h "I mean, he's got a point tho. How're you supposed to know if I'm looking or not? Scoot around, willya?" with dissolve
    h "Oye, pero sí es cierto. ¿Cómo vas a saber si estoy mirando o no? A ver, mejor ponte acá en frente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3937
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_814a290d:

    # n "It's okay, Hiroko. I'm sure you can do this."
    n "No te preocupes, Hiroko. Estoy segura de que puedes hacer esto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3938
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4b285b12:

    # n "Kyou may have tricked you into taking things too far, but I doubt he could've done so unless you had a genuine aptitude as a hypnotee."
    n "Puede que Kyou te haya engañado para llevarte demasiado lejos, pero dudo que hubiera podido hacerlo si no tuvieras una genuina aptitud para ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3940
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_c46d5bd0:

    # n "I think you have an amazingly-focused mind to go as deep into trance as you apparently have. I'm a little envious of you, to be honest." with dissolve
    n "Creo que tu mente tiene una asombrosa capacidad para enfocarse que te permitió entrar en esos trances tan profundos. Siento algo de envidia, siendo honesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3941
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_587325e9:

    # h "Envious?"
    h "¿Envidia?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3943
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_272b17cf:

    # n "But moreso, I think you really want to do this with me. You trust me to give you a hypnotic experience you won't regret." with dissolve
    n "Pero lo más importante, creo que de verdad quieres hacer esto conmigo. Confías en que te dé una experiencia hipnótica de la que no te arrepentirás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3945
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_31570041:

    # n "And I trust you too, Hiroko. So let's have some fun with this, okay?" with dissolve
    n "Y yo confío también en ti, Hiroko. Así que hay que divertirnos un poco, ¿está bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3947
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a4d01cf9:

    # "I simply watch and wait as the girls talk. And although Hiroko falls silent for a moment, I'm pretty sure she is looking straight at that coin hanging before her eyes now." with dissolve
    "Yo simplemente observo y espero mientras las chicas hablan. Y si bien Hiroko se queda en silencio por un momento, sé que debe estar mirando directo a la moneda suspendida ante sus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3948
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2eef5213:

    # h "... Okay."
    h "... Está bien."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3949
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4de9ec52:

    # "Still think this arrangement's stupid. But I'll say no more as Nozomi gets down to business."
    "Yo aún creo que este acomodo es estúpido. Pero no diré nada más, dejando que Nozomi se ponga manos a la obra."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3951
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_3da1ba30:

    # n "Now, just take a deep, calming breath. In and out, as you focus all your attention on this coin now." with dissolve
    n "Ahora, respira hondo y con calma. Inhala y exhala, mientras concentras toda tu atención en esta moneda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3952
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_493642be:

    # n "I'd like you to take it all in. Let every detail of this coin occupy your mind, and allow everything else to fall away."
    n "Quiero que la mires muy bien. Que observar cada detallito de la moneda tenga tu mente ocupada, y deja que todo lo demás de desvanezca."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3953
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2af508ad:

    # n "Just relax... and stare... and watch the coin on its journey. Travelling right... and left..."
    n "Tan solo relájate... y obsérvala... sigue la moneda en su viaje. Moviéndose a la derecha... y a la izquierda..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3955
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ff2a114c:

    # n "{cps=15}Right... {w=0.7}left... {w=0.7}right...{w=0.7}left...{/cps}"
    n "{cps=15}Derecha... {w=0.7}izquierda... {w=0.7}derecha...{w=0.7}izquierda...{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3956
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_19727cfc:

    # "With an elegant flick of her wrist, Nozomi starts to swing the coin in a slow and steady rhythm as Hiroko sits unmoving on the couch."
    "Con un elegante movimiento de su muñeca, Nozomi comienza a balancear el péndulo con un ritmo lento y constante, mientras Hiroko yace inmóvil en el sofá."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3957
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e3fc53f1:

    # "Makes me wonder if she's ever practiced this before despite her lack of practical experience..."
    "Me hace preguntarme si ha practicado esto antes a pesar de su falta de experiencia práctica..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3959
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_f4f3d1c3:

    # n "Right... left... Just relax and allow the coin to guide your eyes." with dissolve
    n "Derecha... izquierda... Tan solo relájate y permite que la moneda guie tus ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3960
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_00c8aeab:

    # n "You may be starting to realize how automatic it's becoming to watch the coin, as though you don't even need to consciously think about it."
    n "Puede que comiences a darte cuenta de lo automático que se está volviendo mirar la moneda, como si ni siquiera tuvieras que pensar conscientemente en ello."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3961
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_9afaf624:

    # n "And that's perfectly fine, Hiroko. You can just let it happen; let your conscious thoughts drift further and further away."
    n "Y eso está perfectamente bien, Hiroko. Solo deja que ocurra; deja que tus pensamientos conscientes se vuelvan más y más distantes."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3963
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0cc209a9:

    # "We hear a muted murmur coming out of Hiroko's mouth while the coin continues its gentle sway before her eyes."
    "Oímos un enmudecido murmullo salir de los labios de Hiroko mientas la moneda continúa su gentil vaivén ante sus ojos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3964
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_9d8ea578:

    # "Is she really doing it? I want to lean in and look at her face so bad right now."
    "¿De verdad lo está haciendo? Cómo me muero de ganas de asomarme a ver su rostro ahora mismo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3966
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_caed7d8a:

    # n "Just breathe, and allow your every conscious thought to drop away. Allow yourself to become more and more relaxed." with dissolve
    n "Tan solo respira, y permite que todo pensamiento consciente se vaya. Permítete relajarte más y más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3967
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a0d4c546:

    # n "Left. Right. Left. Right..."
    n "Izquierda. Derecha. Izquierda. Derecha..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3968
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_cda6c15e:

    # "So... maybe Nozomi really does know what she's doing."
    "Entonces... tal vez Nozomi sí sabe lo que está haciendo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3969
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_6c5a9a73:

    # n "So now you may be feeling like watching this fascinating, absorbing coin is tiring you out. Straining your eyes. Giving you a sleepy feeling."
    n "Y ahora puede que sientas que mirar esta fascinante y cautivadora moneda empieza a agotarte. A cansarte los ojos. Dándote una sensación de sueño."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3971
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_c6ea7094:

    # n "That's okay, Hiroko. Just watch the coin for as long as it's comfortable."
    n "No te preocupes, Hiroko. Tan solo observa la moneda el tiempo que te sientas cómoda."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3972
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ca5a4972:

    # "Maybe... I should've told her I was getting into this stuff too. Back when we were together in the classroom..."
    "Tal vez... sí debí haberle contado que yo también estaba indagando en esto. Cuando estábamos juntos en el salón..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3973
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_917fa76c:

    # n "And when you're ready. When you can no longer keep up with the coin; when all all your conscious thought has dropped all the way to the back of your mind..."
    n "Y cuando estés lista. Cuando ya no puedas seguirle el ritmo a la moneda; cuando todos tus pensamientos conscientes hayan caído al fondo de tu mente."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3974
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_fd1833d9:

    # n "... You can close your eyes and drop deeper into this pleasant state of hypnosis you're experiencing."
    n "... Puedes cerrar los ojos y caer más profundo en este placentero estado de hipnosis que estás experimentando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3976
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0e52913a:

    # n "Only the sound of my voice will remain as you drop deeper and deeper."
    n "Solo el sonido de mi voz prevalecerá una vez caigas más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3977
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_b1d552f5:

    # "As she continues talking, I notice Nozomi making a gesture at me."
    "Mientras continúa hablando, noto que Nozomi me hace un gesto."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3978
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_96752a0a:

    # "Seems she wants me to go peek, and sure enough Hiroko seems like she's down and out before the coin as it swings for no-one."
    "Al parecer quiere que eche un vistazo, y en efecto parece que Hiroko está dormida frente a la moneda que ahora se balancea para nadie."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3980
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4651d81f:

    # "Nozomi seems relieved as she sets the coin down and leans in just a little closer to her friend, then starts speaking softly to her ear." with dissolve
    "Nozomi luce aliviada, bajando la moneda e inclinándose ligeramente hacia su amiga, luego empieza a hablarle suavemente al oído." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3982
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ebeb06bb:

    # n "Deeper and deeper... and the deeper the go, the more you may realize how good this feels." with dissolve
    n "Más y más profundo... y entre más profundo vayas, más te darás cuenta de lo bien que esto se siente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3983
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e932dc91:

    # n "When you can relax so deeply like this, when you can let your conscious thoughts drift away with someone you trust..."
    n "El poder relajarte así de profundo, el poder dejar que tus pensamientos conscientes se desvanezcan junto a alguien en quien confías..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3985
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e7eba5a1:

    # n "... It feels good, right?" with dissolve
    n "... Se siente bien, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3987
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4b2db598:

    # h "Yeah... Feels... good..." with dissolve
    h "Sí... Se siente... bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3989
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_afbdf3d3:

    # "Nozomi starts to smile. From pride because she managed to hypnotize her friend on her first try like I did? Or relief that Hiroko's not so turned off by hypnosis after all?" with dissolve
    "Nozomi comienza a sonreír. ¿De orgullo porque logró hipnotizar a su amiga al primer intento como yo? ¿O de alivio de que Hiroko no deteste la hipnosis al final?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3990
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4c7c6fb5:

    # n "Yes it does. So now that you're feeling this good and comfortable, I want to try that little thing we discussed earlier."
    n "Claro que sí. Y entonces, ahora que te sientes así de bien y cómoda, quiero intentar eso que discutimos hace rato."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3992
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_d95a5f7d:

    # n "After all, that coin was quite fascinating to look at, right?" with dissolve
    n "Después de todo, esa moneda era muy fascinante de ver, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3994
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_3236c9d1:

    # h "Mmn... right..." with dissolve
    h "Mmn... cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3996
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0d28cc93:

    # n "So it would be alright if, for a little while after you leave this state of hypnotized trance, it continued to be fascinating, wouldn't it?" with dissolve
    n "Así que estaría bien si, por un ratito después de que salgas de este estado de hipnosis, continuara siendo fascinante, ¿no lo crees?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3998
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_d0782d04:

    # h "Yeah... alright..." with dissolve
    h "Sí... estaría bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4000
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7f6f8d87:

    # n "Yeah. So in a moment I'm going to count up slowly to three and snap my fingers." with dissolve
    n "Sí. Entonces, en un momento, contaré lentamente hasta tres y chasquearé los dedos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4001
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8002f62d:

    # n "And as I do, I want you to feel more and more awake until on the snap of my fingers you'll awaken from this relaxing state of trance; still feeling as good as you do now."
    n "Y cuando lo haga, quiero que te sientas más y más despierta hasta que, con el chasquido de mis dedos, salgas de este relajante estado de trance; sintiéndote tan bien como ahora."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4003
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7d691ebe:

    # n "But as soon as you see my coin again, you will feel an overwhelming compulsion to stare at it again." with dissolve
    n "Pero en cuanto vuelvas a ver la moneda, sentirás un abrumador impulso de volver a mirarla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4004
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e7c5b323:

    # n "You will continue to find it so fascinating. So hypnotizing... and it will be so very easy to drop back into this nice, relaxing state of trance yet again. Okay?"
    n "Te seguirá siendo tan fascinante. Tan hipnótica... y será muy fácil caer de regreso a este lindo y relajante estado de trance. ¿Está bien?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4006
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_26f74f57:

    # h "Okay..." with dissolve
    h "Está bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4008
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_5fa2d716:

    # n "That's great, Hiroko. So I'm counting up now... one, feeling more aware, more awake." with dissolve
    n "Genial, Hiroko. Entonces, voy a contar ahora... uno, sintiéndote más consciente, más despierta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4010
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0eb1ac7c:

