    h tennis_headhold2 pain "Seeeeh, podría decirse..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3725
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0a772f56:

    # n neutral_side "Alright, I'm going to tell Risa to start the party without us. We'll think of something to tell her later." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Muy bien, voy a decirle a Risa que comience la fiesta sin nosotras. Pensaremos en una excusa después." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3731
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_49e18779:

    # ks "You got hypnotized once at a culture fest. Was that not the only time then? Because the way you're talking..." with dissolve
    ks "Fuiste hipnotizada una vez en el festival cultural. Entonces, ¿esa no fue la única vez? Porque con lo que estás diciendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3732
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7c9892ca:

    # ks "... Do you actually know about hypnosis, Nozomi?" with dissolve
    ks "... ¿De verdad sabes de hipnosis, Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3795
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2fd0e1e3:

    # h irritated "The second you rejigged my brain with all that hypno crap, the very SECOND, I couldn't control myself! It wasn't a fuckin' trick!" with dissolve
    h irritated "¡Desde que me reacomodaste el cerebro con tu hipno cagadero, desde ese mismo SEGUNDO, ya no podía controlarme! ¡Eso no fue un puto engaño!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3800
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2585c33c:

    # n side sad_side "Hiroko... I really don't think this was anything more than a misunderstanding." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Hiroko... de verdad no creo que haya sido más que un malentendido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3801
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e0deedea:

    # n sad_closed "You thought Kyou had control over your thoughts and actions; that you were compelled to obey him. And Kyou selfishly chose to exploit that." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Creíste que Kyou tenía control sobre tus pensamientos y acciones; que no tenías más opción que obedecerlo. Y Kyou, de forma egoísta, eligió explotar eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3935
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_be72c020:

    # "If I hadn't been such a coward back then, then maybe..."
    "Si no hubiera sido tan cobarde ese día, entonces tal vez..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3938
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_51ed15d4:

    # "Me and her, we could've..."
    "Ella y yo... podríamos haber..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3940
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_6639de2f:

    # "... Oh, she just made a gesture at me. I barely noticed while I was busy getting down on myself."
    "... Oh, me acaba de hacer un gesto. Apenas me di cuenta mientras me estaba lamentando."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3982
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e5449224:

    # "She looks for all the world like she'd just woken from a very comfortable dream, as she sits herself up on the couch while Nozomi goes to sit beside her."
    "Cualquiera que la viera pensaría que acaba de despertar de un muy cómodo sueño, al sentarse en el sofá mientras Nozomi toma asiento a su lado."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4031
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_b2b9dbbc:

    # ks sigh "{size=16}That's what I've been telling you!{/size}"
    ks sigh "{size=16}¡Es lo que te he estado diciendo!{/size}"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4032
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_90c0b5b1:

    # "As we exchange whispers, we both then look down to Hiroko, now slumped peacefully over her friend."
    "Mientras nos susurramos, ambos miramos a Hiroko, ahora desplomada pacíficamente sobre su amiga."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4035
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_50bbd14b:

    # n smile_side "That's right, Hiroko; easy does it. You don't need to do anything else." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Eso es, Hiroko; así de fácil es. No necesitas hacer nada más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4036
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_b28ec133:

    # n "This is all I wanted to show you. But maybe... another day..."
    n "Esto es todo lo que quería mostrarte. Pero tal vez... otro día..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4038
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_eda866ea:

    # "She spares me a glance as I stand awkwardly at this sedate scene developing on my living room couch, then continues." with dissolve
    "Me arroja una mirada mientras me quedo incómodamente de pie, mirando esta sosegada escena desarrollarse en el sofá de mi sala, luego continúa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4041
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_639b35e5:

    # n smile_side "Another day, if you're not completely turned off by all of this, I could show you more of what hypnosis can do for you. Without the dirty tricks." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Otro día, si no te sientes completamente repelida por todo esto, podría mostrarte más de lo que la hipnosis puede hacer por ti. Sin los trucos sucios." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4042
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_be2cc8ba:

    # n "But for now, let's make sure your head is clear and we can head back to the others. Okay, Hiroko?"
    n "Pero por ahora, asegurémonos de que tu cabeza esté despejada y podamos volver con las otras. ¿Está bien, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4044
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a5010905:

    # h sleeptalk "Mmmn... okay..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Mmmn... bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4046
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4d89abdf:

    # n "Alright. So I'm going to count up again. And this time, when I count to three you will awaken once more, feeling good and refreshed." with dissolve
    n "Muy bien. Entonces voy a contar otra vez. Y esta vez, cuando cuente hasta tres, despertarás nuevamente, sintiéndote bien y fresca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4047
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_36e68741:

    # n "And the moment I snap my fingers, your mind will be clear of any and all hypnotic suggestions made to you."
    n "Y cuando chasquee mis dedos, tu mente estará libre de toda sugestión hipnótica que se te haya hecho."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4048
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_487176cf:

    # n "So once more... one, beginning to stir. Two, feeling more awake, mind clearing and..."
    n "Así que, una vez más... uno, te puedes empezar a mover. Dos, sintiéndote más despierta, mente clara y..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4051
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_6c82b2e7:

    # n happy "Three! Wide awake, Hiroko!" with dissolve
    n happy "¡Tres! ¡Despierta, Hiroko!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4052
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ca244211:

