    extend "¡¿q-qué?!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4056
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_986a26d2:

    # "Hiroko awakes with a start, to a chuckling Nozomi smiling down at her."
    "Hiroko despierta con una expresión de sorpresa, viendo a una risueña Nozomi que le sonríe."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4058
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_7ce2d5e0:

    # h smile_side "O-oh man, was I s'posed to flop like this?" with dissolve
    h smile_side "A-ah, caray, ¿se suponía que me desplomara así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4060
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_1ab9980e:

    # n laugh "Ahahaha, you tell me~ I only asked you to pay attention to the coin." with dissolve
    n laugh "Ajajaja, tú dime. Yo solo te pedí que le prestaras atención a la moneda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4062
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_d0cb74b8:

    # "And with a sheepish smile, Hiroko rather unhurriedly rights herself on the couch." with dissolve
    "Y con una tímida sonrisa, Hiroko, sin mucha prisa, vuelve a erguirse en el sofá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4064
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_5bddf99a:

    # h smile_side "Well... h'yeah, okay Nozo. I guess I see where you're coming from with this hypno stuff. Kinda." with dissolve
    h smile_side "Pues... s-sí, de acuerdo, Nozo. Supongo que puedo entender lo que le ves a esto de la hipnosis. Más o menos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4066
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_c6406948:

    # h tennis confused_side "Like, it still seems crazy dangerous?" with dissolve
    h tennis confused_side "O sea, aun parece peligrosísimo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4068
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_4d446591:

    # h sleeptalk "But man, if it don't make you feel good..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Pero vaya que te hace sentir bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4070
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_25795eef:

    # n happy blush "Y-yes, it really does~" with dissolve
    n happy blush "S-sí, muy cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4072
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8f7acd92:

    # n neutral_side "But I want to assure you it doesn't have to be dangerous, Hiroko." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Pero quiero asegurarte que no tiene que ser peligroso, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4073
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_d18b7b5f:

    # n "You are all kinds of suggestible, and yes that can leave you open to manipulation if you're not careful."
    n "Eres de lo más sugestionable, y sí, eso te expone a la manipulación si no tienes cuidado."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4075
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a05433b3:

    # n smile_side "But so long as you and your hypnotist are honest and open throughout, you won't be led astray ever again." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pero siempre y cuando tú y tu hipnotista sean honestos y abiertos, no volverán a llevarte por el mal camino." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4077
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8b72df89:

    # "With her hand placed assuringly on her recovering companion, Nozomi turns her gaze back to me once more." with dissolve
    "Poniendo su mano sobre su convaleciente acompañante para reconfortarla, Nozomi vuelve su mirada hacia mí una vez más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4079
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_3f899bd6:

    # n "Now Kyou, we need to leave. But I'd like to think we've all learned something today." with dissolve
    n "Ahora, Kyou, tenemos que irnos. Pero quiero pensar que todos aprendimos algo hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4081
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_bcdf9833:

    # n sad_side "Hypnosis can affect people in powerful ways, and leave severe long-lasting consequences if you're not careful." with dissolve
    n sad_side "La hipnosis puede afectar a la gente de maneras poderosas, y dejar graves y duraderas consecuencias si no tienes cuidado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4083
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a56ed9ef:

    # n frown "It's not a tool for personal gratification. So I really hope you understand now, how reckless you were being." with dissolve
    n frown "No es una herramienta para la gratificación personal. Así que, de verdad espero que lo entiendas ahora, lo imprudente que has estado siendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4084
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a3340d89:

    # "With a sigh, I can only resignedly nod my head."
    "Con un suspiro, no puedo hacer más que asentir con resignación."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4085
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_a43482ec:

    # ks sigh "Yeah, I get it... Message received."
    ks sigh "Sí, lo entiendo... Mensaje recivido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4088
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_9458b185:

    # "Taking my penlight in my hand once again, I look to it as I give voice to my regrets."
    "Tomando la linterna en mi mano una vez más, la observo mientras expreso mis arrepentimientos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4090
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8aa503db:

    # ks neutral "I just really wanted it to work, you know? I tried so hard that I even made this to help me do it." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Es solo que en serio quería que funcionara, ¿saben? Me esforcé tanto que incluso hice esto para ayudarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4091
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_19ec9009:

    # ks "And when it did work, and when Hiroko responded so well... yeah, it was hard to stop."
    ks "Y cuando sí funcionó, cuando Hiroko respondió tan bien... bueno, fue difícil parar."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4092
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_2e184cc8:

    # ks "We had beef with each other, and I guess I couldn't let go of that. So it wasn't hard to keep going."
    ks "Teníamos saña entre nosotros, y supongo que no pude dejar ir eso. Por lo que no me costó seguir adelante."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4093
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_be8c8238:

    # ks "Not to mention how exciting it was, to see how far I could push you. I never even thought about how dangerous it was."
    ks "Sin mencionar lo emocionante que fue, ver lo lejos que podía empujarte. Ni siquiera me puse a pensar en lo peligroso que era."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4094
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_5b7b1e42:

    # ks "I didn't have to go so hard. I never set out to push you like that, Hiroko. I just..."
    ks "No debí ser tan duro. Nunca quise presionarte así, Hiroko. Tan solo..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4096
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ce4a58d8:

    # ks sad "I didn't respect your mind, Hiroko. I didn't respect hypnosis. I'm sorry."
    ks sad "No te respeté, Hiroko. Y no respeté la hipnosis. Lo siento."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4098
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_8bf491aa:

    # "Hiroko lets an uncomfortable moment linger as she stares back at me." with dissolve
    "Hiroko deja que un incómodo momento se prolongue mientras me devuelve la mirada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4100
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_ca42b005:

    # h "... A-anyway, we got a party to get to."
    h "... E-en fin, tenemos una fiesta a la que asistir."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4111
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_24a5f3d1:

    # "But if she had anything she wanted to say to me, she leaves it unsaid as the pair of them get up to leave."
    "Pero si tenía algo que quisiera decirme, lo deja sin decirse, y las dos se levantan para retirarse."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4116
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_49866789:

    # h tennis_headhold2 sleeptalk "I'll... h'yeah, seeya around." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 sleeptalk "Te... sí, te veo luego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4118
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_0d715f27:

    # "They leave the house with barely another word."
    "Salen de la casa sin apenas decir otra palabra."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4121
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e0d9d790:

    # "So I'm back in my room once again, with only my regrets from the evening for company."
    "Y yo nuevamente estoy de vuelta en mi habitación, sin nada más que mis arrepentimientos para acompañarme esta noche."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4122
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_25840177:

    # "I let my wish for revenge get the better of me and I may have blown it with both of them."
    "Dejé que mi deseo de venganza me superara y puede que lo haya echado todo a perder con esas dos."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4123
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_9d768f6d:

    # "Maybe my interest in hypnosis is over after all this. Maybe not."
    "Tal vez mi interés por la hipnosis se haya acabado después de esto. Tal vez no."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4124
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_26511caf:

    # "But one thing's for certain..."
    "Pero de una cosa sí estoy seguro..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:4127
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster2_e21d89b3:

    # "... I'm ditching this damn light."
    "... Voy a tirar esta maldita linterna."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-10-21 19:04

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1522
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_64050964:

    # "Did dad's business trip finish early? He wasn't supposed to be back until tomorrow."
    "¿El viaje de negocios papá terminó antes? No se suponía que regresara hasta mañana."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1524
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_97ca3bd7:

    # ks casual frown "H... hello? Dad?"
    ks casual frown "¿H... hola? ¿Papá?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1525
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5bb93a5c:

    # "Shit, the door's ajar? Did he come home drunk or something? What the hell?!"
    "Mierda, ¿la puerta está semiabierta? ¿Llegó ebrio o algo? ¡¿Qué diablos?!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5fcb8d74:

    # "... Nah come on, this is no time to panic. Dad came home drunk last night and left the door open. That's the only explanation that even makes a lick of sense."
    "... Nah, vamos, no entres en pánico. Papá llegó ebrio anoche y dejó la puerta abierta. Es la única explicación que tiene una pizca de sentido."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:1531
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_884bb1cd:

    # "But just to settle my nerves I'll go from room to room and check the corners. Then I can get on with my day."
    "Pero solo para calmar mis nervios, iré de habitación en habitación a revisar las esquinas. Luego podré seguir con mi día."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-12-01 10:28

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2904
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6bd38ed6:

    # r concerned_side "She's working herself so hard she apparently napped all morning yesterday. But she seems so disconnected about everything." with dissolve
    r concerned_side "Esta trabajando tan duro que al parecer durmió ayer toda la mañana. Pero la noto muy desconectada de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:2905
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f28e74e4:

    # r concerned "I can't figure her out at all." with dissolve
    r concerned "La verdad no la entiendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3072
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5b5c338b:

    # ks sigh "We didn't have to do this tonight, Hiroko. The only reason we are is because you tried to get out of what you owe me." with dissolve
    ks sigh "No teníamos que hacer esto esta noche, Hiroko. La única razón por la que lo estamos haciendo es que intentaste zafarte de lo que me debes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3440
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_018802a2:

    # "Fuck. I don't want to admit it, but this is making me uncomfortable. Like I'm really going too far by pushing the limits of her hypnotic suggestibility."
    "Mierda. No quiero admitirlo, pero esto me está poniendo incómodo. Como si de verdad estuviera yendo muy lejos al empujar los límites de su sugestionabilidad hipnótica."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3441
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_181a4d9e:

    # "And hell, I've certainly gotten more than even with her."
    "Y vaya, ciertamente ya estoy más que a mano con ella."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3442
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8a4a545b:

    # "But even so... in spite of all that..."
    "Sin embargo... a pesar de todo eso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:3443
translate spanish Day7_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_46db7d04:

    # "...I want to finish what we started."
    "... Quiero terminar lo que empezamos."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-02 22:08

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:851
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_3710bd38:

    # "A somewhat restless sleep is followed by the early rays of the Sunday morning sunshine."
    "Una noche de poco descanso da lugar a los casi primeros rayos de sol de la mañana del domingo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:853
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_8a661642:

    # "It's way too early to be awake..."
    "Es muy temprano para estar despierto..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:857
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_ed089744:

    # "... But just then an angry-sounding buzz comes from my phone as if to say \"No it's not!\""
    "... Pero en ese momento un zumbido que pareciera iracundo brota de mi teléfono como si dijera \"¡No, ¿según quién?!\""

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:858
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_193ee21d:

    # "So I let out a weary sigh and pull the phone into my lap to see what Nozomi wants..."
    "Así que, con un cansado suspiro, tomo el celular y lo pongo en mi regazo para ver qué es lo que quiere Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:859
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_facc404c:

    # n "\"Good morning! Are you ready for today?\""
    n "\"¡Buenos días! ¿Listo para hoy?\""

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:860
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_b17cdabd:

    # "I look at the clock on my phone. There's still plenty of time to get to school before the start of the tournament."
    "Miro el reloj en mi teléfono. Aún hay tiempo de sobra para llegar a la escuela antes de que empiece el torneo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:861
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_25adfad7:

    # ks casual sigh "Well somebody's excited."
    ks casual sigh "Veo que alguien está emocionada."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:862
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_2b857a9d:

    # "Was she worried I'd be a no show if she didn't check on me?"
    "¿Le preocupaba que no fuera si no me llamaba?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:863
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_6f4c3fad:

    # n "\"Like you're not!\""
    n "\"¡No digas que tú no!\""

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:864
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_beb0b5f0:

    # "But wait, why would she be worried? Unless..."
    "Pero espera, ¿por qué se preocuparía? A no ser..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:865
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_aba91f28:

    # n "\"You remember what I suggested to you yesterday, right?\""
    n "\"Recuerdas la sugestión que te di ayer, ¿verdad?\""

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:866
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_ae0f2bf4:

    # "Unless..."
    "A no ser..."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:867
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_48786bfa:

    # ks confused "Uh... no?"
    ks confused "Eh... ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:869
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_1ebc4b29:

    # "Unless her plans for me today are so heinous that I'd never go along if I could remember them?"
    "¿A no ser que lo que me tiene planeado para hoy sea tan atroz que yo nunca accedería si lo recordara?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:869
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_e140229b:

    # n "\"Perfect, see you soon!\""
    n "\"¡Perfecto, nos vemos ahí!"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:871
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_03a97981:

    # "She did put me under with the penlight before she left yesterday, and gave me some kind of post-hypnotic trigger for the tournament."
    "Ella me hipnotizó con la linterna antes de irse ayer, y me dio alguna clase de anclaje post-hipnótico para el torneo."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:872
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_eec6607f:

    # "Said there wouldn't be time to do any of that on the day itself; I remember that much."
    "Me dijo que no habría tiempo de hacerlo el mismo día; recuerdo al menos eso."

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:875
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_3c0a22ac:

    # "But what was the trigger? Does she really have to insist on making me forget what she's done every time?"
    "Pero ¿qué clase de anclaje? ¿En serio hace falta que insista en hacerme olvidar lo que me hace cada vez?"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:876
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_35be1a7b:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: Regrettably, this is where I have to leave things for this month. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Muy a mi pesar, lo tengo que dejar aquí este mes. ))"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:877
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_3c01df7b:

    # "(( Sorry for the lack of new writing. I'll try again next time :/ ))"
    "(( Lamento la poca escritura nueva. Volveré a intentarlo la próxima vez. :/))"

# game/Kyou 7.rpy:878
translate spanish Day7_Nozomi_Switch_Safe_a08c132c:

    # "{size=30}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}"
    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"

